quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,Qâf. Ngujilumbila Qur’an jakuchimbichika (kuti tinchiukulidwa m’malembe)
  50,2,"Nambo akusimonga ya kwaichilila nkutetela (Muhammadi ﷺ) jwakuumila mu ŵanyapeo. Basi achimakafili ni akutiji: “Achi ni chindu chakusimosya.”"
  50,3,"“Ana patuchiwapo, ni kusyuka litaka (chisimu uwwe tuchiukulidwa)? Kwalakweko ni kuwuja kwakutalichila (kwangaŵa nkupatikana).”"
  50,4,"Chisimu Uwwe tukumanyilila yaikupungusya litaka mwajamanjao (mu ilu yao ndema jaakuola m’malembe), soni Kukwetu kwana Chitabu chakusunga (chilichose Al-Lauh Al-Mahfȗz)"
  50,5,"Nambo ayikaaniile yakuona ndema ja yaichilile, ni ali mu kaŵe kecholoŵane (akulepela kulekanganya sikati ja yakuona ni yaunami)"
  50,6,Ana ngaakuliona liwunde pachanya pao yatutite kalitaŵe kakwe ni kalisalalisye kakwe! Soni nganilikola mapesa
  50,7,"Ni litaka tulijasesye, ni tuŵisile palakwepo yakunyichisya (matumbi), ni tumesisye palakwepo ntundu uliose (wa mmela) wakusalala"
  50,8,(Kuti iŵe yalakweyi) yakuwugula meso ni yakunkumbusya kapolo jwalijose jwakuwujila (kwa Allah pakutenda toba)
  50,9,"Ni tutulwisye kuumila kwinani mesi gaupile (wula), ni tumesyisye ni galakwego migunda kwisa soni songolo syaagungulidwa"
  50,10,Ni mitende jelewulewu jajikwete itungatunga ya isogosi yakonyokonyo
  50,11,"(Kuŵa) lisiki lya achikapolo (Ŵetu), ni tukuchisyusyaga nago (mesigo) chilambo chachiwe, iyyoyopeyo ni mukuchiŵela kopoka (kwa m’malembe)"
  50,12,"Ŵaakaaniile paujo pao (Makuraishi nkanigaiche) ŵandu ŵa Nuhu, achimisyene chisima ni achina Samuda"
  50,13,"Ni achina Adi, Firiauna ni achalongo achimijakwe Lutwi"
  50,14,"Ni akutama nyyitekete (ŵandu ŵa Shuaibu), ni ŵandu ŵa Tubba‘i (ŵa ku Yemeni), ŵaliose mwa jamanjao ŵaakaaniile Achimitenga, basi ni chasimichiche chitetelo Changu (pa ŵanganyao)"
  50,15,"Ana ni twapesile ni gumba kwandanda? (Ngwamba), nambo ŵanganyao ali mu kaichila ya gumba kwasambano"
  50,16,"Soni chisimu Uwwe tun’gumbile mundu, ni tukumanyilila yaikunsongonela ntima wakwe, soni Uwwe tuli dusi nnope kwa jwalakwe (ni umanyilisi Wetu) kupunda ntasi ŵakuuta myasi (wannukosi mwakwe)"
  50,17,(Kumbuchilani) katema kaakupochela (itendo ya mundu ni kuilemba) akupochela ŵaŵili (Achimalaika) ŵaakutama chakun’dyo ni chakunchiji
  50,18,"Ngaakulumukulaga (mundu) liloŵe lililyose, ikaŵeje kukwakwe kukuŵa kwana nkwembecheya jwatayali (kulemba)"
  50,19,"Ni kuuchiyika kolelwa kwa chiwa mwakuonaonape, (ni tachisalilidwa mundu yanti): “Ayi ni ayila yamwaliji nkuiŵambala.”"
  50,20,"Ni lichigombedwa lipenga, lyele ni lisiku lyaipotesi"
  50,21,Ni tachiyika mundu jwalijose ni akunchiinga ni akuntendela umboni (ŵachilaika)
  50,22,"(Tachisalilidwa nkuleeŵa kuti): “Chisimu mmwe mwaliji nkukwanjila ya yalakweyi, basi tum’bunukwile chisiŵilo chenu, mwanti liso lyenu lelo lili lyakutema.”"
  50,23,"Ni tachiŵecheta n’jakwe jwangalekangana najo (lilaika lyalyalembaga masengo gakwe): “Ayi ni yaili kukwangu tayali (yamasengo gakwe gangalumbana).”"
  50,24,"(Allah tachalamula Achimalaika ŵaŵili ŵala lyakuchiinga ni lyakutendela umboni kuti): “Mumponyaani ku Jahannama jwalijose jwakufulu nnope, jwamakani.”"
  50,25,"“Jwakusiŵilila yambone, jwakusumba mpika, jwakaichila.”"
  50,26,"“Ajula juŵaŵisile nnungu jwine (jwakun’galagatila) pampepe ni Allah, basi mumponyani mu ilagasyo yawukali.”"
  50,27,"Ni tachiŵecheta n’jakwe jwangalekangana najo (jwachishetani): “Ambuje ŵetu! Une nganinansochelesya jwalakweju, nambo kuti jwaliji nkupotela kwakutalikangana nnope (ni yakuona).”"
  50,28,"(Allah) tachiti: “Ngasinkangana pameso Pangu, soni namasile panannongochesye chitetelo Changu.”"
  50,29,"“Ngalikasagalausyidwaga liloŵe Kukwangu, soni Une nganimba jwakwatenda lupuso ata panandi achikapolo (Ŵangu).”"
  50,30,"Lisiku lyatuchijiwusya Jahannama kuti: “Ana n’gumbele?” Basi jalakwe ni jichiti: “Ana pana yakonjechesya?”"
  50,31,"Ni jichiŵandichisyidwa Mbepo kwa ŵaoga (wakun’jogopa Allah), ngasijiŵa pakutalichila"
  50,32,"(Tachisalilidwa yanti): “Ayi ni yamwapedwaga chilanga, ya jwalijose jwakuujilaujila (kwa Allah pakutenda toba), jwakusunga (malamusi Gakwe).”"
  50,33,"“Juŵan’jogwepe Allah mwangali kum’bona, ni jwaiche ni ntima wagalauchila (Kukwakwe pakutenda toba).”"
  50,34,"(Tachisalilidwa yanti): “Jijinjilani (Mbepojo) mwantendele. Ali ni lisiku lya umi wandamo.”"
  50,35,"Akwete kupata ŵanganyao chilichose chatakachisacheje mwalakwemo, soni Kukwetu kwana yakonjechesya (kum’bona Allah)"
  50,36,"Ana mikutula jilingwa jatwajijonasile paujo pao, ŵaŵaliji ŵamachili nnope kwapunda ŵanganyaŵa, nambo soni ŵasyungwile-syungwile mu ilambo, ana ni ŵapapatile pakutilila (ndema ja yaichilile ipotesi, ngati ŵajonasiche)"
  50,37,"Chisimu mu yalakweyo muŵele mwana chikumbusyo kwa mundu jwakwete ntima (waganisya), kapena jwaakutejela liwiwi ni nsyenejo juli papopo (ni nganisyo syakwe)"
  50,38,"Soni chisimu chene twagumbile mawunde ni mataka ni yaili chilikati chakwe m’moŵa nsano nalimo, ni nganikutukwaya kupela"
  50,39,"Basi pililani pa yaakuŵecheta, ni nnuswejesyeje lumbili lwa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) lyuŵa nkanilikopoche (pakuswali swala ja Fajr), nambo soni nkanilitiŵile (pakuswali swala ja Dhuhr ni Asr)"
  50,40,"Nambo soni chilo luswejesyani (lumbili lwa Ambuje ŵenu pakuswali swala ja Maghrib ni Isha), ni panyuma pa kusujudu (panyuma pakuswali swala sya Fard nswaliji soni swala sya sunna, nikutendaga Subhânallâh, Alhamdulillâh ni Allâh-Akbar)"
  50,41,Soni pikanani (ya) lisiku lyatachiŵilanga nkuŵilanga kuumila pamalo pakuŵandika
  50,42,"Lisiku lyatachiupikana n’gumilo (wa lipenga) mwakuonaonape, lyele ni lisiku lyakopoka (m’malembe)"
  50,43,"Chisimu Uwwe ni Ŵatukupelekaga umi ni chiwa, soni Kukwetu ni kwakuwujila"
  50,44,"Lisiku lyaliichaaganjichila litaka (kuti akopochemo) mwachitema-chitema, wele ni nsonganganyo wakwepepala nnope Kukwetu"
  50,45,Uwwe tukumanyilila chenene yaakuŵecheta. Soni mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) nganim’ba ŵakwakanganichisya ŵanganyao (ku chikulupi). Basi munkumbusyani ni Qur’an jwaakogopa chitetelo Changu
  51,1,Ngujilumbila (mbungo) jajikututumya luwundu (lwamesi ni kuŵelekasya mawunde gawula)
  51,2,Ni (ngugalumbila soni mawunde) gagakutwichila mesi gausito
  51,3,Ni (yombo) yaikwenda (m’mbwani) mwakutulalila
  51,4,"Ni (Achimalaika) ŵaakugaŵanya chilamusi (cha Allah, mpela wula ni malisiki gane)"
  51,5,Chisimu yankupedwa chilanga iŵele yakuonaonape
  51,6,Soni chisimu malipilo gaŵele gakupatikana
  51,7,Ngulilumbila liwunde lyalikwete kagumbidwe kambone
  51,8,Chisimu ŵanganyammwe n’di pa maloŵe gakutindana (gakwamba Qur’an ni Muhammadi ﷺ)
  51,9,Akugalawusyidwa ni galakwego (kuleka kujikulupilila Qur’an ni Muhammadi ﷺ) jwagalawusyidwe (kuleka chikulupi cha Tauhidi)
  51,10,Pamasile palaniwe ŵaunami
  51,11,"Aŵala ŵaatiŵiile mu ujinga, achikwanjilaga (ya Akhera)"
  51,12,"Akuwusyaga (mwachipongwe): “Ni chakachi (kwika kwakwe lyele) Lisiku Lyamalipilo?”"
  51,13,(Lyele ni) lisiku lyatachilagasyidwa (pakuchomedwa) ku Moto
  51,14,"(Tachisalilidwa kuti): “Pasyani kulagasyidwa kwenu, ayi ni ayila yamwaliji nkuijanguya (kuti iyicheje, sano ni iyiche).”"
  51,15,Chisimu ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah) tachiŵa m’Matimbe ga ku Mbepo ni achitutumule
  51,16,Achipochelaga yaŵapele Ambuje ŵao (Allah). Chisimu ŵanganyao nkaniyiŵe yalakweyo (ku duniya) ŵaliji ŵakolosya (masengo)
  51,17,Ŵaliji nkugona panandipe chilo
  51,18,Soni kumasikusiku ŵanganyao ŵaliji nkuŵenda chikululuko (kwa Allah)
  51,19,Ni m’chipanje mwao mwaliji mwana liwunjili lyakumpa nkuŵenda ni nkwimidwa (ligongo lya kulisiŵilila kuŵenda)
  51,20,Ni petaka pana ilosyo (yakulosya ukombosi wa Allah) kwa ŵakusimichisya (chikulupi chao)
  51,21,"Ni mu (kagumbidwe ka) jenumanja ŵakwe, ana ngankulola"
  51,22,Soni kwinani ni kwalili lisiki lyenu ni yankupedwa chilanga
  51,23,"Basi ngunnumbila M’mbuje jwa kwinani ni pasi, chisimu yalakweyi yakuona, mpela muyiŵelele (yakuona) yanti jenumanja nkuŵechetaga"
  51,24,Ana jinyyiche abali ja achalendo ŵa Ibrahima ŵakuchimbichikwa
  51,25,"Pa ndema jaŵajinjile kukwakwe ni ŵatite: “Ntendele!” Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ntendele!” (Ni jwatite soni chamuntima: “Jenumanja ni) ŵandu ŵangamanyika (kukwangu).”"
  51,26,"Ni ŵagalauchile ku ŵapeŵasa ŵakwe (mwangalolechela), ni ŵayiche nako kan’gombe kakunakana (kejoche)"
  51,27,"Ni jwakaŵandichisye kukwao. (Pajwagaweni magasa gao kuti ngagakujigala kulya) jwatite: “Ana uli ngankulya?”"
  51,28,"Basi ni wampatile woga wakwajogopa ŵanganyao. Ŵanyao ŵatite: “Nkajogopa.” Ni ŵampele abali jakusengwasya janti chakole mwanache jwakumanyilila nnope"
  51,29,"Ni ŵayiche ŵankwakwe (ŵali Sara) ni masegwe, aku ali nkuliputa kungope (ligongo lya usimongo), ni ŵatite: “Jwanchekulupe, jwampalale (timbeleche chinauli)!”"
  51,30,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Iyyoyopeyo (tim’beleche mwam’belelemo), Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) niyatite, chisimu Ŵalakweo ni Ŵalunda lwakusokoka, Ŵakumanyilila nnope.”"
  51,31,"(Kaneka Ibrahima) jwatite: “Abali jao (jine) jaichile nijapi jaomanja akutumidwa?”"
  51,32,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Chisimu uwwe tutumisyidwe ku ŵandu ŵakuleŵa.”"
  51,33,“Kuti tukaatumichisye sakalawe syelongo (lya ku Moto).”
  51,34,“Syeŵichidwe chimanyilo kwa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) kwaŵichila akusumba mpika (pasambi).”
  51,35,Basi ni twaakopwesye ŵaŵaliji mwalakwemo mwa akukulupilila
  51,36,Nambo nganitujisimana mwalakwemo ikaŵeje nyumba jimpepe ja Asilamu (Lutwi ni ŵanache ŵakwe ŵaŵili ŵachikongwe)
  51,37,Ni twalesile mwalakwemo chilosyo (cha ipotesi jajili mbwani jajiwe) kwa ŵandu ŵaakuijogopa ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope
  51,38,"Nombe mu (abali ja) Musa (muŵele mwana chilosyo cha ipotesi), pandema jatwantumisye kwa Firiauna ni umboni wakuonechela"
  51,39,"Basi (Firiauna) jwanyosyisye ligongo lya machili gakwe, ni jwatite: “(Aju ni) nsaŵi kapena jwamasoka.”"
  51,40,"Ni twankwembekenye jwalakwe ni asilikali ŵakwe ni twaaponyisye m’mbwani, jwalakwe juli jwagambidwa"
  51,41,"Nombe mu (abali ja) achina Adi (muŵele mwana chilosyo cha ipotesi), pandema jatwatumichisye mbungo (jachimbunga) jakonanga"
  51,42,Nganijichilekaga chindu chilichose chajichipujiile ikaŵeje kuchitenda mpela chepukuswe
  51,43,"Nombe mu (abali ja) achina Samuda (muŵele mwana chilosyo cha ipotesi), pandema jaŵasalilidwe kuti: “Sengwagani kwakandaŵi kannono.”"
  51,44,"Ni ŵalikwesisye kuleka lilamusi lya M’mbuje gwao (Allah), ni wakwembekenye n’gumilo (wa ipotesi) aku ali nkulola"
  51,45,"Ni nganakombola kwima (kuti atile), soni nganaŵa ŵanti nikulikulupusya (achimisyene)"
  51,46,"Ni (twajonasile) ŵandu ŵa Nuhu kalakala (nkanaŵe ŵasalidweo), chisimu ŵanganyao ŵaliji ŵandu ŵakunyosya"
  51,47,"Sano liwunde twalitaŵile mwamachili, soni chisimu Uwwe tuŵele Ŵakulisapangula (liwundelyo)"
  51,48,"Ni litaka twalitandiche, basi ni Ŵambone nnope mwa akwasasya (twaliji Uwwe)"
  51,49,"Ni mu chindu chilichose tugumbile iŵili-iŵili (mpela chachilume ni chachikongwe), kuti jenumanja nkumbuchile (ukoto wa Allah)"
  51,50,"Basi (mwasalilani yanti): “Tililani kwa Allah, chisimu une (Muhammadi ﷺ) kukwenu ni nkutetela jwakuonechela jwakuuma Kukwakwe.”"
  51,51,"“Soni ngasim’biika pamo ni Allah nnungu jwine, chisimu une (Muhammadi ﷺ) kukwenu ni nkutetela jwakuonechela jwakuuma Kukwakwe.”"
  51,52,"Iyyoyopeyo (yaakuti pakuntenda mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ kuti nsaŵi kapena jwamasoka), nganijwaichilileje aŵala ŵapaujo pao ntenga jwalijose ikaŵeje ŵanganyao ŵatiji: “(Aju ni) nsaŵi kapena jwamasoka.”"
  51,53,"Ana ate kulechelana gele (maloŵega)? (Ngwamba), nambo ŵanganyao ni ŵandu ŵakusumba mpika (pa ukafili)"
  51,54,"Basi mwatundumalilani ŵanganyao (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ), soni mmwe ngam’ba ŵagambidwa (nkwatundumalilamo)"
  51,55,"Soni kumbusyani, basi chisimu kumbusya tikwakamuchisye ŵakulupilila"
  51,56,Soni nganingamba gumba majini ni ŵandu ikaŵeje kuti angalagatileje Une (Jikape)
  51,57,"Ngangusaka kuumila kukwao lisiki, soni ngangusaka kuti andiisyeeje (kapena kuliisya iwumbe Yangu)"
  51,58,"Chisimu Allah ni Nkupeleka lisiki nnope, Nsyene machili gakulimbangana"
  51,59,"Sano chisimu akwete kupata aŵala ŵalitendele lupuso chipande cha ilagasyo chanti mpela chipande chailagasyo cha achimijao (ŵakala), basi ngasanjanguya (kuti napeje ilagasyoyo ndaŵi jakwe nkanijikwane)"
  51,60,Basi ipotesi tiyichiŵa kwa aŵala ŵaakufuulu pa lisiku lyao alila lyaakupedwa chilanga (cha kwika kwakwe)
  52,1,Ngulilumbila litumbi (lyaŵam’bechetakasyisye Allah Musa lyalili ku Sinayi)
  52,2,Ni chitabu chachilembeedwe (Qur’an)
  52,3,Mu ikalakala yepende yewunukulidwe
  52,4,"Ni Al-Bait-ul-Ma‘mȗr (Nyumba jajili kumawunde mwakulondana ni Likaaba, jaakujijaulilaga Achimalaika mwakuŵilinganya)"
  52,5,Ni nsakasa wenyakulidwe (liwunde)
  52,6,Ni mbwani syegumbasye (mesi)
  52,7,Chisimu ilagasyo ya Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) iŵele yakupatikana kwene
  52,8,Pangali jwakuisiŵilila
  52,9,Lisiku lyalichitenganyika liwunde ni ntenganyiko wamachili
  52,10,Ni gachijenda matumbi ni kajende kaluŵilo
  52,11,Basi ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila
  52,12,Aŵala ŵaakuŵa nkung’anda mu yangali mate
  52,13,Lisiku lyatachitutilidwa ku moto wa Jahannama katutilidwe kamachili
  52,14,"(Ni tachisalilidwa yanti): “Awu ni Moto awula wamwaliji nkuwukaanila.”"
  52,15,"“Ana weleu usaŵi, kapena jenumanja ngankulola?”"
  52,16,"“Ujinjilani (ni kupasya kupoteka kwakwe), pililani kapena nkapilila yalumope kukwenu, chisimu nkulipidwa yamwaliji nkupanganya.”"
  52,17,"Chisimu ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah) tachiŵa m’Matimbe ga ku Mbepo, ni chindimba"
  52,18,"Achiyisengwelaga yaŵapele M’mbuje gwao (Allah), aku M’mbuje gwao ali ŵagosile ku ilagasyo ya Moto Waukali"
  52,19,"(Tachasalila kuti): “Lyagani soni mwagani mwakusengwa ligongo lya ayila (yambone) yamwaliji nkutenda.”"
  52,20,"Ali ajegeme mu itengu yauchimbichimbi yejalidwe chenene, ni tuchalombekasya ni achimmasyeto ŵameso gakulanguka soni gekulungwa mwakusalalila"
  52,21,"Sano aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kwaakuuya ŵanache ŵao pa chikulupi, chitukasimanganye ŵanganyao ni ŵanache ŵao, soni ngatuja kwapunguchisya (malipilo ga) masengo gao chilichose. Mundu jwalijose tachiŵa uwombosi wakuliombolela ku (yakusakala) yaŵapanganyisye (pakutaŵidwa ku Moto)"
  52,22,"Ni tukaajonjechesyeje (ŵakulupililao ndaŵi ni katema) isogosi kwisa soni nyama, mu yataakaisacheje"
  52,23,Takapochelanganeje kwalakweko ipanda (yankologo) wangatendekasya kuŵecheta yangali mate namuno yasambi
  52,24,"Ni taakaasyuunguleje ŵanganyao achiboyi ŵao (ŵakwatumichila), gamba kuŵa ŵanganyao (kamelemende kakwe) nti chisawu ngalekale syesunjidwe"
  52,25,Ni tachigalauchilana ŵane kwa ŵane achiwusyanaga (yatite kawupate ntendele wa ku Mbepo)
  52,26,"Tachiti: “Chisimu uwwe twaliji kala ku maŵasa getu tuli nkogopa (ipotesi ya Allah).”"
  52,27,“Basi Allah atutendele ukoto uwwe ni atugosile ku ilagasyo ya Moto.”
  52,28,"“Chisimu uwwe twaliji kala (ku duniya) tuli nkum’bomba (Jwele Jikape), chisimu Jwalakwe ni Jwambone nnope, Jwachanasa channope.”"
  52,29,"Basi kumbusyani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ), soni mmwe nganim’ba abimbi kapena ŵamasoka pa chindimba cha Ambuje ŵenu (champele, wauli utume)"
  52,30,"Kapena ŵanganyao akutiji: “(Jwalakweju ni) nkwiimba ilaanga, tugamba kun’jembechela kuti chimpate chiwa (yachatite pakwapata akwiimba ŵane ŵaakala)?”"
  52,31,"Jilani: “Jembechelaani, chisimu une none ndinamwe mwa akwembecheya.”"
  52,32,"Kapena lunda lwao ni lwalukwalamulila yalakweyi, kapena agambile kuŵa ŵandu ŵakusumba mpika"
  52,33,"Kapena akutiji: “Jwalakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) ni jwaajituunjile (Qur’aniji)?” (Ngwamba), nambo kuti ŵanganyao ngaakukulupilila"
  52,34,"Basi ayiche najo abali janti mpela jalakweji (Qur’an), naŵaga jamanjao akuŵecheta yakuona"
  52,35,"Kapena ŵagumbidwe mwangali chilichose (chakwagumba), kapena ŵanganyao ni ŵaŵaligumbile (achimisyene)"
  52,36,"Kapena ŵanganyao ni ŵaŵagumbile mawunde ni mataka? (Ngwamba), nambo kuti ngakusimichisya (ya ilagasyo ya Allah)"
  52,37,"Kapena akwete ŵanganyao imatiilo ya Ambuje ŵenu (Allah), kapena ŵanganyao ni ŵaakwete machili gakutendela yaakusaka"
  52,38,Kapena akwete makwelelo (gakwelela kwinani) ni akupikanilaga pa galakwego (yakuŵecheta Achimalaika kwinaniko)? Basi ayiche naotu akupikanila ŵaowo umboni wakuonechela
  52,39,"Kapena Jwalakwe (Allah) ni jukwete ŵanache ŵachikongwe, sano jenumanja ni nkwete ŵanache ŵachilume"
  52,40,"Kapena mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) nkwajuga ŵanganyao malipilo, sano jamanjao ni akusitopelwa nasyo ngongole"
  52,41,"Kapena akwete ŵanganyao (ilimu) yakusisika, basi ŵanganyao ni akulemba (yalakweyo)"
  52,42,Kapena akusaka kutenda maliindi? Basi aŵala ŵaakufuulu ni ŵali ŵakwaujila malindi gao
  52,43,Kapena akwete ŵanganyao nnungu jwine jwangaŵaga Allah? Aswejele Allah ku yaakum'bwanganya nayo
  52,44,"Namuno angachione chipande cha liwunde chinankugwa (kukwao kwakuli kwika kwa ipotesi), angatite: “(Aga ni) mawunde gawula gagakamatene (ngaŵa kwika kwa ipotesi).”"
  52,45,"Basi mwalekaani, mpaka tasimangane nalyo lisiku lyao alila lyatachikomoka kwa kuwa mu lyalakwelyo"
  52,46,"Lisiku lyaangaakamuchisya malindi gao chilichose, soni ŵanganyao ngasakulupusyidwa"
  52,47,"Soni chisimu akwete kupata aŵala ŵaatesile lupuso (ligongo lya ukafili wao) ilagasyo (ine pa duniya pano) nkaniyiŵe yalakweyo (ya ku Akhera), nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao ngakumanyilila"
  52,48,"Basi chijembecheyaani mwakupilila (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) chilamusi cha Ambuje ŵenu (Allah), basi chisimu mmwe nkuloleledwa ni meso Getu, ni lluswejesyeje lumbili lwa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) ndema jankwiimuka (kuumila llugono kapena pamalo palipose)"
  52,49,"Nombe soni chilo lluswejesyeje (lumbili lwa Ambuje ŵenu), ni pakutiŵila ndondwa (kumasikusiku)"
  53,1,Ngujilumbila ndondwa ndema ja jikutiŵila
  53,2,"Nganapotela n’jenuju (Muhammadi ﷺ), soni nganapombotala"
  53,3,Soni ngajukuŵecheta ya chisako (chakwe)
  53,4,Nganigaŵa galakwego ikaŵeje maloŵe gakuuwula gagakuuwulidwa
  53,5,An’jiganyisye (Qur’anijo Jibulilu) jwamachili gamajinji
  53,6,Jwajukwete kaoneche kambone. Basi ni jwatamilichiche (pakaoneche kakwe kasyesyene kaŵan’guumbiile Allah)
  53,7,Jwalakwe (Jibulilu) juli pachipelela cha meso chamwinani nnope
  53,8,"Kaneka ni jwaŵandichile (Jibulilu), basi ni konjechesya soni nnope kuŵandichila"
  53,9,"Ni waliji (uŵandikane wao) mpela sikati ja songa siŵili sya ukunje, kapena kuŵandichila nnope (kupunda pele)"
  53,10,Basi (Allah) ni jwaajuuwiile kwa kapolo Jwakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) ya jwaajuuwiile (kupitila mwa Jibulilu)
  53,11,Ntima (wa Muhammadi ﷺ) nganiulambusya pa yajwaiweni (ni meso gakwe)
  53,12,Ana ni nkukangana najo pa yajukuiona
  53,13,Soni chisimu (Muhammadi ﷺ) ŵam’bweni (Jibulilu) ndema jine (chilo cha Al-Mi‘râj)
  53,14,"Pa chitela chansaawu chakupelelapo (indu yakwela kwinani kapena kutuluka pasi, chachili kusyeto kwa mawunde nsano nagaŵili)"
  53,15,Palakwepo ni pajili Mbepo Jakutamilichikamo
  53,16,Ndema jayachiunichilaga chitela chansaawucho yayachiunichilaga
  53,17,"Liso (lya Muhammadi ﷺ) nganilisembenduka, soni nganilisumba mpika"
  53,18,Chisimu chene jwalakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) jwaiweni ilosyo yekulungwa-kulungwa ya Ambuje ŵakwe (Allah)
  53,19,Ana mwaweni Al-Lâta ni Al-‘Uzzâ
  53,20,Kwisa soni Manâta jwatatu jwinejo (kuŵa milungu jenu mmalo mwa Allah)
  53,21,"Ana jenumanja ni nkwete ŵanache ŵachilume, sano Jwalakwe (Allah) ni jukwete ŵanache ŵachikongwe"
  53,22,Kwele ni gaŵanya kwalupuso (kwakuntenda lupuso Allah)
  53,23,"Nganigaŵatu galakwego ikaŵeje menape (ga isanamu) gan’gakolasile jenumanja ni achatati ŵenu, Allah nganatulusya pa yalakweyo umboni uliose (wakundisya kuigalagatila), ngakukuya ŵanganyao ikaŵeje liganichisya, ni yayikusaka mitima, kutendaga pamasile pachaichilile kuumila kwa M’mbuje gwao (Allah) chongoko"
  53,24,Kapena mundu mpaka akombole kupata chilichose chaakuchiluumba? (Ngwamba)
  53,25,Basi Allah ni Nsyene Akhera ni Duniya
  53,26,"Ana soni Achimalaika ŵalingwa kumawunde ŵangaŵa nkukamuchisya chondechonde jao chilichose, ikaŵeje panyuma pakupeleka lusa Allah kwa jwaankunsaka (mwa ŵanganyao kuti awombe duwa ja chondechonde), ni kunonyelwa najo (nkuwombeledwajo)"
  53,27,Chisimu aŵala ŵangakukulupilila ya Akhera akwakolanga Achimalaika ni mena gachikongwe (pakuŵecheta kuti ŵanganyao ŵanache ŵachikongwe ŵa Allah)
  53,28,"Ni nganakola ŵanganyao pa yalakweyo umanyilisi uliose, ngakukuya ikaŵeje liganichisya, sano liganichisya lyangakamuchisya chilichose pa yakuona"
  53,29,"Basi munnekaani ajula jwaachitundumalile chikumbusyo Chetu (Qur’an), ni ngajukusaka ikaŵeje umi wa duniya"
  53,30,"Chele ni chipelela chao cha umanyilisi. Chisimu Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) ni ŵaakummanyilila jwaapoteele kuleka litala Lyakwe, nambo soni ni ŵaakummanyilila jwajongweche"
  53,31,"Soni Allah ni Nsyene yosope yaili ku mawunde ni yaili petaka, kuti akaalipile aŵala ŵasakesye pa yaŵapanganyisye, ni kwalipila yambone aŵala ŵaakolosisye (masengo)"
  53,32,"Aŵala ŵaakuliŵambasya ilemwa yekulungwa-kulungwa, ni yakunyalaya, ikaŵeje yamwanamwana. Chisimu Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) ni Ŵachikululuko chakusapanguka. Ŵalakwe ni ŵaakummanya chenene jenumanja, kutandila paŵan’gumbaga kuumila mwitaka, ni pandema jankuŵaaga misigo mu itumbo ya achimama ŵenu. Basi ngasilliswejesyaga mwachimisyene, Jwalakwe ni Jwaakummanya chenene jwaali ni woga (wakun’jogopa Allah)"
  53,33,Ana mum’bweni (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) ajula jwaagalawiche (kuleka kuunda malamusi ga Allah)
  53,34,Ni jutosile panandi (mu chipanje chakwe) kaneka ni kuleka (kutolako)
  53,35,"Ana kukwakwe kwana umanyilisi wakusisika, basi jwalakwe ni jukuiona (yanti chipanje chakwecho chichimale ligongo lyakutola)"
  53,36,Ana nganijusalilidwa yaili mu ikalakala ya Musa
  53,37,Ni Ibrahima ajula juŵakwanilisye (chilanga cha Allah)
  53,38,Yanti jwantwiichile nsigo (wasambi) ngasaja kutwichila nsigo (wasambi) wajwine
  53,39,Niyanti mundu nganijukola ikaŵeje yajupanganyisye
  53,40,Nambo soni kuti masengo gakwe gaachionedwa
  53,41,Kaneko ni tachilipidwa malipilo gakwana
  53,42,Ni yanti kwa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) ni kuchipelela (kwakuwujila indu yosope)
  53,43,Ni yanti Jwalakwe (Allah) ni Jwaakutendekaasyaga kuseka ni Jwaakutendekasyaga soni kulila
  53,44,Ni yanti Jwalakwe (Allah) ni Jwaakupeleka chiwa ni Jwaakupeleka soni umi
  53,45,Ni yanti Jwalakwe (Allah) ni jwaagumbile mitundu jiŵili; chachilume ni chachikongwe
  53,46,Kuumila mu lindondwa (lya ulume) pati litajidwe (m’chiŵelechelo)
  53,47,Ni yanti kwa Jwalakwe (Allah) kwana guumba kwine (kwakwimusya ŵawe m’malembe)
  53,48,"Ni yanti Jwalakwe (Allah) ni Jwaakupeleka yakwanila (kuikamulichisya masengo), ni Jwaakupeleka soni yakusalasya"
  53,49,Ni yanti Jwalakwe (Allah) ni M’mbuje jwa ndondwa ja chilimila (jaŵajigalagatilaga ŵarabu ŵane)
  53,50,Ni yanti Jwalakwe (Allah) ni juŵajonasile achina Adi ŵandanda
  53,51,"Ni achina Samuda, ni nganansigasya (ata jumo)"
  53,52,"Kwisa soni ŵandu ŵa Nuhu kalakala, chisimu ŵanganyao ŵaliji ŵalupuso nnope, ni ŵakusumba mpika nnope (pa sambi)"
  53,53,Ni misi jakupitikusyidwa (ja ŵandu ŵa Lutwi) ŵajigwisyisye
  53,54,Ni yam’bunichiile (misijo) yayam’bunichiile (yaili ilagasyo ya sakalawe syelongo lyejoche ni moto wa Jahannama)
  53,55,Ana ni chapi mu chindimba cha Ambuje ŵenu (Allah mmwe amundu) cha nkuchikaichila (kuti mwine nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  53,56,Aju (Muhammadi ﷺ) ni nkutetela jumpepe mwa akutetela ŵandanda
  53,57,Chikusejelela chakusejelela (Kiyama jikuŵandichila)
  53,58,Pangali jwampaka achiunukule (kuti chimanyiche ndema jakwe jakwichila) jwangaŵaga Allah
  53,59,Ana jenumanja nkujisimonga aji abaliji (Qur’an)
  53,60,Ni nkuseka (mwachipongwe) ni ngalilaga (pati nchipikanaga yogoyo ya Allah)
  53,61,Ni n’gamba kwanjila pe
  53,62,Basi munsujudilaani Allah ni mun’galagatileje (Jwele Jikape)
  54,1,"Ndaŵi (jakwichila Kiyama) jiŵandichile, ni ugaanjiiche mwesi"
  54,2,"Soni naga ali achiweni chisimosimo akasanyosyaga, ni akutiji: “(Awu ni) usaŵi wakwendelechela.”"
  54,3,"Ni ŵaakaaniile, ni kuya isako yao, sano chindu chilichose (chambone kapena chakusakala chaŵapanganyisye mundu) chiŵele chakutamilichika (malipilo gakwe lisiku lya Kiyama)"
  54,4,Soni chisimu chene pamasile pasyaayiiche ŵanganyao ngani (mu aji Qur’an) syasikwete nkati mwakwe ikaanyo yaukali (yakwakanya kutenda yakusakala)
  54,5,"(Aji Qur’an jiŵele jegumbale) lunda lwakusokoka nnope, nambo itetelo ya akutetela nganiyiŵa ikamuchisye (kwa ŵandu ŵaajitundumalile)"
  54,6,Basi mwalekani. (Mwakumbusyani) lisiku lyatachiŵilanga nkuŵilanga (Israfil) ku chindu chakunyalaya kusyene (chiŵalanjilo cha pa Kiyama)
  54,7,"Gali gateteŵele meso gao, achikopokanganaga m’malembe, nti chisawu ŵanganyao sombe syakubalalikangana"
  54,8,"Achikangamalaga (aku ali anyakwile ngosi, mwanja) wa kwankuŵilanga. Achimakafili tachiti: “Ali ni lisiku lyakusausya kusyene.”"
  54,9,"Ŵaakaaniile paujo pao (Makuraishi nkanigaiche) ŵandu ŵa Nuhu, basi ŵansisisye kapolo Jwetu (Nuhu), ni ŵatite: “Jwalakweju jwamasoka.” Ni jwakalipilidwe (ni kogoyesyedwa)"
  54,10,"Basi jwaaŵendile Ambujegwe (Allah juchitiji): “Chisimu une ngomboleedwe, basi njokolaani.”"
  54,11,Basi ni twawugwile milango ja kwinani ni mesi gakusuka kwanneso
  54,12,"Ni twaliganjile litaka ni achitutumule, ni gasimene mesi (gakuuma kwinani ni gakopoka pasi) pa chindu chachaliji chepanjepanje (chigumula chakwajonanjila ŵandu ŵa Nuhu)"
  54,13,Ni twan’jigele (Nuhujo) pa chombo chamatabwa chachakomedwe ni misomali (jaitela)
  54,14,"Chaliji nkwenda (mwakuloleledwa) ni meso Getu, kuŵa malipilo kwa ajula juŵaliji ali akaniliidwe (Nuhu)"
  54,15,"Soni chisimu twachilesile (chombocho) kuŵa chilosyo, ana pana ŵaachikumbuchila (ni kuliwunda nacho)"
  54,16,Ana ilagasyo Yangu yaliji uli kwisa soni itetelo Yangu
  54,17,"Soni chisimu chene tujijepepesye Qur’an kuti jiŵe chikumbusyo, ana pana ŵaajikumbuchila (nikuliwunda najo)"
  54,18,Achina Adi (nombe) ŵaakaaniile. Ana ilagasyo Yangu yaliji uli kwisa soni itetelo Yangu
  54,19,Chisimu Uwwe twatumichisye mbungo jakusisima nnope mu lisiku lyachitapani chakwendelechela
  54,20,"Jaliji nkwachuŵa ŵandu (kuja nao mwinani, kaneka nikwagwichisya pasi mwakwapitikusya) nti chisawu ŵanganyao mapata ga itela ya tende yechuŵidwe"
  54,21,Ana ilagasyo Yangu yaliji uli kwisa soni itetelo Yangu
  54,22,"Soni chisimu chene tujijepepesye Qur’an kuti jiŵe chikumbusyo, ana pana ŵaajikumbuchila (nikuliwunda najo)"
  54,23,Achina Samuda ŵaakaaniile akutetela
  54,24,"Ni ŵatite: “Ana mundu jwakuumila mwetuwe jumpepe ni tunkuyeje? Chisimu uwwe pa jele ndemajo chituŵe mu kupotela ni masoka.”"
  54,25,"“Ana chikumbusyo chipelecheedwe kukwakwe (Swaleh jikape) sikati jetu? (Ngwamba), nambo jwalakwe ni jwaunami kusyene, (soni) jwakulikulungusya.”"
  54,26,"Tachimanyilila malaŵi kuti ana nduni jwali jwaunami kusyene, (soni) jwakulikulungusya"
  54,27,"(Twansalile Swaleh kuti): “Chisimu Uwwe tukutumisya ngamiya jekongwe kuŵa mayeso kukwao, basi mwajembechelani ni mpilile.”"
  54,28,"“Ni mwatagulile yanti mesi gagaŵiidwe sikati jao (ni ngamiya, lisiku amweje ŵandu, lisiku line jimweje ngamiya), kumwa kulikose akuŵichilileje (jwakukum’bandika).”"
  54,29,Nambo ŵam’bilasile n’jao (Qudâr bin Sâlif juŵaliji jwakusakalilwa nnope) ni jwajigele (upanga) ni jwajiuleje (ngamiya jila)
  54,30,Ana ilagasyo Yangu yaliji uli kwisa soni itetelo Yangu
  54,31,"Chisimu Uwwe twatumichisye ŵanganyao n’gumilo umpepe, basi niŵaliji nti chisawu mbelenje sya nkutaŵa lichinga (ni gumuka nikupondedwapondedwa)"
  54,32,"Soni chisimu chene tujijepepesye Qur’an kuti jiŵe chikumbusyo, ana pana ŵaajikumbuchila (nikuliwunda najo)"
  54,33,Ŵandu ŵa Lutwi ŵaakaaniile akutetela
  54,34,"Chisimu Uwwe twatumichisye chimbunga cha sakalawe (syasyajonasile wosope ŵene), ikaŵeje ŵaliŵasa lya Lutwi, twajokwele kumasikusiku"
  54,35,"Kuŵa ukoto wakuuma Kukwetu, iyyoyopeyo niyatukutiji pakun’dipila jwaatogolele"
  54,36,"Soni chisimu jwalakwe (Lutwi) jwaatetele ŵanganyao ilagasyo Yetu, nambo ŵaikaichile itetelo"
  54,37,"Soni chisimu ŵannyenjelele (Lutwi kuti ŵape) achalendo ŵakwe (atende nao matanyula), basi ni twatatalesye meso gao, (ni twasalile kuti): “Pasyani ilagasyo Yangu ni itetelo Yangu.”"
  54,38,Ni yaalaaŵiile ŵanganyao kundaŵi ilagasyo yakutamilichika
  54,39,"(Twasalile kuti): “Pasyani ilagasyo Yangu ni itetelo Yangu.”"
  54,40,"Soni chisimu chene tujijepepesye Qur’an kuti jiŵe chikumbusyo, ana pana ŵaajikumbuchila (nikuliwunda najo)"
  54,41,Soni chisimu chene ŵandu ŵa Firiauna yaichilile itetelo
  54,42,"Ŵaakaaniile ilosyo Yetu yosopeyene (nsano nancheche), basi nitwaakwembekeenye kakwembekanye ka Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwakombola (chilichose)"
  54,43,"Ana makafili genu (jenumanja Makuraishi) ni gagali gambone kwapunda ŵanganyao (ŵaŵajonanjidwe kala, mwanti jenumanja ni ngan’jonanjidwa), kapena nkwete chilanga chantunjelele (chachilembedwe) mu itabu (chanti ngasin’jonanjidwa)"
  54,44,"Kapena akutiji: “Uwwe tuli likuga lyejinji mwanti mpaka tukombole kulichenjela (pangali jwampaka atukombole)"
  54,45,"Lichikomboledwa likuga (lyaolyo), ni tachilosya migongo (kutila. Yatendekwe yalakweyi pangondo ja Badr)"
  54,46,"Nambo Kiyama ni chilanga chao (chakwapela ilagasyo), soni Kiyama ni jamakungu gamakulungwa soni jakuŵaŵa nnope"
  54,47,Chisimu akuleŵa ali nkupotela ni m’masoka
  54,48,"(Mwakumbusyani) lisiku lyatachiwutidwaga ku Moto chamakuku, (achisalilidwaga kuti): “Pasyani kakwaye ka Moto.”"
  54,49,Chisimu Uwwe chindu chilichose tuchigumbile kwa mpango (wakwe wawapanjidwe kalape)
  54,50,Ni nganiuŵa ulamusi Wetu ikaŵeje mwanakamo mpela kupila kwa liso
  54,51,"Soni chisimu chene twajonasile ŵakulandana namwe (m’makafili gakalakala), ana pana jwampaka akumbuchile (ni kuliwunda)"
  54,52,Soni chilichose chaŵapanginyisye chili mu itabu (yakulembedwamo masengo gao)
  54,53,Soni chilichose chamwana ni chekulungwa chileembeedwe
  54,54,Chisimu ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah) tachiŵa m’Matimbe ni sulo (sya ku Mbepo)
  54,55,"Pakutama pambone kusyesyene, kwa Nchimwene (Allah) Jwakombola (chilichose)"
  55,1,(Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji
  55,2,Jujiganyisye Qur’an
  55,3,Jwagumbile mundu
  55,4,Ŵan’jiganyisye kuŵecheta
  55,5,Lyuŵa ni mwesi (ikwenda) kwa chiŵalanjilo (chakwe)
  55,6,Itela yakutambala ni itela yakwimilichika ikunsujudilaga (Allah)
  55,7,"Soni liwunde ŵalinyakwile, ni ŵaŵisile chilungamiko"
  55,8,Kuti mkapungusyaga pa kupima
  55,9,"Ni n’jimicheje chipiimo mwachilungamiko, soni nkapungusyaga yakupimidwa"
  55,10,Soni litaka ŵaliŵisile (mwakulitaandika) ligongo lya iwumbe
  55,11,"Mwalakwemo mwana isogosi, ni mitende jajikwete itungatunga"
  55,12,"Ni songolo syasikwete masapi, ni masamba gakunuunjiila"
  55,13,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,14,Jwagumbile mundu (Adam) kuumila mwilongo lyakulilaga mpela liigeleesya
  55,15,Sano majini ni ŵagagumbile kuumila m’malamba ga moto gangali lyosi
  55,16,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,17,"(Allah ni) M’mbuje jwa kungopoko kuŵili (kwa lyuŵa chawu ni chuku), soni ni M’mbuje jwa kungapililo kuŵili (kwa lyuŵa chawu ni chuku)"
  55,18,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,19,Aŵisile mbwani siŵili syasikusimana (jamesi gakunong’a ni jamesi gachijete)
  55,20,"Sikati jakwe jana uŵigo, mwanti syangajinjililana"
  55,21,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,22,Sikasakopokaga mu (mbwani) sinasiŵilisyo ngalekale syekulungwa-kulungwa ni ngalekale syamwana-mwana
  55,23,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,24,Ni jukwete yombo yayinyakuliidwe (tanga syakwe) yaikwenda m’mbwani (yekulungwa-kulungwa) mpela matumbi
  55,25,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,26,Chilichose chachili palakwepo (petaka) chichijonasika
  55,27,Ni jichisigala ngope ja Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) jajikwete uchimbichimbi ni ukoto
  55,28,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,29,"Akasam’bendaga Jwalakwe wosope ŵali ku mawunde ni petaka, lisiku lililyose Jwalakwe juli pa masengo (mpela kwakwesya ni kwaatulusya ŵandu pa uchimbichimbi nambo soni kupeleka umi ni chiwa, ni ine)"
  55,30,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,31,Sampano chitulipe lipesa Uwwe kwa jenumanja jampingo ŵaŵili (ŵandu ni majini lyakum’balanga itendo yenu pa Kiyama)
  55,32,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,33,"E jenumanja makuga ga majini ni ŵandu! Naga tinkombole kupeleta upande wa kumawunde ni petaka (kuti mundiile ngampata), basi peletani. Nganim’ba mpeleete ikaŵeje ni machili (gakuuma Kukwangu)"
  55,34,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,35,"Chigatumisyidwe kukwenu malamba gamoto ni ntofu wenyelenyenduche, ni ngankombola kulupusyana"
  55,36,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,37,Basi palichipapuka liwunde nikuchejela mpela lipende lyechejewu
  55,38,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,39,Basi lyele lisikulyo mundu namuno lijini ngasawusyidwa ya sambi syakwe
  55,40,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,41,"Akuleŵa tachimanyika ni imanyilo yao, basi ni tachikwembekanyisyidwa ni wumbo sya pewuwo pakupwatikanya ni makawu (kaneka ni kuponyedwa ku Moto)"
  55,42,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,43,"(Ichiŵechetedwa kwa akuleŵa mwa kwanyosya kuti): “Aji ni Jahannama ajila jaŵajikanilaga akuleŵa.”"
  55,44,“Taŵeje ali nkusyungula sikati ja jalakweji ni mesi gamoto gamasemule nnope.”
  55,45,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,46,"Sano jwaakujogwepe kwimichidwa pameso pa Ambujegwe (Allah, ni kupanganyaga yalamulidwe, ni kuiŵambalaga yakanyisyidwe), takapate matimbe gaŵili ga ku Mbepo"
  55,47,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,48,(Matimbe) gagakwete nyambi syakutenjela mwakusalalila
  55,49,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,50,Nkatikati mwa (matimbe) ganagaŵiliga mwana achitutumule ŵaŵili ŵaakujilimaga
  55,51,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,52,Mwalakwemo ntundu uliose wa isogosi uli patundu paŵili
  55,53,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,54,"Tachiŵa ali ajegeme mu yakutandika (pa itengu yauchimbichimbi) nkati mwakwe mwekunje nguo ja silika jwakandapalila, ni isogosi ya m’matimbe ganagaŵili ili yakuŵandichila nnope (yaati konyola chitamile)"
  55,55,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,56,"Mwalakwemo mwana (achiŵammakwao) ŵakulola pejipi (ŵakwalola achalume ŵaope ŵangatenda meso mwamwamwa kwa achalume ŵane), nganagoneje nao mundu jwalijose namuno lijini nkanaŵe ŵanganyao (achalume ŵao)"
  55,57,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,58,(Kasalale kao achimmasyetowo) gamba kuŵa nti chisawu ngalekale syakuswejelngo (mpela kwesya ni kutulusya a nnope ni ngalekale syakuchejelela)
  55,59,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,60,Ana pana malipilo ga umbone pangaŵaga kulipa umbone (soni)
  55,61,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,62,"Konjechesa pa (matimbe) gaŵili gala, pana matimbe gane gaŵili soni"
  55,63,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,64,Gakubiliŵita nnope
  55,65,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,66,Nkatikati mwa matimbe ganagaŵiligo mwana achitutumule ŵaŵili ŵakoposya mesi mwamachili (kuumila pasi)
  55,67,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,68,"Mwalakwemo mwana isogosi, kwisasoni mitende ni mikomamanga"
  55,69,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,70,"Mwalakwemo mwana achimmasyeto achambonembone, soni ŵakusalala"
  55,71,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,72,"Ŵameso gakulanguka, ŵachigosedwele mu yumba"
  55,73,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,74,Nganagoneje nao mundu jwalijose namuno lijini nkanaŵe ŵanganyao (achalume ŵao)
  55,75,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,76,"Tachiŵa ali ajegeme m’misago jachisamba, ni (kutamila) makondolo (matelesi) gakusalala nnope"
  55,77,Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  55,78,Linyakwiche (pa uchimbichimbi ni upile) lina lya Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) Asyene uchimbichimbi ni ukoto
  56,1,Patichitendekwa chakutendekwa (Kiyama)
  56,2,Pangali jwakanila yakutendekwa kwakwe
  56,3,(Chalakwe ni) chakwaatulusya (achimakafili pakwajinjisya ku Moto) ni kwakwesya (Asilamu pakwajinjisya ku Mbepo)
  56,4,Ndema jalichitenganyika litaka kutenganyika kwamachili
  56,5,Matumbi ni kusyajidwa-syajidwa
  56,6,Ni kuŵa luwundu lyakuwululusyidwa
  56,7,Ni tinchiŵa jenumanja (pa Kiyama) mikutula jitatu
  56,8,"Basi (pachiŵa pana) ŵandu ŵa kunkono wan’dyo, ana ŵandu ŵa kunkono wan’dyo ni ŵapi (uchimbichimbi wao uchiŵa uli)"
  56,9,"Ni (pachiŵa pana soni) ŵandu ŵa kunkono wanchiji, ana ŵandu ŵa kunkono wanchiji ni ŵapi (kusakala kwao kuchiŵa uli)"
  56,10,Ni (pachiŵa pana soni) ŵaŵalongolele (pakutenda yambone ku duniya) ŵatachiŵa ŵakulongolela (ku Mbepo)
  56,11,Ŵanganyao ni ŵatachiŵa ŵakuŵandichisyidwa (kwa Allah)
  56,12,Tachiŵa m’Matimbe Gachindimba (ku Mbepo)
  56,13,Likuga lyejinji (lya akulongolela ku yambone) lichiŵa lyakutyochela mu ŵandu ŵandanda
  56,14,Sano (likuga) lyannono (lya akulongolela ku yambone) lichiŵa lyakutyochela mu ŵandu ŵakumalichisya
  56,15,Ali pa itengu yauchimbichimbi yeluche (ni golodi ni mitapo jine)
  56,16,Tachiyijegamaga mwakulolegana
  56,17,Tachasyungulaga (pa kwatumichila) achachanda ŵakutamilichika (pa uchanda)
  56,18,"Ni migao kwisa soni mabilika (ga yakumwa), ni ipanda ya ukana wakuumila mu tutumule jwakujilimaga"
  56,19,Ngasalwala nao ntwe namuno kutyoka lunda
  56,20,Ni isogosi iliyose yatakaisaguleje
  56,21,Ni nyama ja ijuni jatakajilaluchileje
  56,22,Ni achimmasyeto ŵameso gakulanguka soni gekulungwa mwakusalalila
  56,23,(Ŵakuswejela) nti chisawu ngalekale syesunjidwe
  56,24,Kuŵa malipilo pa yaŵaliji nkupanganya
  56,25,"Ngaaja kupikana mwalakwemo maloŵe gangali mate, namuno gakutendekasya kupata sambi"
  56,26,"Ikaŵeje maloŵe ganti: Ntendele, ntendele"
  56,27,"Sano (pachiŵa pana) ŵandu ŵa kunkono wan’dyo, ana ŵandu ŵa kunkono wan’dyo ni ŵapi (uchimbichimbi wao uchiŵa uli)"
  56,28,(Tachiŵa) mu itela ya masaawu yetyosye miŵa
  56,29,Ni itela ya magombo yesogole magombo gakwe mwakusajikana chenene
  56,30,Ni miwulili jakwendelechela
  56,31,Ni mesi gakujilima ndaŵi ni katema
  56,32,Ni isogosi yejinji
  56,33,Yangakatichisya kasogole nambo soni yangasiŵiilidwa
  56,34,Ni yakutandika yenyakulidwe (pa itengu yauchimbichimbi)
  56,35,Chisimu Uwwe chitukaaguumbe ŵanganyao (achakongwe ŵakuumila ku duniya) kagumbidwe kane (kakusalala nnope kulekangana ni muŵaŵelele ku duniya)
  56,36,Basi chitukatende kuŵa ŵaali
  56,37,"Ŵakulinonyelesya kwa achalume ŵao, ŵakulandana misingu"
  56,38,(Tachiŵa) ŵa (achalume) ŵa kunkono wan’dyo
  56,39,Likuga lyejinji (lya ŵa kunkono wan’dyo) lichityochela mu ŵandu ŵandanda
  56,40,Nambo soni likuga lyejinji (lya ŵa kunkono wan’dyo) lichityochela mu ŵandu ŵakumalichisya
  56,41,"Ni (pachiŵa pana) ŵandu ŵa kunkono wanchiji, ana ŵandu ŵa kunkono wanchiji ni ŵapi (kusakala kwao kuchiŵa uli)"
  56,42,"(Tachiŵa) mu chimbunga chamoto, ni mesi gamasemule nnope"
  56,43,Ni m’bulili wa lyosi lyepiliwu nnope
  56,44,Wangapeleka kusisimila namuno kutulalila
  56,45,Chisimu ŵanganyao nkaniyiŵe yalakweyi (ku duniya) ŵaliji nkutama umi wakusangalala (ni yakanyisyidwa)
  56,46,Ni ŵaliji nkwendelechela (kutenda) sambi syekulungwa
  56,47,"Ni ŵaliji nkuŵecheta kuti: “Ana patuchiwapo ni kusyuka litaka ni maupa, nambo yakuona uwwe tuchiukulidwa (m’malembe)?”"
  56,48,“Ni achatati ŵetu ŵakwe ŵandanda?”
  56,49,"Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Chisimu ŵandanda ni ŵambesi ŵakwe.”"
  56,50,“Tachisonganganyisyidwa wa kunsongangano wetomechedwe wa lisiku lyakumanyika.”
  56,51,"“Kaneka chisimu ŵanganyammwe, E jenumanja ŵalupuso, (soni) ŵakanila!”"
  56,52,“Tinkalye kwene chitela cha Zakkum.”
  56,53,“Ni tinkachigumbasyeje ndumbo (syenu).”
  56,54,“Ni tinkachimweleje mesi gamasemule nnope.”
  56,55,“Ni tinkamweje mwasikumwelaga ngamiya syanjota nnope.”
  56,56,Aji ni mbiiko jao Lisiku Lyamalipilo
  56,57,"Uwwe twan’gumbile jenumanja, nambi ligongo chichi ngankukulupilila (ya kwimuka m’malembe panyuma pakuwa)"
  56,58,Ana nkuliona uli lindondwa lya ulume lyankudondechesyaga (m’chiŵelechelo)
  56,59,"Ana jenumanja niŵankuligumbaga (kuti liŵe mundu), kapena Uwwe niŵatukuligumbaga"
  56,60,"Uwwe tupimiile chilikati chenu chiwa (kuti jwalijose mwa jenumanja tachiwa), ni nganituŵa Uwwe ŵakulepela"
  56,61,"Kuti chitun’galawusye kagumbidwe kenu (lisiku lya Kiyama), nikun’gumba mu kaŵe kangankukamanyilila"
  56,62,"Soni chisimu chene pamasile pankumanyi gumba kwandanda (kuti Allah ni juŵagumbile), nambi uli ngankukumbuchila (yanti Jwalakwe mpaka jukombole gumba kwaŵili)"
  56,63,Ana nkujiona uli mbeju jankupandaga
  56,64,"Ana jenumanja niŵankujimesyaga, kapena Uwwe niŵatukumesyaga"
  56,65,"Tungasache tungajitesile kuŵa jakuteketuka, ni nkaliji ŵakusimonga (chachintendesye kuti jiteketuche)"
  56,66,"(Ni nkatiji): “Chisimu uwwe tugambile kwasa chipanje chetu.”"
  56,67,“Nambo uwwe tujimidwe.”
  56,68,Ana nkugaona uli mesi gankumwaga
  56,69,"Ana jenumanja ni ŵan’gatulwisye kuumila kumawunde gawula, kapena Uwwe ni Akutulsya"
  56,70,"Tungasache tungagatesile kuŵa gachijete nnope, nambi ligongo chichi ngankutogolela"
  56,71,Ana nkuuwona uli moto wankukolesyaga
  56,72,"Ana jenumanja ni ŵamwagumbile itela yakwe, kapena Uwwe ni Akugumba"
  56,73,"Uwwe tuwutesile walakwe (motowo) kuŵa chikumbusyo (cha Moto wa ku Akhera), ni wakwakamuchisya ŵa paulendo"
  56,74,Basi liswejesyani lina lya Ambuje ŵenu Ŵakulungwa nnope (Allah)
  56,75,Ngumulumbila mwagwila ndondwa (mwakutiŵilila mwakwe kwinani)
  56,76,Soni chisimu chalakwechi ni chilumbilo chekulungwa nnope ingaŵe mwamanyililaga
  56,77,Chisimu jalakweji ni Qur’an jakuchimbichika
  56,78,Jili m’Chitabu chesunjidwe chenene (Al-Lauh Al- Mahfȗz)
  56,79,Ngakuchikwayaga ikaŵeje ŵaswejesyedwe
  56,80,Chakutulusyidwa kuumila kwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope
  56,81,Ana aji abaliji (Qur’an) jenumanja (achimakafili) nkujikaanila
  56,82,Sano kanila kwenu (lisiki lyampele Allah) nikwankukutenda kuŵa kutogolela kwenu
  56,83,Nambi uli ntima uli uyiche pekolongo (ndema jakuwa jumo jwenu ngankuuwuchisyaga m’chilu mwakwe)
  56,84,Kutendaga jenumanja jele ndemajo nkasaŵaga n’di nkulola
  56,85,"Soni Uwwe (Achimalaika ŵakutyosya ntima) tukuŵaga dusi kwa jwalakwe kumpunda jenumanja, nambo ngankutuonaga"
  56,86,"Nambi uli naga nganim’ba ŵanti nikuja kulipidwa (itendo yenu, soni ngasin’jimuka m’malembe)"
  56,87,"(Uli) ngankuuwuchisyaga (ntimao m’chilu mwakwe kuti akawa mundujo), naga jenumanja nkuŵecheta yakuona (kuti kwangali kwimuka m’malembe, ngati nichiwa chakwe chikapagwa)"
  56,88,Sano naga juli (nkuwajo) mwa akuŵandichisyidwa (kwa Allah)
  56,89,"Basi jukasapata ntendele ni lisiki lyakununjila, kwisa soni Litimbe Lyachindimba lya ku Mbepo"
  56,90,Sano naga juli (nkuwajo) mwa ŵandu ŵakunkono wan’dyo
  56,91,"Basi (jukasasalilidwaga kuti): “Ntendele uli kukwenu, (ligongo lyakuŵa kwenu) mu ŵandu ŵakunkono wan’dyo.”"
  56,92,"Nambo naga juli (nkuwajo) mwa akukanila, ŵakupotela"
  56,93,Mbiiko jakwe jikasaŵa mesi gamasemule nnope
  56,94,Ni kupya m’Moto Waukali
  56,95,Chisimu ayi (yatunsimbile mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) ni yakuona yakusimichika
  56,96,Basi liswejesyani lina lya Ambuje ŵenu Ŵakulungwa nnope (Allah)
  57,1,"Iŵele ili nkunswejesya Allah Yosope yaili kumawunde ni petaka, soni Jwalakwe ni Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  57,2,"Uŵele Ŵakwe uchimwene wa kumawunde ni petaka, jukupelekaga umi ni chiwa, soni Jwalakwe pa chindu chilichose juŵele Jwakombola"
  57,3,"Jwalakwe ni Jwandanda (pangali chilichose paujo Pakwe), soni Jwambesi (pangali chilichose panyuma Pakwe), soni Jwapenani kusyene (pangali chilichose pachanya Pakwe), soni Jwakuŵandika nnope (ni umanyilisyi Wakwe, pangali chakuŵandika nnope kupunda Jwalakwe), soni Jwalakwe chindu chilichose juŵele Jwaachimanya chenene"
  57,4,"Jwalakwe ni Ajula juŵagumbile mawunde ni mataka m’moŵa nsano nalimo, kaneka ni jwatenjele pa Arishi (Chindanda Chaulungu). Jukuimanyilila yaikwinjila mwitaka, ni yaikopoka mwalakwemo, ni yaikutuluka kuumila kwinani, ni yaikwela kwalakweko, soni Jwalakwe juli pampepe ni jenumanja (ni umanyilisyi Wakwe) palipose pan’di, soni Allah ichindu yankutenda juŵele Jwakuilolechesya"
  57,5,"Uŵele Ŵakwe uchimwene wa kumawunde ni petaka, soni kwa Allah ni kwakuuchisyidwa ichindu yosope"
  57,6,"Akasachijinjisyaga chilo m’muusi (ni kuleupa muusi kwipipa chilo mpela ndaŵi jachitukuta), ni akwinjisyaga soni muusi m’chilo (ni kuleupa chilo kwipipa muusi mpela ndaŵi jakusisima), soni Jwalakwe ni Nkumanyilila chenene yaili m’mitima"
  57,7,"Munkulupililani Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ, ni ntoleje mu ayila (ipanje) yantesile jenumanja kuŵa ŵakuipochelangana (ŵane kuumila kwa ŵane), basi aŵala ŵaakulupilile mwa jenumanja, ni kutola (ipanje yao), akwete kupata malipilo gamakulungwa"
  57,8,"Chipali chichi kukwenu chikuntendekasya kuti nkankulupilila Allah, kutendaga Ntenga (Muhammadi ﷺ) akum’bilanga kuti munkulupilile M’mbuje gwenu, soni (Allah) pamasile paajigele chilanga chenu? Nam’baga jenumanja ŵanti nikulupilila (basi kulupililani)"
  57,9,"Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwaakuntuluchisya kapolo Jwakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) ma Ȃya gakusalichisya, kuti ankoposye m’chipi (chaukafili) ni kun’jinjisya mu lilanguka (lya Usilamu), soni chisimu Allah kukwenu ni Mpole kusyene, Jwachanasa channope"
  57,10,"Soni chipali chichi kukwenu chikuntendekasya kuti nkatola petala lya Allah, kutendaga Allah ni Nsyene yakulechedwa (yosope) ya kumawunde ni petaka? Nganaŵa alandene mwa jenumanja aŵala ŵaŵatosile nkanikuŵe kuwugula (Maaka) ni kuputa ngondo, ŵanganyao niŵaakwete uchimbichimbi wekulungwa nnope ngalandana ni aŵala ŵatosile panyuma (pakuwugula Maaka) ni kuputa ngondo, nambo ŵosope ŵeneo Allah ŵaapele chilanga cha umbone, soni Allah abali syosope sya yankutenda aŵele Jwaasimanya chenene"
  57,11,"Ana ni nduni jwatankongosye Allah ngongole jambone (pakupeleka chipanje chakwe petala lya Allah) kuti ajijonjechesye kwa jwalakwejo (ni yakonjechesya yejinji, pakun’jonjechesya chipanje chakwe pa duniya pano)? Ni jukwete kupata soni jwalakwejo malipilo gakuchimbichika (ku Akhera)"
  57,12,"Lisiku litinchaona ŵakulupilila ŵachilume ni ŵakulupilila ŵachikongwe lilanguka lyao linankwenda paujo pao ni kunkono wao wan’dyo, (achisalilidwaga yanti): “Kusengwa kwenu lelo! (Nikugajinjila) Matimbe ga ku Mbepo, gasikujilima chapasi pakwe sulo! Tim’be ŵandamo mwalakwemo! Kwalakweko ni kupunda kwekulungwa nnope!”"
  57,13,"Lisiku lyatachiŵecheta achinakunaku ŵachilume ni achinakunaku ŵachikongwe kwasalila aŵala ŵaŵakulupilile: “Tulindani kuti tupale nao lilanguka lyenulyo.” Kuchiŵechetedwa (kukwao mwachipongwe): “Ujilaani munyuma mwenu, ni nkasosesose lilanguka.” Basi ni uchiŵichidwa sikati jao uŵigo wana nnango, nkati mwakwe (upande wa ŵakulupilila) muchiŵa mwana chanasa, nambo kusa kwakwe cha upande ŵakwe (wa achinakunaku) kuchiŵa kwana ipotesi"
  57,14,"(Achinakunaku) tachaŵilanga ŵanganyao (ŵakulupilila), (achitiji): “Ana nganituŵaga imo ni jenumanja (ku duniya pakutenda ibada)?” (Ŵakulupilila) takajile: “Elo (mwaŵaga nowe pachanyape), nambo jenumanja mwalijonasile mwachimisyene (ni unakunaku), ni mwajembechele (kuti yapate ipato Asilamu), ni mwakayichile (ya kwimuka m’malembe), ni yannyenjile isako yenu yaunami mpaka chayiiche chilamusi cha Allah (chiwa), ni ŵannyenjile jenumanja pa ya Allah nkunyenga (Ibulisu).”"
  57,15,"“Basi lelo ngachipocheledwa chaaliwombolela kuumila kukwenu namuno kwa aŵala ŵaŵakufuulu, mauto genu ni ku Moto, gele ni malo genu gakum’bajila, kaje kusakala malo gakuwujila gakwe!”"
  57,16,"Ana nganijikwane ndaŵi kwa aŵala ŵaakulupilile janti mitima jao jiteteŵaleje pa kunkumbuchila Allah, ni (pakuipikana) ayila yakuona yaitulwiche (Qur’an). Soni ngasaŵa nti chisawu aŵala ŵaŵapedwile Chitabu kalakala (Ayuda ni Akilisito), basi jalewipe kukwao ndaŵi (jakulekangana ni achimitume ŵao), ni jajumwile mitima jao, soni ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao ŵakunyosya"
  57,17,"Manyililani yanti Allah akulisyusyaga litaka panyuma pakuwa kwakwe, chisimu chene tunsalichisye jenumanja ilosyo (ya ukombosi Wetu) kuti nkole lunda"
  57,18,"Chisimu akutola sadaka ŵachilume ni akutola sadaka ŵachikongwe, ni kunkongosyaga Allah ngongole jambone (pakupeleka chipanje chao petala lya Allah), tiyijonjechesyedwe kukwao (ipanje yao pa duniya pano), ni akwete kupata soni ŵanganyao malipilo gakuchimbichika (ku Akhera)"
  57,19,"Sano aŵala ŵankulupilile Allah ni Achimitenga Ŵakwe, ŵanganyao kwa M’mbuje gwao ni (ŵaakuŵalanjidwa kuti) ŵakulungamika kusyene (pachikulupi) soni ŵakuwila pa ngondo (jakumenyana ni makafili), akwete kupata ŵanganyao malipilo gao ni lilanguka lyao. Nambo aŵala ŵaakufuulu ni kanila ma Ȃya Getu ŵanganyao niŵandu ŵa ku Moto Waukali"
  57,20,"Manyililani yanti umi wa duniya uŵele ŵamasanje ni wangali mate, nambo soni chipeto, ni kupoochesyaana sikati jenu, ni kutupiya kusonganganya chipanje ni ŵanache. Ili chisawu wula jaukunsengwasyaga nnamalima mmela wakwe, kaneka ni kumula ni nkuuwonaga uli wam’bilichila, kaneka ni ukasaŵaga wakuteketuka (wangali chilichose). Sano ku Akhera tikukaŵe kwana ilagasyo yaukali nnope (kwa achimakafili), nambo soni chikululuko chakuumila kwa Allah ni chinonyelo (kwa ŵakulupilila). Ni nganiuŵa umi wa duniya ikaŵeje chisengwasyo chakunyenga"
  57,21,"Kangamalani wa ku chikululuko chakuumila kwa M’mbuje gwenu (Allah), ni Mbepo kusapanguka kwakwe kuli mpela kusapanguka kwa kwinani ni pasi, jiŵichidwe tayali kwa aŵala ŵankulupilile Allah ni Achimetenga Ŵakwe. Walakweo ni ukoto wa Allah waakumpaga jwansachile, soni Allah ni Nsyene ukoto wekulungwa nnope"
  57,22,"Nganichipatikaneje chipato petaka, namuno mu mwachimisyene, ikaŵeje (chalembedwe) m’Chitabu (cha Al-Lauh Al-Mahfȗz) nkanituchiguumbe, chisimu yalakweyo kwa Allah iŵele yakwepepala kusyene"
  57,23,"Kuti nkadandaula pa yaimpiite, nambo soni nkatwanga pa yampeele, soni Allah ŵangannonyela jwakulikwesya jwalijose jwakuliiti"
  57,24,"Aŵala ŵaakutenda ubayili, ni kwachisyaga ŵandu kutenda ubayili. Sano jwatagalauche (kuleka yalamulidwe), basi (niyakwe), chisimu Allah ni Jwakupata kwejinji Jwakulapilidwa kusyesyene"
  57,25,"Chisimu twaatumisye Achimitenga Ŵetu ni ilosyo yakuonechela, ni twatumisye pampepe ni ŵanganyao chitabu kwisa soni chilungamiko, kuti ŵandu ajime (pakutendelana ichindu yao) mwachilungamiko, ni tutulwisye chisyano, mwalakwemo mwana machili gamajinji (gakuputila ngondo), kwisa soni yakwakamuchisya ŵandu (yakulekangana-lekangana), soni kuti Allah ammanyukule mundu jwaakunkamuchisya Jwalakwe (paajikamuchisya dini Jakwe), ni (kwakamuchisya) Achimitenga Ŵakwe mwangali kum’bona (Allah jo). Chisimu Allah ni Jwakulimbangana nnope, Jwamachili gakupunda"
  57,26,"Soni chisimu chene twantumisye Nuhu ni Ibrahima, ni twaŵisile mu ŵanache ŵao Utume ni Chitabu, basi ŵane mwa ŵanganyao ŵaliji ŵakongoka, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao ŵaliji ŵakunyosya"
  57,27,"Kaneko twakuyichisye mu sajo syao Achimitenga Ŵetu (ŵane), ni twakuyichisye soni ni Isa mwanache jwa Maryam, ni twampele Injil, ni twaŵisile m’mitima mwa aŵala ŵaŵankuyiye upole ni chanasa. Sano ungalombela ŵautandisye achimisyene, Uwwe nganitwalamulila yele. (Achimisyene ni ŵaŵaitandisye yalakweyo) pakusachilila chinonyelo cha Allah, ni nganaugosa (ungalombelao) kaugose kakwe kasyesyene. Basi ni twapele aŵala ŵaŵakulupilile (Allah ni Achimitenga Ŵakwe) mwa ŵanganyao malipilo gao, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao ali ŵakunyosya"
  57,28,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Mun’jogopani Allah, ni munkulupilile Ntenga Jwakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ), tampe mitambala jiŵili ja chanasa Chakwe, ni tam’bichile lilanguka lyatin’jendeje nalyo, soni tankululuchile, sano Allah ni Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope"
  57,29,"Kuti ŵandu ŵaŵapedwile Chitabu (Ayuda ni Akilisito ŵangaakunkulupilila Muhammadi ﷺ) amanyilile yanti ŵanganyao nganakola ukombosi uliose pa ukoto wa Allah, ni kuti ukoto (wosope) uli m’makono mwa Allah akumpaga jwaakunsaka, soni Allah ni Nsyene ukoto wekulungwa nnope"
  58,1,"Chisimu pamasile paapikene Allah liloŵe lya ajula (jwammasyeto) jwaakusisyana namwe (maloŵe) pa ya ŵankwakwe (ŵantuumbiliile), ni jukulaŵila (magambo) kwa Allah, mwanti Allah akuŵa ali nkupikana kuŵechetana kwenu, chisimu Allah ni Jwakupikanichisya Jwakulolechesya"
  58,2,"Ŵandu ŵaakuŵa mu jenumanja ali nkwalandanya achimmasyeto ŵao ni migongo (ja achimama ŵao pa chiŵako), ngaŵa nkuŵa ŵanyao achimama ŵao (pa chiŵako changaŵa nkutenda nao soni ulombela), nganaŵa achimama ŵao ni ikaŵeje aŵala ŵaŵaŵeleche, soni chisimu ŵanganyao akuŵecheta maloŵe gakusakala soni gaunami, soni chisimu Allah ni Nkusiimaasya (ilemwa) Jwakululuka kusyene"
  58,3,"Sano ŵandu ŵaakuŵa ali nkwalandanya achimmasyeto ŵao ni migongo (ja achimama ŵao pa chiŵako changaŵa nkutenda nao soni ulombela), kaneko ni kuusyausya yaŵaŵecheteyo; basi agopole kapolo nkanaiche mwakwayana (ni achiŵammakwaowo), jalakweji ni (misyungu ja Allah) jankuwundidwa najo, sano Allah abali syosope sya yankutenda aŵele Jwaasimanya chenene"
  58,4,"Sano jwanganapata (kapolo) basi chataŵe myesi jiŵili jakuyana nkanaiche mwakwayana (ni ŵankwakwe), nambo jwanganaŵa apakombwele (kutaŵa) basi chiŵape yakulya masikini makumi nsano nalimo . Yalakweyo (ilamulidwe) kuti munkulupilile Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ. Soni jalakweji ni mipingu ja Allah, ni akwete kupata achimakafili ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope"
  58,5,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaakunsiisya Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ, anyosyedwe mpela yaŵatite pakunyosyedwa ŵakala ŵao, soni pamasile patutulwisye ma Ȃya gakusalichisya, ni akwete kupata achimakafili ilagasyo yakwalusya"
  58,6,"Lisiku lyatachasyusya Allah ŵanaose ni kwatagulila yaŵapanganyisye, Allah jwaisonganganyisye (ni kuisunga) nambo ŵanganyao ŵailiŵalile, sano Allah pa chindu chilichose aŵele Mboni"
  58,7,"Ana ngankuiona yanti Allah jukuimanya yaili kumawunde ni yaili petaka? Ngaukasatamidwaga ntemela wa ŵandu ŵatatu ikaŵeje Jwalakwe jukasaŵa Jwancheche jwao, naatamuno wa ŵandu nsano ikaŵeje Jwalakwe jukasaŵa Jwansano najumo jwao, naatamuno wa ŵandu ŵakunandipila pele kapena ŵakutupila ikaŵejepe Jwalakwe jukasaŵa nao palipose pachaŵe (ni umanyilisi Wakwe wangasisika chilichose), kaneka ichindu yaŵapanginyisye tachatagulila lisiku lya Kiyama, chisimu Allah chindu chilichose aŵele Jwaachimanya chenene"
  58,8,"Ana ngankwaona aŵala ŵanya ŵaŵakanyisyidwe kutama ntemela (wamalindi), kaneka ni akuwujauja kutenda yaŵakanyisyidweyo? Ni akusongonelanaga yasambi ni yaumagongo kwisa soni yakunnyosya Ntenga ﷺ. Soni pati am’bichililemo akasankomasyaga ni komasya (kwakuchindimbula) kwanganankomasyeje nako Allah, m’mitima mwao niakutiji: “Nambi uli Allah ngatupa ilagasyo pa yatukuŵechetayi?” Jahannama jichakwana ŵanganyao, chachijijinjila. Kaje kusakala malo gakuujila gakwe"
  58,9,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Pati nchitamaga ntemela basi ngasinsongonelanaga yasambi ni yaumagongo kwisa soni yakunnyosya Ntenga ﷺ, nambo nsongonelaneje yaukoto ni woga (wakun'jogopa Allah), soni mun'jogopani Allah Ajula jwachinchisonganganyisyidwa Kukwakwe"
  58,10,"Chisimu mitemela (jamalindi) jikuumilaga ku shetani kuti ŵaadandaulikasye aŵala ŵaakulupilile, nambo nganaŵa ŵaapoteche nao chilichose ikaŵeje kwa lisosa lya Allah, sano ŵakulupilila ajegamileje kwa Allah pe basi"
  58,11,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Pati nsalilidwemo kuti pelekani lipesa panganya basi pelekani lipesalyo, Allah chansapangulile (ukoto Wakwe), soni pati iŵechetedwe yanti: “Jimani (kuja kutenda masengo ga Dini),” basi jimani. Allah tiŵanyakule pa uchimbichimbi aŵala ŵaakulupilile mwa jenumanja kwisa soni aŵala ŵaapedwile umanyilisi, sano Allah abali syosope sya yankutenda aŵele Jwaasimanya chenene"
  58,12,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Ndema jankusaka kuŵecheta najo Ntenga ﷺ yantemela, basi longosyani (kutola) sadaka (jakwapa masikini) nkaniuŵe ntemela wenuo, yalakweyo ni yaili yambone nnope kukwenu ni yakuswejelesya, nambo naga nganimpata (sadakajo ngalikandu), basi chisimu Allah ni Jwakululuka kusyene Jwachanasa channope"
  58,13,"Ana n'jogwepe kulongosya (kutola) sadaka nkaniuŵe ntemela wenu (wakuŵechetana najo Ntenga ﷺ)? Sano naga nganim’biche mwakutenda, basi Allah an'jepepachisye, sano gambagani kwimika Swala mwakolosya ni kutolaga Zaka, soni mumpikanilani Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ, sano Allah ni Nkusimanya chenene abali syosope sya yankutenda"
  58,14,"Ana ngankwaona aŵala (achinakunaku) ŵatomene nao ulongo ŵandu ŵaŵatumbilile Allah? Ŵanganyao nganaŵa mwa jenumanja nambo soni nganaŵa mwa ŵanganyao, soni akulumbilaga yaunami aku achimanyililaga (kuti akulambusya)"
  58,15,"Allah ŵalinganyichisye ŵanganyao ilagasyo yaukali nnope, chisimu ŵanganyao iŵele yakusakala nnope yaaŵele nkupanganya"
  58,16,"Akutesile kulumbila kwao (kwaunami) kuŵa chakusiŵilila (itendo yao yangalumbana), basi ni ŵasiŵilile (ŵandu) kwitala lya Allah; ni akwete kupata ŵanganyao ilagasyo yakwalusya"
  58,17,"Ngasichija kwakamuchisya ŵanganyao chipanje chao atamose ŵanache ŵao chilichose mu (ipotesi) yakuumila kwa Allah, ŵanganyao niŵandu ŵa ku Moto, ŵanyao kwalakweko takaŵe ŵandamo"
  58,18,"Lisiku lyatachasyusya Allah ŵanaose, basi ni chachiŵa nkulumbila Kukwakwe (Allah, mwaunami) yaŵatiji pakulumbila kukwenu, aku ali nkuganichisya yanti chapate chilichose (pakulumbila kwaoko), manyililani yanti ŵanganyao chisimu chene niŵali ŵaunami"
  58,19,"Shetani jwaguŵatiile ŵanganyao ni jwaliŵeesye kunkumbuchila Allah, ŵanganyao ni likuga lya shetani, manyililani yanti chisimu chene likuga lya shetani nilyalili lyakulepela"
  58,20,Chisimu aŵala ŵaakunsiisya Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ ŵanganyao chachiŵa mu ŵakunyosyeka nnope
  58,21,"Allah jwaalembile yanti: “Chisimu Une ni Achimitenga Ŵangu niŵachituŵe Ŵakupunda.” Chisimu Allah ni Jwakulimbangana nnope, Jwamachili gakupunda"
  58,22,"Ngamwasimana ŵandu ŵaakunkulupilila Allah ni Lisiku Lyambesi ali nkwanonyela ŵandu ŵaakunsisya Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ, namuno akaliji achatati ŵao, kapena ŵanache ŵao, kapena achachimwene ŵao, kapena ŵalukosyo lwao. Ŵanganyao (Allah) alembile m’mitima mwao chikulupi (mwakuchisimika kusyene), ni ŵalimbangenye ni Nsimu (Jibulilu) wakuumila Kukwakwe, ni tachajinjisya ku Matimbe ga ku Mbepo gasikujilima cha pasi pakwe sulo, chakaŵe ŵandamo mwalakwemo. Allah tachanonyela (pakwapochela masengo gao gambone), nombe nao chachinonyelwa Najo (pamalipilo gataachaapa). Ŵanganyao ni likuga lya Allah, manyililani yanti chisimu chene likuga lya Allah ni lyalili lyakupunda"
  59,1,"Iŵele ili nkunswejesya Allah yosope yaili kumawunde ni yaili petaka, soni Jwalakwe ni Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  59,2,"Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwana kwakoposyaga ŵandu ŵaŵakanile mwa anchinsyene chitabu (Ayuda ŵalukosyo lwa Nadhîr) kutyochela m’majumba mwao mu kusonganganyisidwa kwandanda (kwausami). Nganin'ganichisyaga kuti mpaka akopoche, nombe nao ŵaganichisyaga yanti chisimu ŵanganyao gasiŵilile makome gao kwa Allah, basi Allah ni jwaapele (ipotesi) kuumila upande wanganaganichisyaga, ni jwaponyisye woga m’mitima mwao, (mwanti) ŵaliji nkugumula majumba gao ni makono gao kwisa soni makono ga ŵakulupilila. Basi chetelelani jenumanja ŵankwete meso (gakulolechesya mwaumanyilisi)"
  59,3,"Soni ingaŵaaga kuti Allah jwaalembele (pandandape) yakusama, jukaapele ilagasyo pa duniya, nambo akwete kupata ŵanganyao ku Akhera ilagasyo ya Moto"
  59,4,"Yalakweyo paligongo lyanti ŵanganyao ŵatindene najo Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ, sano jwatatindane najo Allah, basi chisimu Allah ni Jwaukali pakupeleka ipotesi"
  59,5,"Muitela ya tende ya mwaikatile (jenumanja Asilamu) kapena ya mwailesile ili chiimile m’mapata mwakwe, basi (yatendekwe) mu lisosa lya Allah ni kuti ŵajalusye ŵakunyosya"
  59,6,"Soni ipanje yakupalagula yaapeleche Allah kwa Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ kuumila kwa ŵanganyao, basi pa (kuipata) yalakweyo nganinnajila kuutusya hachi kapena ngamiya, nambo kuti Allah akwapaga machili Achimitenga Ŵakwe gakwakombolela ŵaakwasaka, sano Allah pa chindu chilichose aŵele Jwakombola"
  59,7,"Ipanje yakupalagula yaapeleche Allah kwa Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ kuumila kwa achinsyene misi, basi iŵele ya Allah ni Ntenga ﷺ ni ŵaulongo (wa Ntenga ﷺ), kwisa soni ŵawina, masikini ni jwapaulendo; kuti ikaŵa yagamba kusyungula chilikati cha ŵakusichila mwa jenumanja. Sano champele Ntenga ﷺ basi chipochelani, nambo chankanyisye basi chilekani. Ni mun'jogopani Allah, chisimu Allah ni Jwaukali pakupeleka ipotesi"
  59,8,"(Ipelechedweje) kuŵakulaga ŵaasamile, aŵala ŵakoposyedwe nsimangwao kwisa soni ipanje yao achisachililaga umbone wa kuumila kwa Allah kwisa soni chinonyelo, ni akuŵa ali nkunkamuchisya Allah (paajikamuchisya Dini Jakwe), ni (akuŵa soni nkunkamuchisya) Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ, ŵanganyao niŵali ŵakuonaonape"
  59,9,"Sano aŵala ŵaŵatemi mu nsinda (wa Madina) ni kulupilila nkanaiche ŵanganyao akuŵa ali nkwanonyela ŵandu ŵaasaamiile kukwao, soni ngaakuchisimana m’mitima mwao chipaka chilichose mu ichindu yaapedwile (akusamao), soni akulongosyaga (isako ya achimijao pa chindu chilichose) kupunda isako yao, namuno angaliji ali nkuchisachilila (chinducho) kwanneso. Sano ŵaakuŵambasyidwa ku ubaili wa ntima wao basi ŵanganyao ni ŵali ŵakupunda"
  59,10,"Sano aŵala ŵaiche panyuma pao akasatiji: “Ambuje ŵetu! Tukululuchilani uwwe ni achimijetu aŵala ŵaŵatulongolele pa chikulupi, ni ngasim'biika m’mitima mwetu uchimwa wakwatendela aŵala ŵaakulupilile, Ambuje ŵetu! Chisimu Mmwejo ni Mpole kusyene, Jwachanasa cha nnope.”"
  59,11,"Ana nganimwaona aŵala akutenda unakunaku ŵaakutiji pakwasalila achimijao aŵala ŵakanile mwa achinsyene chitabu (Ayuda): “Chisimu naga n'di nkoposyedwe jenumanja (m’Madina muno) tuchikopoka namwe kwene, soni ngasitun'jiitika jwalijose mpaka kalakala pa (yakunsausya) jenumanja, soni naga n'di mputidwe ngondo (ni Asilamu) tuchinkamuchisya kwene.” Nambo Allah akutendela umboni kuti chisimu ŵanganyao ŵaunami"
  59,12,"Mwanti naga ali akoposyedwe (Ayudao) nganaŵa akopweche nao imo (achinakunakuo), soni naga ali aputidwe ngondo nganaŵa ŵakamuchisye, soni mwanti ali atite ŵakamuchisye mpaka alosye kwene migongo (kutila), kaneka ni ngasakulupusyidwa"
  59,13,"Chisimu ŵanganyammwe (Asilamu) niŵan'di ŵakogopedwa nnope m’mitima mwao kupunda Allah, yalakweyo niligongo lyanti ŵanganyao niŵandu ŵangali chachimanyi"
  59,14,"Nganaŵa amputile ngondo (Ayudao atamose ali) wosope, ni ikaŵeje m’misi jegosedwe ni makome, kapena kusyeto kwa mapupa. Ngondo jao (ja utinda) chilikati chao jiŵele jekulungwa nnope, mpaka mwaganichisye kuti ali imo kutendaga mitima jao jelekangane, yalakweyo niligongo lyanti ŵanganyao niŵandu ŵangali lunda"
  59,15,"(Kaŵe ka Ayuda ŵalukosyo lwa Nadhîr) kali chisawu aŵala (Ayuda ŵalukosyo lwa Kainukai) ŵaŵalongolele ŵanganyao (kupata ilagasyo) pangakaŵapa, agapasisye makungu ga itendo yao, ni akwete soni kupata ŵanganyao ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope (ku Akhera)"
  59,16,"Chilandanyo cha achinakunaku pakwanyenga Ayuda ŵalukosyo lwa Nadhîr ya kumpitikuchila Muhammadi (ﷺ chili chisawu shetani ndema jaŵansalile mundu kuti: “Munkanani (Allah).” Basi ndema ja ŵakanile, (shetani) jwatite: “Chisimu une ndalikangene namwe, unetu ngun'jogopa Allah M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  59,17,"Basi ni jaliji mbesi ja ŵanaŵaŵiliŵa kuja kwinjila ku Moto ni kuŵa ŵandamo mwalakwemo, sano galakwego ni malipilo ga ŵakulitenda lupuso"
  59,18,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Mun'jogopani Allah, soni mundu jwalijose ayilole yaalongwesye ya malaŵi (ku Akhera), ni mun'jogopani Allah, chisimu Allah ni Nkusimanya chenene abali syosope sya yankutenda"
  59,19,"Ni ngasim'ba mpela aŵala ŵanya ŵan'diŵalile Allah, nombe Najo ni ŵaliŵeesye mitima jao. Ŵanganyao niŵali ŵakunyosya"
  59,20,"Ngaŵa nkulandana ŵandu ŵa ku Moto ni ŵandu ŵa ku Mbepo, ŵandu ŵa ku Mbepo ni ŵali ŵakupunda"
  59,21,"Ingaŵe kuti twajitulwisye aji Qur’aniji pachanya petumbi, chisimu nkaliweni lili lyakuteteŵala ni ganjika ligongo lya kun'jogopa Allah, yalakweyo ni ilandanyo ya tukupeleka kwa ŵandu kuti achetelele"
  59,22,"Jwalakwe ni Allah Ajula jwaali pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun'galagatila) ikaŵeje Jwelepejo, Jwakumanyilila yakusisika ni yakuonechela, Jwalakwe ni Jwaukoto wejinji, Jwachanasa channope"
  59,23,"Jwalakwe ni Allah Ajula jwali pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun'galagatila) ikaŵeje Jwelepejo, Nchimwene, Jwakuswejela, Nsyene ntendele, Nkupeleka ntunjelele, Nkung'unulila ni goosa chilichose (mu itendo ya achikapolo Ŵakwe), Jwamachili gakupunda, Nkuteteŵasya iwumbe Yakwe, Jwakulikusya kusyene. Aswejele Allah ku yaakum'bwanganya nayo"
  59,24,"Jwalakwe ni Allah, Nkugumba, Nkusipusya chilichose pandanda, Nkupaanga kaoneche ka chindu. Jukwete mena gambone nnope. Ikunswejesyaga Jwalakwe yosope yaili kumawunde ni petaka, soni Jwalakwe ni Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  60,1,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Ngasimwatenda amagongo Ŵangu ni amagongo ŵenu kuŵa isyoŵe ni kwatulilaga (abali syenu) mwachinonyelo, kutendaga pamasile paayikanile yakuona yaim’bichilile. Akunkoposya Ntenga ﷺ ni jenumanja ŵakwe (nsimangwenu) ligongo lyanti nkunkulupilila Allah M’mbuje gwenu. Nam'baga jenumanja nkopweche kuumenyana ngondo petala Lyangu ni kusachilila chinonyelo Changu (ngasimwatenda kuŵa isyoŵe yenu), nkwatumichisya asili (syenu syangondo) mwachinonyelo kutendaga Une nguimanyilila yansisile ni yannosisye (palangulangu)! Sano jwataitende yele mwa jenumanja nikuti amasile mwapotele kuleka litala lyagoloka"
  60,2,"Ali asimangene namwe (pangondo) akuŵaga amagongo ŵenu, soni akasan'jongolelaga makono gao ni ndimi syao mwakusakala (pakumputa ni kuntukana), ni akasasachililaga n'di nkufuulu (pakuleka Usilamu)"
  60,3,"Ngasaŵa ankamuchisye achalongo achin'jenu namuno ŵanache ŵenu lisiku lya Kiyama, (Allah) tachijilanya chilikati chenu, sano Allah ichindu yankutenda aŵele Jwakuilolechesya"
  60,4,"Pamasile paluŵele kukwenu lusyasyo lwambone pa Ibrahima ni aŵala ŵaŵaliji najo, ndema ja ŵasalile ŵandu ŵao kuti: “Chisimu uwwe tuŵambalene namwe kwisa soni ayila yankuŵa nkuigalagatila kunneka Allah, tunkanile ŵanganyammwe, soni uonechele chilikati chetuwe ni jenumanja utinda ni uŵengani wa mpaka kalakala mpaka nkankulupilile Allah Jikape.” (Nombe jenumanja umati wa Muhammadi ﷺ syasyani yele yagakana makafiliyo,) ikaŵeje maloŵe (gajwaŵechete) Ibrahima kwasalila babagwe (ŵaŵaliji kafili kuti): “Chisimu chene chinjim'bendela chikululuko, nambo nganingola chilichose chanti ni kun'gosela nacho kwa Allah.” (Yagaŵendela chikululuko makafiliyo nkasyasya, nambo n'jileje): “Ambuje ŵetu! Kukwenu pe tujeegamiile, soni Kukwenu pe tugalauchiile pakutenda toba, soni Kukwenu pe ni kwakuujila.”"
  60,5,"“Ambuje ŵetu! Ngasintuŵika uwwe pa kulingwa ni achimakafili (pakwakombolasya kutuwatanganyichisya chikulupi), soni tukululuchilani Ambuje ŵetu! Chisimu Mmwe niŵan'di Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵalunda lwakusokoka.”"
  60,6,"Chisimu pamasile paluŵele kukwenu pa jamanjao (Ibrahima ni umati wakwe), lusyasyo lwambone kwa mundu jwaali nkuŵichila ntima pa Allah ni lisiku lyambesi, nambo mundu jwatanyosye (yaalamwile Allah), basi chisimu Allah ni Jwakupata kwejinji, Jwakulapilidwa kusyesyene"
  60,7,"Mwine Allah kuŵa nkuŵika usyoŵe chilikati chaŵanganyammwe ni ŵane mwa aŵala ŵamwatesile kuŵa amagongo ŵenu (pa kwajongolela ku Usilamu), soni Allah ni Jwakombola kusyesyene, soni Allah ni Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope"
  60,8,"Allah ngaakunkanya ŵanganyammwe kwaatendela yaukoto ni yagoloka aŵala ŵanganamputa ngondo pa Dini soni nganankoposya nsimangwenu, chisimu Allah akwanonyela ŵagolosya (ichindu)"
  60,9,"Chisimu Allah akunkanya ŵanganyammwe kusyoŵekana nao aŵala ŵamputile ngondo pa Dini ni kunkoposya nsimangwenu, ni akamuchiisye pa yakoposyedwa kwenu, sano ŵatasyoŵekane nao ŵanganyao, basi ŵanyao ni ŵali ŵakulitenda lupuso"
  60,10,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Pati am’bichiiliile ŵakulupilila ŵachikongwe ŵakusama basi mwalingani (kuti nchimanye chikulupi chao), Allah ni Jwaakumanyilila nnope ya chikulupi chao. Sano naga n'di mwamanyi kuti ŵakulupilila, basi ngasimwauchisya ku makafili, nganaŵa ŵanyao (achimmasyeto) ŵakundisyidwa kwa ŵanganyao, nombenao (achimakafili) nganaŵa (achikunganya) ŵakundisyidwa kwa ŵanyao, nambo mwauchisyani (achimakafilio) yaŵatosile (pakwalomba achimmasyetowo), ni chikuŵe kwangali ulemwa kukwenu kwalomba (achimmasyetowo) pati mwapele mahari gao (namuno kuti ŵalesile achalume ŵao ŵachikafili ku Maaka), soni ngasinkanganichila malombela ni achimmasyeto ŵachikafili (ŵaŵasigele ku Maaka), ŵilasyani ya mwatosile (pakwalomba achimmasyeto ŵachikafilio), nombe nao (achimakafili) aŵilasye yaŵatosile (pakwalomba achimmasyeto ŵaaujitiche Usilamu). Wele ni ulamusi wa Allah, Jwalakwe akulamula chilikati chenu. Sano Allah ni Jwakumanyilila nnope, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  60,11,"Sano naga jwalijose mwa achiŵammakwenu ali antisile kuja kumakafili (ni m'bilasisye mahari genu nambo akanyisye), kaneka ni mpatile chipanje (cha makafilio chachaŵajilwe kwauchisya pa achiŵammakwao ŵaŵatisile kapena chinchipatile petala lyangondo), basi mwapani aŵala ŵaatisile achiŵammakwao yakulandana ni yaŵatosile (pakulombela). Soni mun'jogopani Allah Ajula jwankuŵa nkunkulupilila"
  60,12,"E mmwe Ntume ﷺ! Pati am’bichiiliile ŵakulupilila ŵachikongwe kuutaŵana namwe chilanga chanti; ngawwanganyaga Allah ni chilichose, soni ngajiŵaga, soni ngatendaga chigwagwa, soni ngaulagaga ŵanache ŵao, soni ngaikaga nao ukapanga-panga (unami) watausepeje chilikati chamakono gao ni ngongolo syao (kwakuli kwalambuchisya achiŵammakwao ŵanache ŵangaŵandika), soni ngannyosyaga pa ichindu yambone (yatimwalamuleje), basi taŵanani nao chilangacho, ni mwaŵendelani chikululuko kwa Allah, chisimu Allah ni Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope"
  60,13,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Ngasinsyoŵekana nao ŵandu ŵaŵatumbilile Allah, pamasile paakatile tama (jakupata malipilo gambone) ku Akhera (ligongo lya kusakasya nnope), yaatite pa kata tama (jakupata yambone iliyose) achimakafili ŵaali m’malembe"
  61,1,"Iŵele ili nkunswejesya Allah yosope yaili kumawunde ni yaili petaka, soni Jwalakwe ni Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  61,2,E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Ligongo chichi nkuŵechetaga yangankutendaga
  61,3,Ikunchimaga kwekulungwa nnope Allah yakuti m'becheteje yangankutendaga
  61,4,Chisimu Allah akwanonyela aŵala ŵaakumenyanaga ngondo petala Lyakwe ali chilili pansela nti chisawu ŵanganyao lipupa lyekamulane chenene
  61,5,"Soni (kumbuchilani) katema kajwaŵechete Musa ku ŵandu ŵakwe kuti: “E ŵandu ŵangu! Ligongo chichi nkuusausya, kutendaga nkumanyilila kusyene yanti une ni Ntenga jwa Allah kukwenu?” Basi ndema jaŵapombotele (kuleka litala lya Allah), Allah ŵajipombotesye mitima jao, sano Allah ngakwajongolaga ŵandu ŵakunyosya"
  61,6,"Soni (kumbuchilani) katema kajwaŵechete Isa mwanache jwa Maryam kuti: “E jenumanja ŵanache ŵa Israila! Chisimu une ni Ntenga jwa Allah kukwenu jungwitichisya yaili paujo pangu yakuumila mu Taurat, soni ni ngutagulila ya abali jakusengwasya ja Ntenga jwatachiika panyuma pangu lina lyakwe Ahmadu.” Nambo ndema jajwaichilile ni ilosyo yakuonechela papaswela, ŵatite: “Awu ni usaŵi ŵakuonechela.”"
  61,7,Ana soni nduni jwali jwalupuso nnope kumpunda mundu jwansepele Allah unami kutendaga jwalakwe ali nkuŵilanjidwa ku Usilamu? Sano Allah ngaakwajongolaga ŵandu ŵakulitenda lupuso
  61,8,"Akasasachililaga ali asimisye lilanguka lya Allah (Usilamu) ni ngamwa syao, sano Allah ni Jwakwanilisya lilanguka Lyakwe namuno achimakafili yachime"
  61,9,"Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwaatumisye Ntenga Jwakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) ni chongolo kwisa soni Dini jakuona kuti ajikwesye pachanya pa dini syosope, namuno ŵakuwanganya (Allah ni isanamu) yachime"
  61,10,E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Ana nammanyisye malonda gampaka gan'jokole ku ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope
  61,11,"Munkulupilileje Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ, soni mputeje ngondo petala lya Allah ni chipanje chenu ni mwachimisyene ŵakwe, yalakweyo ni yaili yambone kukwenu naga n'di ŵakumanyilila"
  61,12,"Tankululuchile sambi syenu ni kun'jinjisya ku Matimbe ga ku Mbepo gasikujilima cha pasi pakwe sulo, ni malo gambone nnope ku Matimbe Gandamo. Kwalakweko ni kupunda kwekulungwa nnope"
  61,13,"Ni (ukoto) wine wachiwwunonyele (chachili) chikamuchisyo chakuumila kwa Allah kwisa soni kuugula (Maaka) kwakuli pakuŵandika, ni mwatagulilani abali jakusengwasya ŵakulupilila"
  61,14,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Ŵaagaani ŵakamuchisya (pakwenesya Dini ja) Allah, mpela yajwatite kuŵecheta Isa mwanache jwa Maryam pakwawusya achinafunsi (ŵakwe kuti): “Ana akungamuchisya ŵangu niŵani kwa Allah?” Achinafunsi (ŵakwe) ŵatite: “Uwwe ni akukamuchisya (pakwenesya Dini ja) Allah.” Basi likuga line mu ŵanache ŵa Israila lyakulupilile, nambo likuga line lyakanile. Basi ni twaalimbangenye aŵala ŵaŵakulupilile pa amagongo ŵao ni ŵasyuchile kuŵa ŵapachanya"
  62,1,"Yosope yaili kumawunde ni yaili petaka ikunswejesyaga Allah, Nchimwene, Jwakuswejela, Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  62,2,"Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwaatumisye ku ŵangapakombola kulemba ni kuŵalanga (Ŵarabu) Ntenga ﷺ jwakuumila mu ŵanganyapeo jwaakuŵa nkwasoomela ma Ȃya Gakwe, ni kwaswejesyaga, ni kwajiganyaga soni Chitabu ni lunda lwakusokoka, kutendaga kala ŵaliji m’kusokonechela kwakuonechela"
  62,3,"Ni (antumiisye soni ku) ŵane mwa ŵanganyao ŵanganasimangane nao. Sano Jwalakwe (Allah) ni Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  62,4,"Walakweo niumbone wa Allah waakumpaga jwaakunsaka, sano Allah ni Nsyene umbone wekulungwa"
  62,5,"Chilandanyo cha aŵala (Ayuda) ŵana kupedwaga Taurat kaneka ni nganajitendela masengo, chili chisawu mbunda (bulu) jajikutwichila itabu yekulungwa-kulungwa (nambo ngali yakunkamuchisya). Kaje kusakala chilandanyo cha ŵandu aŵala ŵaakaaniile ma Ȃya ga Allah, Sano Allah ngaakwajongolaga ŵandu ŵakulitenda lupuso"
  62,6,"Jilani: “E jenumanja ŵan'di m'chiyuda! Nam'baga nkuliitwanjila yanti ŵanganyammwe ni asyoŵe ŵa Allah pangali ŵandu ŵane soni, basi chilajilani chiwa naga nkuŵecheta yakuona.”"
  62,7,"Nambo ngaachilajila ata panandi ligongo lya (yasambi) yagalongwesye makono gao, sano Allah ni jwaakwamanya chenene ŵakulitenda lupuso"
  62,8,"Jilani: “Chisimu chiwa chankuchitilacho mwannami tichimpatepe, kaneka ni tinchiuchisyidwa kwa (Allah) Jwakumanyilila yakusisika ni yakuonechela, basi ni tachintagulila ichindu yamwaliji nkupanganya.”"
  62,9,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Pati ukomedwe nsana wa Swala (ja Ijuma) Lisiku Lyaijuma basi kangamalani kuja kunkumbuchila Allah, soni lekani malonda, yalakweyo ni yaili yambone kukwenu naga n'di ŵakumanyilila"
  62,10,"Sano pati Swala (ja Ijuma) jimasile basi balalikanganani pa chilambo ni kupitaga nchisosa umbone wa Allah, soni munkumbuchileje Allah kwejinji kuti m'be ŵakupunda"
  62,11,"Soni pati agaweni malonda kapena yang'anda-ng'anda akuigungumuchila yalakweyo ni kunneka mmwe n'di chiimile. Jilani: “Ichindu yaili kwa Allah ni yambone nnope kupunda yang'anda-ng'anda kwisa soni malonda, sano Allah ni Jwambone nnope mwa akupeleka lisiki.”"
  63,1,"Pati am’bichiiliile achinakunaku akasatiji: “Tukutendela umboni yanti chisimu mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) Ntenga jwa Allah.” Sano Allah akumanyilila kuti chisimu mmwejo Ntenga Jwakwe, soni Allah akutendela umboni yanti chisimu achinakunaku ŵaunami kusyene"
  63,2,"Akutesile kulumbila kwao (kwaunami) kuŵa chakusiŵilila (itendo yao yangalumbana), basi ni ŵaasiŵilile (ŵandu) kwitala lya Allah; chisimu ŵanganyao iŵele yakusakala nnope yaaŵele nkupanganya"
  63,3,"Yalakweyo ligongo lyanti ŵanganyao ŵaakulupilile kaneka ni kanila, basi ni jaugalidwe mitima jao mwanti nganaŵa amanyilile (chilichose chakwajokola)"
  63,4,"Sano ndema jankwaonaga ikunsengwasyaga ilu yao, soni atite aŵechete nkasagatejelaga liwiwi maloŵe gao (ligongo lyakakolosye kao pakuŵecheta, nambo maloŵe gao gali gangali mate), ŵanganyao agambile kuŵa nti chisawu ipika yaijegamisyidwe (kwipupa, agambile kuŵa ilu-ilupe yangali lunda), akuganichisyaga n'gumilo uliose (mpela wakuŵilanjila ku ngondo) kuti ukwamba ŵanganyao (ligongo lya woga), ŵanganyao ni amagongo, mwakalamukani, pamasile pa ŵalwesile Allah! Ana akugalausyidwa chinauli (kuleka yakuona ni kulupilila unami)"
  63,5,"Soni pati iŵechetedwe kukwao (yanti): “Ikanganani kuti am'bendele chikululuko Ntenga jwa Allah,” akasapombotasyaga mitwe jao, soni mpaka mwaone achisyululaga aku ali nkulikwesya"
  63,6,"Yalumope kwa jamanjao, mwaŵendele chikululuko kapena nkaŵendela, Allah nganaŵa ŵakululuchile. Chisimu Allah jwangaŵa nkwajongola ŵandu ŵakunyosya"
  63,7,"Jamanjao ni aŵala ŵaakutiji (pa kwasalila Answari): “Ngasintola (chipanje chenu) kwapa aŵala (Akusama) ŵali kwa Ntenga jwa Allahﷺmpaka atimbuche.” Kutendaga Allah ni Nsyene imatiilo (yosope ya ipanje) ya kumawunde ni petaka, nambo kuti achinakunaku ngakupata kumanyilila kusyesyene"
  63,8,"Akutiji: “Naga tuujile ku Madina, chisimu jwakuchimbichika nnope (achambaga Abdullah bin Ubayi bin Salulu nnongola jwa achinakunaku), chaakankoposye mwalakwemo jwakunyosyeka nnope (achambaga Muhammadi ﷺ).” Kutendaga Allah ni Nsyene uchimbichimbi, kwisa soni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ ni ŵakulupilila, nambo kuti achinakunaku ngakumanyilila"
  63,9,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Ikalluyaluya ipanje yenu ni ŵanache ŵenu kwakuleka kunkumbuchila Allah, sano ŵachaiche mwakutenda yele, basi ŵanganyao niŵataŵe ŵakwasika"
  63,10,"Soni tolani mu ichindu yatumpele nkanichim’bichilile jumo jwenu chiwa, ni kwisa kuŵecheta (mwakudandaula kuti): “Ambuje ŵangu! Uli nganjelewasya kandaŵi kannono kuti ndole sadaka ni mbe mu ŵandu ŵambone!”"
  63,11,"Sano Allah nganaŵa auchelewasisye ntima uliose pati jiiche ndema jakwe (jakuwila), soni Allah ni Nkusimanya chenene abali syosope sya yankutenda"
  64,1,"Yosope yaili kumawunde ni yaili petaka ikunswejesyaga Allah, uchimwene wosope wene ni Wakwe soni lumbili losope lwene ni Lwakwe, soni Jwalakwe pa chindu chilichose aŵele Jwakombola"
  64,2,"Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwaŵan'gumbile ŵanganyammwe, basi ŵane mwa jenumanja makafili, ŵane mwa jenumanja soni ŵakulupilila, sano Allah ichindu yankutenda aŵele Jwakuilolechesya"
  64,3,"Agumbile mawunde ni mataka mwakuonaonape, ni ampaanjiile kaoneche kenu, basi ni akakolosyisye kaoneche kenuko, soni Kukwakwe pe ni kwakuujila"
  64,4,"Akumanyilila yaili ku mawunde ni petaka, ni akuimanyilila soni yankuisisa ni yankuijuwula, soni Allah ni Nkuimanya chenene yaili m’mitima"
  64,5,"Ana nganijinyyika ŵanganyammwe abali jaaŵala ŵaŵakanile kalakala? Basi ŵapasyisye makungu ga itendo yao (ya ukafili pa duniya pepano), ni akwete kupata soni ŵanganyao ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope (ku Akhera)"
  64,6,"Yalakweyo niligongo lyanti Achimitenga ŵaliji nkwaichilila ni ilosyo yakuonechela, basi niŵatiji (pakuŵecheta mwachalu): “Ana ŵandu (mpela uwwewe) ni mpaka atujongole?” Basi ŵakanile ni kusyulula, nambo Allah nganaŵa pausauchi (wakulajila chikulupi chao), soni Allah ni Jwakupata kwejinji, Jwakulapilidwa kusyesyene"
  64,7,"Ŵandu ŵaakanile akulitwanjilaga yanti ngasaukulidwa (m’malembe). Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Elo! Ngwalumbila Ambuje ŵangu! Chisimu chene chinchiukulidwa, kaneka nikwisa kusalilidwa kwene yamwaliji nkutenda (ku duniya), soni yalakweyo kwa Allah iŵele yakwepepala kusyene.”"
  64,8,Basi munkulupililani Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ kwisa soni Lilanguka lyatutulwisye (Qur’an). Sano Allah abali syosope sya yankutenda aŵele Jwaasimanya chenene
  64,9,"(Kumbuchilani) lyuŵa lya tachinsonganganya pa Lisiku Lyansongano, lyele ni Lisiku lya kalamusyana (ŵandu ŵa ku Mbepo chakakalamusye ŵa ku Moto majumba gao gaakajile kwinjila akakulupilile). Sano jwachankulupilile Allah ni kutendaga yambone tansiimaachisye ilemwa yakwe, soni takan'jinjisye ku Matimbe ga ku Mbepo gasikujilima cha pasi pakwe sulo, chakaŵe ŵandamo mwalakwemo kwa yaka ni yaka. Kwele ni kupunda kwekulungwa nnope"
  64,10,"Nambo ŵandu ŵakufuulu ni kanila ma Ȃya Getu ŵanganyao niŵandu ŵa ku Moto, takaŵe ŵandamo mwalakwemo, kaje kusakala nnope malo gakuujila gakwe"
  64,11,"Nganichipatikaneje chipato chilichose ikaŵeje mu lisosa lya Allah, sano jwachankulupilile Allah tan'jongolele ntima wakwe (ku chikulupi chanti: yaimpatileyo yaliji yelembedwe kala ni Allah kuti impate), sano Allah chindu chilichose aŵele Jwaachimanya chenene"
  64,12,"Soni mumpikanilani Allah ni mumpikanile soni Ntenga ﷺ, nambo naga nkugalauka (kuleka yele), basi masengo ga Ntenga Jwetuﷺni kulungusya (utenga) mwakupikanika"
  64,13,"Allah pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun'galagatila) ikaŵeje Jwelepejo, soni basi kwa Allah pe ajegamile ŵakulupilila"
  64,14,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Chisimu ŵane mwa achiŵammakwenu ni ŵanache ŵenu ali amagongo ŵenu (ligongo akunnuyaluyaga mpaka kuleka ya Dini), basi mwakalamukani, nambo naga nkwakululuchila, ni kuipwanyila (yayapite) ni kuisiimaasya (kwene m’mitima mwenu Allah tasengwe), basi chisimu Allah ni Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope"
  64,15,"Chisimu ipanje yenu ni ŵanache ŵenu iŵele mayeso (gakun'dinga chikulupi chenu), sano Allah Kukwakwe nikwagali malipilo gamakulungwa nnope"
  64,16,"Basi mun'jogopani Allah mwachinkombolele, soni pikanilani (malamusi) ni nkunde (yankusalilidwa), soni tolani; chiiŵe yambone kukwenu mwachimisyene. Sano ŵaakuŵambasyidwa ku ubaili wa ntima wao, basi ŵanganyao ni ŵali ŵakupunda"
  64,17,"Naga nkunkongosya Allah ngongole jambone (pakutola ipanje yenu petala Lyakwe) tajijonjechesye kukwenu (malipilo gakwe) ni kunkululuchila (ilemwa yenu), sano Allah ni Jwakutogolela kusyene (pakulipila yejinji ku itendo yannono), Mpole nnope"
  64,18,"Jwakumanyilila yakusisika ni yakuonechela, Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  65,1,"E mmwe Ntume ﷺ! Pati nchalekaga achakongwe (ulombela), basi mwalekani pa eda jao (jajili ndema jakwembecheya panyuma pakulechedwa ulombela, jajikutandila ŵakongwe ali aswejele ku wesi nikwalekaga nkanimwakwaye), soni ŵalanjilani ya (masiku ga) eda. Ni mun'jogopeje Allah M'mbuje gwenu. Nkasimwakoposya m’majumba mwao, nombenao soni akasakopoka (achimisyenepe kwikanila ndema ja eda jili jimasile), ikaŵeje naga ali atesile chakusakala chakuonechela (mpela chigwagwa, apo chinkomboleche kwakoposya). Sano jele ni mipingu ja Allah, mwanti jwataguluche mipingu ja Allah nikuti pamasile paalitendele lupuso nsyene. Ngankumanyilila (chaaŵiichiile Allah jele mipinguji), mwine Allah kuŵa nkuchipatikanisya chindu chine panyuma payele (yakulekanayo chakwilanya chilikati chenu, nikuujilana eda nkanijimale)"
  65,2,"Basi pati jiŵandichile ndema jao (jakumalila eda) mwaujilani mwaumbone, kapena lekanganani nao mwaumbone, soni soselani mboni siŵili syakulungamika syakutyochela mwa jenumanja (Asilamu).Ni mpelecheje umboni chenene ligongo lya Allah. Yalakweyo akuundidwa nayo mundu jwaaŵele ali nkunkulupilila Allah ni Lisiku Lyambesi. Sano mundu jwatan'jogope Allah tam'bichile litala lyakopochela (mu ipato)"
  65,3,"Soni tampe lisiki m’matala gangaakuganichisya, soni jwatajegamile kwa Allah, basi Jwalakwe tankwanile (kuŵa nkunkamuchisya jwakwe), chisimu Allah ni Jwakwanilisya chisako Chakwe, Allah pamasile paaŵisile chipiimo cha chindu chilichose"
  65,4,"Sano aŵala ŵaakatile tama jakulwala wesi mwa achimmasyeto ŵenu naga nkukaichila (ya ndema jao ja eda), basi eda jao ni myesi jitatu, ni aŵala ŵanganatande kulwala wesi (eda jao iyyoyo soni). Sano aŵala ŵaakwete yiilu ndema jao (ja kumalila eda) ni muchachiŵelechela yiilu yaoyo. Sano mundu jwatan'jogope Allah tan'jepepachisye ichindu yakwe"
  65,5,"Lyele ni lilamusi lya Allah lyaalitulwisye kukwenu, sano jwatan'jogope Allah tansiimaachisye yakusakala yakwe ni kunkuchisya malipilo gakwe"
  65,6,"Mwatamikani (achimmasyeto ŵamwalesileo) mwankutama pemo, yankuti pakulipatila (namuno kuti mwalesile ulombela naga eda jao nkanijimale), soni nkasimwalagasya ŵanganyao kuti mwaaŵane (niaganisye yakutila achimisyene). Soni naaŵaga ŵana yiilu basi mwapani (yosope yakusosekwa pa umi) mpaka aŵeleche yiilu yaoyo. Sano naga ali an'jonjecheesye (ŵanache ŵenu), basi mwapani malipilo gao, soni tamani ntemela wakupikanganana (ya malipilogo) chilikati chenu mwaumbone. Nambo naga nkunonopesyana basi (mwanachejo) tiŵajonjechesye (babao ŵakongwe) ŵane"
  65,7,"Jwakupata atole mwakulandana ni kupata kwakwe, nambo jwaanaandiyisyiidwe lisiki lyakwe, basi atole (kachinandipamuno) mu yampele Allah, Allah jwangankanganika mundu (kutola) ikaŵeje yampeele, Allah taaŵiiche kwepepala panyuma pakunonopa"
  65,8,"Ana soni ŵalingwa-ŵalingwa mwa achimisyene misi ŵaŵanyosyisye lilamusi lya Ambuje ŵao kwisa soni Achimitenga Ŵakwe! Basi ni twaŵalasile chiŵalanjilo chaukali nnope, ni twapele ilagasyo yakunyalaya kusyene"
  65,9,"Basi ni ŵapasisye makungu ga itendo yao, soni kupelelwa ni jaliji mbesi ja itendo yao"
  65,10,"Allah ŵaalinganyichisye ŵanganyao ilagasyo yaukali nnope, basi mun'jogopani Allah, E jenumanja ŵankwete lunda! Aŵala ŵankulupilile! Pamasile paatulwisye Allah kukwenu Chikumbusyo"
  65,11,"Ntenga ﷺ jwaakunsoomela ma Ȃya ga Allah gakusalichisya, kuti ŵakoposye aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone kutyochela m’chipi ni kwajinjisya mwilanguka. Sano jwatankulupilile Allah ni kutendaga yambone takan'jinjisye ku Matimbe ga ku Mbepo gasikujilima cha pasi pakwe sulo, chakaŵe ŵandamo mwalakwemo kwa yaka ni yaka, Allah pamasile pankolochesye jwalakwejo lisiki lyambone nnope"
  65,12,"Allah ni Ajula jwaagumbile mawunde nsano nagaŵili, nombe nalyo litaka yalumope (mataka nsano nagaŵili). Malamusi gakuŵa gali nkutuluka chilikati chakwe (cha mawunde ni mataka) kuti mmanyilile ŵanganyammwe yanti Allah pa chindu chilichose aŵele Jwakombola kusyene, ni yanti Allah amasile paachisyungwile chindu chilichose ni umanyilisi (waachimanya chenene)"
  66,1,"E mmwe Ntume ﷺ! Ligongo chichi nkuchitenda kuŵa haraam chindu chaachitesile Allah kuŵa halaal kukwenu? Nkusachilila kwasengwasya achiŵammakwenu (ni ligongo lyakwe ntesile yalakweyi)? Sano Allah ni Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope"
  66,2,"Allah pamasile pam'biichiile ŵanganyammwe lilamusi lya kagopole ka kulumbila kwenu, soni Allah ni Akun'gosa ŵenu, soni Jwalakwe ni Jwakumanyilila nnope, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  66,3,"Soni (kumbuchilani) katema kajwasunjisye ngani Ntume ﷺ kwa ŵamo mwa achiŵammakwakwe (Hafswa رضي الله عنهم), basi ndema ja ŵaajijuwile (asilijo kwa Aisha رضي الله عنهم), Allah ni kummanyisya (Ntume ﷺ) yalakweyo, (Ntume ﷺ) jwatagulile (Hafswa رضي الله عنهم) upande wine wanganijo nambo upande wine jwaulesile, basi ndema jajwatagulile yalakweyo (Hafswa رضي الله عنهم) ŵatite: “Ŵani ŵantagulile yele?” (Ntume ﷺ) jwatite: “Andagulile (Allah) Jwakumanyilila nnope, Jwaasimanya abali syosope.”"
  66,4,"Naga ŵanaŵaŵilimmwe (Hafswa ni Aisha رضي الله عنهم) ntende toba kwa Allah (pakuleka kunnagasya Ntume ﷺ ni wiwu basi tiiŵe yambone kukwenu, soni tendani chitema) ligongo mitima jenu jipombotele panandi (kusaka kunkanila Ntume ﷺ yajukusaka), nambo naga nkamusyangane pa yakunnagasya Ntumejo r, basi Allah chisimu chene ni Nkunchengeta jwakwe, kwisa soni Jibulilu ni ŵali ŵambone mu (ŵandu) ŵakulupilila, ni Achimalaika konjechesya pele tankamuchisye"
  66,5,"Naga (Ntume ﷺ) ali annesile jenumanja (ulombela), chisimu Ambujegwe mpaka ampe mmalo mwa jenumanja achiŵammakwakwe ŵane ŵambone nnope kumpunda ŵanganyammwe, Asilamu (ŵakulipeleka kwa Allah), ŵakulupilila, ŵakunda malamusi mwakulinandiya, ŵakutenda toba, ŵakutenda ibada nnope, ŵakutaŵataŵa (swaumu), mauli ni ŵali ŵakwe"
  66,6,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Lichingani mwachimisyene kwisa soni maŵasa genu ku Moto wauli sasu syakwe ŵandu ni maganga, pa walakweo pana Achimalaika (ŵakuulolela) ŵakalalisya, ŵamachili, ŵangannyosya Allah pa yaŵalamwile, soni akasatenda (yosope) yaakulamulidwaga"
  66,7,"E jenumanja achimakafili! Ngasin'diŵalanga lelo, chisimu nkulipidwa pa yamwaliji nkupanganya"
  66,8,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Galauchilaani kwa Allah pakutenda toba jisyesyene, chisimu M'mbuje gwenu tansiimaachisye yakusakala yenu, ni kuja kun'jinjisya ku Matimbe ga ku Mbepo gasikujilima cha pasi pakwe sulo, Lisiku lyangan'jigasya Allah nchesela Ntume (Muhammadi ﷺ) ni ŵandu ŵaŵakulupilile najo imo. Lilanguka lyao lichiŵaga nkwenda paujo pao ni kunkono wao wan'dyo, achiŵechetaga (kuti): “Ambuje ŵetu! Tukwanilichisyani lilanguka lyetu, soni ntukululuchile. Chisimu Mmwejo pa chindu chilichose m'bele Ŵakombola.”"
  66,9,"E mmwe Ntume ﷺ! Limbanani nao achimakafili ni achinakunaku, ni mwajumulile ntima, mauto gao ni ku Jahannama, kaje kusakala malo gakuujila gakwe"
  66,10,"Allah apeleeche chilandanyo chaŵandu makafili pa ŵankwao Nuhu ni ŵankwao Lutwi, ŵanaŵaŵiliŵa ŵaliji pasi pa achikapolo ŵaŵili mwa achikapolo Ŵetu ŵambone, nambo ŵaatesile chinyengo (achiŵammakwaowo pakusisa ukafili mu ntima ni kamulana ni amagongo), basi (Achimitumeo) nganiŵakamuchisya (achiŵammakwaowo) chilichose mu (ipotesi) yakuumila kwa Allah, ni yaŵechetedwe (yanti): “Jinjilani ku Moto pamo ni akwinjila.”"
  66,11,"Ni apeleeche soni Allah chilandanyo cha ŵandu ŵakulupilila pa ŵankwakwe Firiauna ndema jaŵatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Mundaŵilani Kukwenu nyumba ku Mbepo, ni munjokole kwa Firiauna kwisa soni itendo yakwe, ni munjokole ku ŵandu ŵalupuso.”"
  66,12,"Ni Maryam mwanache jwa Imrani ajula juŵaugosile utukani wakwe, ni twapepelele mwalakwemo (umi) kuumila kwa Nsimu Wetu (Jibulilu ni kupagwa Isa jwangali babagwe), ni jwajitichisye (Maryamujo) maloŵe ga M'mbujegwe ni itabu Yakwe, ni jwaliji soni mu ŵakunda malamusi mwakulinandiya"
  67,1,"Anyakwiche (pa uchimbichimbi ni upile) Ajula (Allah) jwauli mu Nkono Mwakwe uchimwene, soni Jwalakwe pa chindu chilichose aŵele Jwakombola"
  67,2,"Ajula jwaagumbile chiwa ni umi kuti an'dinje (yanti) ana ŵani mwa jenumanja ŵali ŵakolosya kusyene masengo. Soni Jwalakwe ni Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwakululuka kusyene"
  67,3,"Ajula jwaagumbile mawunde nsano nagaŵili mwakusajikanya (line pachanya pa lijakwe, natamuno nnole kwinaniko) ngankuona kutindana kulikose mu kagumbe ka (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji, basi wilisyani kulola, ana nkujiona midala jilijose"
  67,4,"Soni wilisyani kulola kaŵilikose, chikum'bujile mwasyene kulolako (meso gali) nkuchenga soni galakwe gali pambesi pakupela (nambo so! Nganim'ba nchiweni chilema chilichose)"
  67,5,"Soni chisimu chene pamasile patulisalalisye liwunde lya duniya ni nyali (ndondwa), ni tusitesile kuŵa (mwakuumila yenje) yagasomela mashetani. Soni twalinganyichisye ŵangayao ilagasyo ya Moto Wakulapuka"
  67,6,"Soni akwete kupata ŵandu ŵankanile M'mbuje gwao ilagasyo ya Jahannama, kaje kusakala nnope malo gakuujila gakwe"
  67,7,Ndema jatachiponyedwa mwalakwemo tachikupikana kulilima kwakwe soni aku uli nkutokota kusyene
  67,8,"Ukusigalaga panandi kuti ukatichekatiche ligongo lya ukali. Ndema jilijose jalikaponyedweje mwalakwemo likuga (lya achimakafili), chaakaawusyeje akuwusunga (Motowo ŵali Achimalaika kuti): “Ana nganam’bichilila nkutetela?”"
  67,9,"Takajanjeje (kuti): “Elo, chisimu jwatuichilile nkutetela, nambo twakaaniile, ni twatite: ‘Allah nganatumisya chilichose, nganim'batu jenumanja ikaŵeje mu kupotela kwekulungwa.”"
  67,10,"Soni takajileje: “Tungaŵe twapikanile (yaŵatusalilaga ila) kapena kuiganichisya mwalunda, nga nganituŵa mu ŵandu ŵa ku Moto Wakulapuka.”"
  67,11,"Basi takajitichisye ileŵi yao (nambo kwitichisyako ngakuja kwakamuchisya), mwanti kutalichila nikwao ŵandu ŵa ku Moto Wakulapuka (kutyochela ku chanasa cha Allah)"
  67,12,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaakun’jogopa M’mbuje gwao akakum’bona, akwete kupata chikululuko ni malipilo gekulungwa"
  67,13,"Soni (kanga) chin'gasise maloŵe genu (gakun'gaamba Muhammadi ﷺ) kapena chin'galochesye papaswela (yalumope), chisimu Jwalakwe (Allah) ni Nkumanyilila yayili m’mitima"
  67,14,"Ana jukamanyilila Jwagumbile? Kutendaga Jwalakwe ni Jwakumanyilila yakunyilila nnope, Jwaasimanya abali syosope"
  67,15,"Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwam'biichiile litaka kuŵa lyakutumika (pa chilichose chankusaka, mpela kwendajenda, kulima ni kutaŵapo yakutaŵataŵa), basi jendani mbali ni mbali syetakalyo soni lyagani mu lisiki Lyakwe (Allah), soni Kukwakwe pe ni kwakuujila (kwenu pa Kiyama)"
  67,16,"Ana nkuiona kuti n'di pantunjelele mwanti (Allah) Jwaali kwinani ngaŵa nkuntitimisya nalyo litaka, basi nikuŵa lyalakwelyo lina nkutenganyika (pakuwowochelwa)"
  67,17,Kapena nkuiona kuti n'di pantunjelele mwanti (Allah) Jwaali kwinani ngaŵa nkuntumichisya chimbunga chasakalawe (nikun'jonanga nasyo sakalawesyo)? Basi ni tinchimanyilila mwachikasaŵelaga chitetelo Changu
  67,18,"Soni yakuonaonape pamasile paŵaakaaniile aŵala ŵapaujo pao, nambi kwaliji uli kasilika Kwangu (ngati najonasile wosope)"
  67,19,"Ana ngaakuiona ijuni pachanya pao mwaikusapangulila mapapiko ni kugapinda? Pangali jwaakuijangata ikaŵeje (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji, chisimu Jwalakwe pa chindu chilichose aŵele Jwakulolechesya"
  67,20,Kapena niŵani aŵala ŵali asilikali ŵenu ŵanti ni kunkulupusya pangaŵaga (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji? Nganaŵatu achimakafili ikaŵeje ali mu kunyenjeka basi
  67,21,Kapena niŵani aŵala ŵampaka ampe lisiki naga Jwalakwe (Allah) ali aumbete lisiki Lyakwe? Nambo ŵanganyao akwendelechela kulikwesya ni kuitila (yakuona)
  67,22,"Ana mundu jwaakwenda chiinamile (akakulola m'bujo jwanti komboleka kugwa) chamakuku ni jwali jwakongoka, kapena mundu jwaakwenda chongochele petala lyagoloka"
  67,23,"Jilani: “Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwaŵan'gumbile (nkakupatikana kalakose), ni ŵam'biichiile kupikana, kulola ni mitima (jaganichisya). Nambo kutogolela kwenu kuŵele kwannonope.”"
  67,24,"Jilani: “Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwan'jenesye petaka, soni Kukwakwe ni kutinchisonganganyisidwa.”"
  67,25,"(Achimakafili) niakutiji: “Ana nichakachi (chatichikwanilana) chele chilanga (cha Kiyamachi) nam'baga jenumanja nkuŵecheta yakuona?”"
  67,26,"Jilani: “Umanyilisi (wa yele) uli kwa Allah pe, sano une ngambile kuŵa nkutetela jwakusalichisya.”"
  67,27,"Nambo ndema jatakachione (chilanga cha Kiyamacho) chili dusi (ni ŵanganyao), ngope sya aŵala ŵaŵakanile sichipiilila ni kalaluka (ligongo lya madandausi). Ni kuchiŵechetedwa (mwa kwachindimbula kuti): “Ayi niayilayila yamwaliji nkuiŵilasya (kuti iyiche, sano ni iyiiche).”"
  67,28,"Jilani: “Ana nkuiona uli, naga Allah ali anjonasile une pamo ni aŵala ŵandinao (mwankusachila ŵanganyammwe), kapena kututendela chanasa, ana ni ŵani ŵampaka agajokole makafili ku ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope?”"
  67,29,"Jilani: “Jwalakwe ni (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji, tunkulupilile Jwele, soni kwa Jwalakwe pe ni kutujeegamiile. Basi tinchimanyilila (panyuma pakwika ilagasyo kuti) nduni jwali m’kupotela kwakuonechela.”"
  67,30,"Jilani: “Ana nkuiona uli, naga mesi genu (gosope) gali gajumilile, ana ni ŵani ŵampaka ayiche nago kukwenu mesi gatutumule?”"
  68,1,Nûn. Nguchilumbila chakulembela (chaakuleembelaga Achimalaika ni ŵane wosope) kwisa soni yaakulembaga
  68,2,"Mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) nganim'ba ŵamasoka pachindimba cha Ambuje ŵenu (champele, wauli utume)"
  68,3,Soni chisimu nkwete kupata mmwejo malipilo gangamala (ligongo lya kulagasika kwenu pakwenesya utenga)
  68,4,Soni chisimu mmwe n'di pachanya pandamo jambone nnope
  68,5,"Basi, sampano tinyyione, nombe nao soni taione"
  68,6,Yanti ana ŵani mwa jenumanja ŵagaapatile masoka? (Mmwejo kapena ŵanganyao)
  68,7,"Chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵaakummanyilila chenene mundu jwaapoteele kuleka litala Lyakwe, soni Ŵalakweo ni ŵaakwamanyilila chenene ŵali ŵakongoka"
  68,8,Basi ngasimwapikanila ŵakanila
  68,9,"Akasasachililaga n'di mwaakundilile (pa yakusakala), basi nombe nao ni ankundilile (pa yambone)"
  68,10,Soni ngasimumpikanila jwalijose jwakulumbila-lumbila soni jwakwaluka
  68,11,"Nkusogoda, jwakwendajenda kupita nchitenda unakunaku"
  68,12,"Jwakusiŵilila yambone, jwakusumba mpika, jwasambi syejinji"
  68,13,Jwakumula ntima soni panyuma pa yele jwakulipakasya utundu wa ŵane
  68,14,(Akulikwesya) ligongo lyakuŵa jwana chipanje ni ŵanache
  68,15,"Pati gachisoomedwaga kukwakwe ma Ȃya Getu jukasatiji: “Asi ni adisiadisi sya ŵandu ŵandanda.”"
  68,16,Chiitum'biika chimanyilo palupula
  68,17,"Chisimu Uwwe twalinjile (achimakafili ŵachikuraishio pakwapa chindimba ni kuchikana) yatwatite pakwalinga achinsyene n'gunda, ndema jaŵalumbile kuti takaugungule (isogosi yakwe) kumasikusiku (kuti ŵakulaga akaaona atakwika muŵaŵendile)"
  68,18,Ni nganaŵecheta maloŵe ganti “Nasakaga Allah.”
  68,19,Nilyaawusyungwile (n'gundao) likungu lyakuumila kwa Ambuje ŵenu kutendaga ŵanganyao ali nnugono
  68,20,Basi niwachelelwe uli nti chisawu wegungule
  68,21,Basi ni ŵaŵilangene kumasikusiku
  68,22,“Laŵililani kun'gunda wenu naga nkusaka gungula.”
  68,23,Basi ni ŵaŵigwile aku achisongonelanaga
  68,24,“Akasan'jinjilila ata panandi kwalakweko lelo masikini jwalijose.”
  68,25,Ni ŵalaŵilile mwachisindo achiganichisyaga kuti apakombwele (kwasiŵilila masikinio)
  68,26,"Basi ndema jaŵauweni (n'gundao) ŵatite: “Chisimu uwe tusokonechele.”"
  68,27,"(Niŵatite soni: “Ngwamba, niwwuwu) nambo kuti uwwe tujiimiidwe.”"
  68,28,"Jwakulungamika chilikati chao jwatite: “Ana nganinansalila yanti: ‘Ana uli ngankunswejesya (Allah pakuŵecheta maloŵe ganti: Naga Allah akusaka chitukagungule)?”"
  68,29,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Aswejeele Ambuje ŵetu! Chisimu uwwe twaliji ŵakulitenda lupuso (pangankumbuchila Allah).”"
  68,30,Basi ni ŵalolegene aku achidandaulanaga (pakupulisyana yaagajima masikini)
  68,31,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Kutapana kwetuwe! Chisimu uwwe twaliji ŵakusumba mpika (paganisya yagajima masikini).”"
  68,32,"“Mwine Ambuje ŵetu kuŵa nkututindanyichisya ni (n'gunda) wambone nnope kupunda walakweu, chisimu uwwe kwa Ambuje ŵetu tukusachilila (chikululuko Chakwe).”"
  68,33,"Mwele ni mwaikasaŵelaga ilagasyo (ya pa duniya), nambo ilagasyo ya ku Akhera ni yaikulungwa nnope ingaŵe ŵamanyililaga"
  68,34,Chisimu ŵakun'jogopa Allah akwete kupata kwa Ambuje ŵao Matimbe Gachindimba (Mbepo)
  68,35,Ana twatende Asilamu nti chisawu akuleeŵa (pakwalipila mwakulandana)
  68,36,Chipali chichi kukwenu! Ana nkwiilanya chinauli
  68,37,Kapena nkwete chitabu chankusoomaga nkati mwakwe
  68,38,Yanti chisimu nkwete kupata mu lyele (lisiku lya Kiyamalyo) yankuisaka
  68,39,"Kapena nkwete ŵanganyammwe ilanga Kukwetu yakuja kwika mpaka lisiku lya Kiyama, yakuti chisimu ŵanganyammwe chinchipata yankulijiilanyichisya"
  68,40,Mwawusyani kuti ŵani mwa ŵanganyao ŵali nnongola jwatachajimila pa yalakweyi
  68,41,Kapena akwete ŵanganyao ŵakamusyangana nao? Basi ayiche naotu ŵakamusyangana naowo naga akuŵecheta yakuona
  68,42,(Kumbuchilani) lisiku lya luchiunukulidwa Lusonjo (lwa Allah) ni tachiŵilanjidwa (achinakunaku) kuti atende sijida (kunsujudila Allah) nambo ngasakombola
  68,43,"Meso gao gachiteteŵala, ni kuchaunichila kunyosyeka. Nambo posepo ŵaliji nkuŵilanjidwa kuti asujudu (kuswali) ali ŵambonembonepe (ku duniya)"
  68,44,"Basi munekani ni akukanila aji abaliji, chitwajigale mbolembole (wa ku ipotesi) kupitila m’matala gangaakugamanyilila"
  68,45,"Soni ngamba kwalechelesya ŵanganyao, chisimu mpango Wangu uŵele wakulimbangana"
  68,46,"Kapena nkwajuga malipilo (pakulungusya utenga), mwanti ŵanganyao ni akusitopelwa nasyo ngongole"
  68,47,"Kapena akwete (chitabu) chakusisika, mwanti ŵanganyao niakulemba"
  68,48,"Basi pilililani ku ulamusi wa Ambuje ŵenu (wakwalechelesya achimakafili), mwanti ngasim'ba mpela nsyene somba (Yunusu pakwanguya kwakasilichila ŵandu ŵakwe), ndema jajwaŵilasile (Ambujegwe) juli jwakutaŵika ni madandausi"
  68,49,Ukaŵa kunsimana ukoto wakuumila kwa M’mbujegwe jukaponyedwe pantetete juli jwanchesela
  68,50,Basi Ambujegwe ŵansagwile ni kuntenda kuŵa jumpepe mwa ŵandu ŵambone
  68,51,"Soni chisimu aŵala ŵakufuulu akusigalaga panandi kuti antelesyasye ni meso gao (ligongo lya kunchima) ndema jaakuchipikana chikumbusyo (Qur’an), ni akutiji: “Chisimu jwalakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) jwamasoka.”"
  68,52,Ni nganijiŵa jalakwe (Qur’aniji) ikaŵeje chikumbusyo ku iumbe yosope
  69,1,Chakusimichika (kwika kwakwe)
  69,2,Ana chakusimichika (kwika kwakwe) nichichi
  69,3,Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya chakusimichika (kwika kwakwe)? (Jeletu ni Kiyama)
  69,4,Ŵanya Asamuda ni Adi ŵakaaniile ya chagunda ntima (Kiyama)
  69,5,Mwanti ŵanya Asamuda ŵajonanjidwe ni n'gumilo wakupelenganya nnope
  69,6,Sano ŵanya Adi ni ŵajonanjidwe ni mbungo jakusisima nnope soni jamachili gakupelenganya
  69,7,"(Allah) ŵajitumisye kukwao yilo nsano naiŵili ni muusi nsano nautatu mwakulundanya, mwanti nkaweni ŵandu mwalakwemo ali jajaja! Nti chisawu mapata ga itela yatende gangali chachipali nkati mwakwe"
  69,8,Nambi kwali nkum'bona mwa ŵanganyao jwalijose jwasigele
  69,9,Nombe Afiriauna kwisa soni ŵandu ŵa paujo pakwe ni achinsyene misi jajapitikusyidwe (ŵandu ŵa Lutwi) ŵayiche ni ilemwa
  69,10,"Sano (ŵaliose mwa ŵanganyao) ŵannyosyisye Ntenga jwa M’mbuje gwao, basi (Allah) ni jwaakwembekenye ni ilagasyo yakupelenganya nnope"
  69,11,"Chisimu Uwwe ndema jagaagumbalile mesi (pachigumula cha Nuhu), twankwesisye ŵanganyammwe m’chombo chakwenda (mwakujajaŵala)"
  69,12,"Kuti tuchitende kuŵa chikumbusyo kukwenu, ni kuti lijisunje (jele abaliji) liwiwi lyakupikanichisya"
  69,13,Basi pandema jalichigombedwa lipenga n'gombo umpepe
  69,14,Nombe litaka ni matumbi ni kutyosyedwa m’mangwakwe kaneka ni kusyajidwa nsyago umo
  69,15,Basi lyele lisikulyo chichipatikana chakupatikana (Kiyama)
  69,16,"Ni lichipapuka liwunde, mwanti lyalakwe palyele lisikulyo lichiŵa nyangwinyangwi (ngalimba)"
  69,17,"Ni Achimalaika tachiŵa ali mungulugulu mwakwemo, soni pachanya pao lyele lisikulyo (Achimalaika ŵakwana) nsano naŵatatu, tachitwichila Arishi ja Ambuje ŵenu (Chindanda Chaulungu)"
  69,18,"Lyele lisikulyo tachiika namwe (ku magambo), pangali chilichose chankasasisaga jenumanja chachichisisika"
  69,19,"Sano mundu jwatachipedwa chitabu chakwe chakunkono wakwe wan'dyo, basi tachiti: “Eni! Soomani chitabu changu!”"
  69,20,“Chisimu une (ku duniya) nasimichisyaga yanti tinjisimangana nacho chiŵalanjilo changu.”
  69,21,Basi jwalakwe tachiŵa mu ndamo jakusengwasya
  69,22,Mu Mbepo Japenani
  69,23,Isogosi yakwe yakuŵandichila (yangasausya kaŵa)
  69,24,"(Tachasalila kuti): “Lyagani soni mwagani mwakusengwa ligongo lya ayila imwalongwesye m’moŵa gagaapite (kala ku duniya).”"
  69,25,"Nambo kwa mundu jwatachipedwa chitabu chakwe cha kunkono wakwe wanchiji, basi tachiti (pakudandaula): “Nkongwene! Nabola nga nganimbedwa chitabu changu!”"
  69,26,“Ningaatende ngachimanya chiŵalanjilo changu!”
  69,27,“Ha! Nabola chiwa chila chikaŵe chipelela (changu ni ngaujila soni ku umi)!”
  69,28,“Nganichingamuchisya chipanje changu.”
  69,29,“Gaanjonasichile machili gangu (gakulichenjelela).”
  69,30,"(Kuchiŵechetedwa kuti): “Munkamulani soni muntaŵe makongwa.”"
  69,31,“Kaneka ni mumponye ku Moto Waukali.”
  69,32,"“Kaneko muntaŵikanye m’malundelunde (ga unyolo), ulewu wakwe makono makumi nsano nagaŵili .”"
  69,33,Chisimu jwalakwe jwaliji jukaakunkulupilila Allah Jwakuchimbichika nnope
  69,34,Soni nganaŵa jwakuchisya yagaliisya masikini
  69,35,Basi nganakola jwalakwejo lelo kwekuno nsyoŵe (jwakunkamuchisya)
  69,36,Namuno yakulya ikaŵeje uwowu (wakusulula m’maŵanga ga ŵandu ŵa ku Moto)
  69,37,Pangali ŵatachiulya ikaŵeje ŵakulemwa
  69,38,Basi nguilumbila yankuiwona
  69,39,Ni yangankuiwona
  69,40,Chisimu jalakwe (Qur'aniji) liŵele liloŵe lya Ntenga Jwakuchimbichika (Jibulilu)
  69,41,"Ni nganijiŵa jalakwejo liloŵe lya nkwimba chilaanga, yannonope ni yankuikulupilila"
  69,42,"Soni ngaŵa liloŵe lya abimbi, yannonope ni yankukumbuchila"
  69,43,(Jiŵele) jakutulusyidwa kuumila kwa M'mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope
  69,44,Soni ingaŵe kuti (Muhammadi ﷺ) jwalukenye Kukwetu unami winewakwe
  69,45,Chisimu tukankwembekenye mwamachili
  69,46,Kaneka nitukakatile kwene mwa jwalakwejo ntasi (wakwe waumi nikuwa)
  69,47,Mwanti nga nganapatikana jwalijose mwa jenumanja jwakun'gosa (ku ipotesi Yetu)
  69,48,Soni chisimu jalakwe (Qur’ani) jiŵele chikumbusyo kwa ŵakun'jogopa (Allah)
  69,49,Sonitu Uwwe tukumanyilila kusyene yanti mwa ŵanganyammwe mwana ŵakanila
  69,50,Soni chisimu jalakwe (Qur’ani) jichiŵa jakwadandaulikasya kusyene achimakafili (ku Kiyama ndema jatachiuwona ntendele wa ŵajikuya ni ipotesi ya ŵajikana)
  69,51,Soni chisimu jalakweji jiŵele jakuona kusyesyene
  69,52,Basi liswejesyani lina lya Ambuje ŵenu Ŵakuchimbichika nnope
  70,1,"Jwawusisye nkuwusya (mwachipongwe) yailagasyo yakupatikana (kuti: Tiyipatikane chakachi)"
  70,2,Kwa achimakafili pangali jwampaka ayisiŵilile
  70,3,Yakuumila kwa Allah Nsyene Makwelelo
  70,4,Akasakwelaga Kukwakwe Achimalaika ni Jibulilu jwakwe. (Tiyichipatikana ilagasyoyo) mu lisiku (lya Kiyama) lyalili chipiimo chaulewu wakwe yaka yakwana masausande makumi nsano
  70,5,Basi pililani kupilila kwambone
  70,6,Chisimu ŵanganyao akuiwona (ilagasyoyo) kuti ili kwanaula (yangaŵa nkupatikana)
  70,7,Nambo Uwwe tukuiwona kuti ili dusi (kupatikana)
  70,8,Lisiku lya lichiŵa liwunde chisawu ntofu wenyelenyenduche
  70,9,Nombe matumbi gachiŵa chisawu litonji (pa kaululuche kakwe)
  70,10,Soni nsyoŵe ngasaja kuwusya ya nsyoŵe jwakwe
  70,11,"Namuno kuti tachipedwa lipesa lyakuonegana (mwanti mundu nikwaona babagwe, ŵanagwe ni ŵaulongo, nambo ngasakombola kwaŵechetekasya namuno kwaŵenda chikamuchisyo), jwakuleŵa tachilajila ali aliombwele ku ilagasyo ya lyele lisikulyo pakutola ŵanagwe"
  70,12,Kwisa soni ŵankwakwe ni nchimwenegwe
  70,13,Ni ŵalukosyo lwakwe ŵaŵaliji nkunsunga
  70,14,"Ni yosope yayili pachilambo (kupeleka kwa Allah), kut in'jokole"
  70,15,"Nambo kwapi! (Nganikuŵa kun'jokwele kuliwombola kwakweko), chisimu walakweo ni Moto Wakolela (mwamachili)"
  70,16,Wakusupula mwanakamo lipende lyamuntwe
  70,17,Uchiŵa uli nkum'bilanga mundu jwa ŵachitundumalile chikulupi ni kunyosya
  70,18,Ni ŵasonganganyisye (chipanje) ni kusalasya (mwakusalasya ata Zaka ngatola)
  70,19,Chisimu mundu agumbidwe kuŵa jwakupapamba kusyene (jwangapilila)
  70,20,Pati impatile yakusakala akasaŵa jasajasa
  70,21,Nambo pati impatile yambone akasaŵa jwaugaga
  70,22,Ikaŵeje ŵakuswali
  70,23,Aŵala ŵanya ŵaakuŵa pa swala syao ali nkwendelechela (kusiswaliswali)
  70,24,Ni aŵala ŵamuli nchipanje chao mwana liunjili lyachimanyichile
  70,25,Lyakumpa nkuŵenda ni nkwimidwa jwakwe (ligongo lyakulisiŵilila kuŵenda)
  70,26,Ni aŵala ŵaakwitichisya ya Lisiku Lyamalipilo
  70,27,Ni aŵala ŵanya ŵaakuŵa nkuijogopa ilagasyo ya M’mbuje gwao
  70,28,Chisimu ilagasyo ya M’mbuje gwao nganiyiŵa yati kulupuka nayo (mundu jwakusakala)
  70,29,Ni aŵala ŵanya ŵaakuŵa ali nkuugosa utukani wao (pangatenda yansese)
  70,30,Ikaŵeje kwa achiŵammakwao kapena (mateeka) gagapatile magasa gao gakun'dyo; basi chisimu ŵanganyao (pa yalakweyo) nganaŵa agambidwe
  70,31,"Nambo ŵatasache yangaŵaga yele, basi ŵanganyao niŵali ŵakusumba mpika"
  70,32,Ni aŵala ŵanya ŵaakuŵa ali nkusunga chenene amana syao kwisa soni ilanga yao
  70,33,Ni aŵala ŵanya ŵaakuŵa ali nkwimilichika pakupeleka umboni wao
  70,34,Ni aŵala ŵanya ŵaakuŵa ali nkwendelechela kusigosa swala syao (pakusiswaliswali)
  70,35,Ŵanganyao tachiŵa m’Matimbe ga ku Mbepo ali nkupedwa uchimbichimbi
  70,36,Ana chipali chichi kwa aŵala ŵaakufuulu chaakukangamalila kukwenu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ ali atunjile meso)
  70,37,(Ni kutama) nganyanganya chakun'dyo ni kunchiji (kwenu nambo ningakuuya yankwasalila)
  70,38,Ana jwalijose mwa jamanjao akukolaga tama janti takajinjisyidwe ku Litimbe Lyachindimba (ku Mbepo)
  70,39,Ngwamba! Chisimu Uwwe twagumbile ŵanganyao kuumila mu yaakuimanyilila (gagali mesi)
  70,40,"Basi ngunnumbila M'mbuje jwa kungopoko ni kungapililo kosope (kwa lyuŵa, mwesi ni ndondwa), kuti chisimu Uwwe tuŵele Ŵakombola"
  70,41,"Kuti twagalausye (nikwikanao ŵane) ŵambone kwapunda ŵanganyao, sonitu Uwwe nganituŵa ŵanti nikupundidwa (ni chilichose)"
  70,42,"Basi mwalekani agambeje kuweweta yangali mate ni kupita nching'anda, mpaka chasimangane nalyo Lisiku lyao alila lyaakuŵa ali nkupedwa chilanga (cha kwisa kwakwe)"
  70,43,Lisiku lyatachikopokangana m’malembe mwachitema chisawu ŵanganyao akuutuchila ku (isanamu yao) yaisimichidwe
  70,44,"Meso gao gali gateteŵele, kwaluka kuli kwaunichile, lyalakwelyo ni Lisiku alila lyaŵaliji nkupedwa chilanga (cha kwisa kwakwe)"
  71,1,"Chisimu Uwwe twantumisye Nuhu ku ŵandu ŵakwe (ni kuntenda kuti): “Mwatetelani ŵandu ŵenu nkaniyayichilile ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope.”"
  71,2,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “E ŵandu ŵangu! Chisimu une ninkuntetela jwenu jwakuonechela.”"
  71,3,“Mun'galagatilani Allah ni kun'jogopa soni mumbikanilani une.”
  71,4,"“Tankululuchile sambi syenu ni kunchelewasya kwikanila ndema jajikolanjidwe (kuŵa mbesi ja umi wenu), chisimu ndema ja Allah (jakuwila mundu) pati jiyiche, jangaŵa nkujichelewasya ingaŵe mwamanyililaga.”"
  71,5,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Chisimu une mbele ndili nkwaŵilanjila ŵandu ŵangu chilo ni muusi.”"
  71,6,“Nambo kuŵilanjila kwanguko nganikwajonjechesya (chilichose) ikaŵeje kutilape.”
  71,7,"“Soni chisimu une ndema jilijose jimbele ndili nkwaŵilanjila (Kukwenu) kuti mwakululuchile, aŵele ali nkuŵika yala yao m’mawiwi mwao ni kuliunichilaga nguwo syao, soni aŵele ali nkuchalila (kutenda makani), ni alikwesisye kulikwesya kusyene.”"
  71,8,“Kaneka une chisimu naŵilanjiile ŵanganyao mwakunyanyika.”
  71,9,"“Kaneko chisimu une nagombelesye kukwao, soni ni nasongonele mwaasili.”"
  71,10,"“Basi ni natite: ‘Mum'bendani chikululuko M'mbuje gwenu, chisimu Jwalakwejo juŵele Jwakululuka kusyene.”"
  71,11,“Juntuluchisye wula mwawinji.”
  71,12,"“Ni jun'jonjechesye chipanje ni ŵanache, ni kum'bichila migunda, ni kum'bichila soni sulo.”"
  71,13,“Chipali chichi kukwenu changampela Allah uchimbichimbi (pakun'galagatila Jwele Jikape)!”
  71,14,“Kutendaga pamasile pan'gumbile mu kaŵe kakulekangana-lekangana kane panyuma pa kane!”
  71,15,“Ana ngankuyiona yatite kagumbe Allah mawunde nsano nagaŵili mwakusajikanya?”
  71,16,"“Ni auŵisile mwesi mwalakwemo kuŵa lilanguka, ni aliŵisile lyuŵa kuŵa nyali?”"
  71,17,“Soni Allah ammesisye (pakun'gumba) kuumila mwitaka mwammela.”
  71,18,"“Kaneka tachim'buchisya m’momo (panyuma pakuwa), ni kwisa kunkoposya mwanakamo (pa Kiyama).”"
  71,19,“Soni Allah am'biichiile litaka kuŵa chakutandika.”
  71,20,“Kuti n'jendejejendeje palakwepo m’matala gakusapanguka.”
  71,21,"Nuhu jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Chisimu ŵanganyao anyosisye une, ni ankuyiye ajula jwangaŵa nkun'jonjechesya chipanje chakwe ni ŵanache ŵakwe (chilichose) ikaŵeje kupelelwape.”"
  71,22,“Ni atesile malindi gamakulungwa nnope.”
  71,23,"“Soni aŵele ali nkuti: ‘Ngasinneka (galagatila) milungu jenu ata panandi, ngasinnogwa kwaleka Awadda, Asuwa'a, Ayagh'utha, Aya’uka ni Anasra.”"
  71,24,"“Soni ŵanganyao pamasile paŵasokonesye (ŵandu) ŵajinji, ni ngasimwajonjechesya ŵakulitenda lupuso (chine chakwe) ikaŵeje kupotelape.”"
  71,25,"Ligongo lya ilemwa yao ŵamisyidwe (m’mesi) ni kwinjisyidwa ku Moto, soni nganansimana jwalijose jwanti ni kwakulupusya jwangaŵaga Allah"
  71,26,"Soni Nuhu jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Ngasimunneka pa chilambo pano ata jumo mwa makafiliŵa.”"
  71,27,"“Chisimu Mmwe naga nkwaleka ŵanganyao taŵe ali nkwasokonesya achikapolo Ŵenu, soni ŵanyao ngaŵa nkuŵeleka (mwanache jwambone) ikaŵeje jwakusakasya nnope, jwakanila kusyene.”"
  71,28,"“Ambuje ŵangu! Mungululuchilani une ni achinangolo ŵangu, ni jwalijose jwaajinjile m’nyumba mwangu ali jwakulupilila, kwisa soni ŵakulupilila ŵachilume ni ŵachikongwe (wosope), ni ngasimwajonjechesya ŵakulitenda lupuso (chine chakwe) ikaŵeje chonasikope.”"
  72,1,"Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Ijuwulidwe kukwangu yanti likuga line lya majini lyapikanile (Qur’an), basi ni gatite (pakugasalila majini gajao): ‘Chisimu uwwe tupikene Qur’an jakusimosya"
  72,2,"Jikongolela kuchongoko mwanti tujikulupilile, soni nganituŵa tum’bwanganyisye M’mbuje gwetu ni chilichose"
  72,3,"Soni chisimu Uchimbichimbi wa M’mbuje gwetu unyakwiche kusyene, nganijulitendela ŵankwakwe namuno mwanache"
  72,4,Soni chisimu jwam’bwawate mwetuwe jwaliji nkum'bechetela Allah yaukoleko wakunaula
  72,5,Soni chisimu uwwe twaliji nkuganichisya yanti mundu ni lijini ngaŵa nkum'bechetela Allah yaunami
  72,6,"Soni chisimu achalume ŵachiŵandu ŵaliji nkulijuya mwa achalume ŵachijini, basi niŵaliji nkwajonjechesya kusumba mpika pasambi"
  72,7,Soni chisimu ŵanganyao ŵaiche mwaganisya mwamwaganichisyaga ŵanganyammwe kuti Allah ngaŵa nkutumisya (ntume) jwalijose (kuŵandu ni majini)
  72,8,"Soni chisimu uwwe twasachilile kuja kwika kwinani, nambo twakusimene kuli kugumbele achilonda ŵamachili (ŵachilaika) ni yenje (yandondwa)"
  72,9,"Soni chisimu uwwe (kala) twaliji nkutama mwalakwemo m’malo mwakupikanila (abali syakwinani), nambo jwatasache kuja kupikanila sanojino, takachisimane chenje (chandondwa) chili chin'juŵilile"
  72,10,"Soni chisimu uwwe ngatukumanyilila kuti, ana akusachiilidwa yangalumbana ŵali pa chilambo kapena M’mbuje gwao jukwasachilila chongoko"
  72,11,"Soni chisimu mwetuwe mwana ŵane ŵambone, nambo ŵane mwetuwe nganaŵa iyyo. Tuŵele (mikutula ja) matala gakulekangana-lekangana (ga dini)"
  72,12,"Soni chisimu uwwe twaimanyi kusyene yanti ngaŵa nkunnepelaasya Allah (kutupa ilagasyo) pa chilambo pano, soni ngaŵa nkunnepelaasya pakutilila (kwinani)"
  72,13,"Soni chisimu uwwe ndema jatuchipikene chongolo (Qur’an) tuchikulupilile, basi jwatankulupilile M’mbujeegwe nikuti ngajogopa kupungusyidwa (yambone yakwe) kapena kutwichidwa (nsigo wa sambi sya jwine)"
  72,14,"Soni chisimu mwetuwe mwana Asilamu ni mwana ŵane mwetuwe ŵapombotale (kuleka litala lyagoloka lya Usilamu). Sano ŵajinjile mu Usilamu, basi ŵanganyao ni ŵalungeme ku chongoko.”"
  72,15,"Nambo aŵala ŵapombotele (kuleka Usilamu), nikuti chachiŵa sasu sya ku Jahannama"
  72,16,"Soni mwanti ingaŵe ŵajimilichiche (akupombotalao) petala (lya Usilamu), chisimu tungaamwesisye mesi gamajinji (nga nganalajila chilichose)"
  72,17,"Kuti twalinje muwele (ukotowo yanti: Ana chapitilisye Usilamu kapena chakufulu)? Sano jwatakutundumalile kunkumbuchila M’mbujeegwe (Allah), tan'jinjisye ku ilagasyo yakusausya nnope"
  72,18,"Soni chisimu misikiti nsyene jwakwe ni Allah, basi ngasimun'galagatila jwalijose pampepe ni Allah"
  72,19,"Soni chisimu ndema ja jwajimi kapolo jwa Allah (Muhammadi ﷺ pa swala) achim'bombaga (Allah), ŵasigele panandi (achimajini) kuti ammate (ligongo lya winji nnope ni kunyambatikana pakusaka kupikanila Qur’an)"
  72,20,"Jilani: “Chisimu ngun'galagatila M'mbuje gwangu pe, ni ngangum'bwanganya Najo julijose.”"
  72,21,"Jilani: “Chisimu une nganingola kukwenu (machili gakumpela) isausyo kapena chongoko.”"
  72,22,"Jilani: “Chisimu une ngaŵa nkuunjokola jwalijose (ku ipotesi ya) kuumila kwa Allah (naga ndili nannyosisye), soni ngaŵa nkupata kwakutilila kwangaŵaga Kukwakwe"
  72,23,"Ikaŵeje kulungusya (yakuona) ya kuumila kwa Allah ni utenga Wakwe (gele ni machili gangwete une), sano jwatannyosye Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ; basi chisimu uŵele wakwe jwalakwejo moto wa Jahannama, chakaŵe ŵandamo mwalakwemo yaka-yaka.”"
  72,24,"Kwikanila ndema jataachiiwona yaakuŵa ali nkupedwa chilanga (cha kwika kwakwe), pele nipatachimamyilila (yanti) ana ŵani ŵaakwete nkwaakamuchisya jwangali machili ni ŵaali chiŵalanjilo channono"
  72,25,"Jilani: “Ngangupata kumanyilila kuti ana ili pakuŵandika (ipotesi) yankupedwa chilangayo kapena Ambuje ŵangu tayiŵiichile ndaŵi jelewu!”"
  72,26,"(Jwalakwe ni) Nkumanyilila yakusisika, basi ni jwangailosya yakusisika Yakweyo kwa jwalijose"
  72,27,"Ikaŵeje Ntenga jwansagwile, basi chisimu akasam'biichilaga m'bujo mwakwe ni munyuma mwakwe (Achimalaika) ŵakunnonda-londa"
  72,28,"Kuti amanyilile (Ntengajo) yanti pamasile paŵaalungwisye (Achimitenga ŵane wosope) mautenga ga M’mbuje gwao, soni nikuti (Allah) ayisyuungwiile yali nayo (paaimanya chenene), soni ni akusenye chiŵalanjilo cha chilichose"
  73,1,"E, mmwe ŵan'diŵijiiliile mu nguwo"
  73,2,Jimani chilo (kuswali) ikaŵeje kandaŵi kannono
  73,3,"Litika lyakwe (½), kapena mpungusye mwitikamo panandi"
  73,4,"Kapena n'jonjechesye petikalyo, ni nsoomeje Qur’an mwaakosoŵalila"
  73,5,Chisimu Uwwe chituntuluchisye mmwejo liloŵe lyausito
  73,6,"Chisimu kwimuchila chilo (kuswali) nikwakuli kwakwinjilisya nnope (mu ntima), soni yakuŵecheta yakwe ikasaŵaga yagoloka kusyene"
  73,7,Chisimu mmwejo muusi nkwete ipaka yejinji
  73,8,"Ni likumbuchilani lina lya Ambuje ŵenu (Allah pakulikolanga), soni lipelekani Kukwakwe nalipelekape"
  73,9,"M'mbuje jwa kungopoko ni kungapililo, pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ikaŵeje Jwalakwe, basi muntendani kuŵa Nkun'jegama"
  73,10,"Soni pililani pa yaakuŵecheta (achimakafili), ni mwaŵambalani kuŵambala kwambone"
  73,11,"Soni munekaani Une ni ŵakanila achinsyene ukoto (wa duniya), gambani kwalechelela panandipe (timalane nao)"
  73,12,Chisimu Kukwetu kwana matondolo gakulimbangana ni Moto Waukali
  73,13,Ni yakulya yakwama (palukosi) kwisa soni ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope
  73,14,"Lisiku lya lichitenganyika litaka kwisa soni matumbi, ni gachiŵa matumbigo chisau liunjili lya nsanga wakupwelembwesuka"
  73,15,"Chisimu Uwwe tutumisye kukwenu Ntenga (Muhammadi ﷺ) kuŵa mboni pa jenumanja, mpela yatwatite pakutumisya kwa Afiriauna Ntenga (Musa)"
  73,16,"Nambo Afiriauna ŵannyosyisye Ntengajo, basi ni twaakwembekenye ni ilagasyo yakandapala kusyene"
  73,17,Ana chin'digose chinauli (ku ipotesi) naga nkulikanila Lisiku lyalichitendekasya ŵanache kola wuuli
  73,18,"Liwunde lichipasuka mu lyele Lisikuli (ligongo lya kogoya kwakwe), chilanga Chakwe (Allah) chichiŵa chakutendekwa (mwangalepeleka)"
  73,19,"Chisimu galakwe (ma Ȃyaga) gaŵele chikumbusyo, basi jwaakusaka aliikolochesye chilepe litala lyakuujila kwa M'bujegwe"
  73,20,"Chisimu Ambuje ŵenu akumanyilila yanti mmwejo (Muhammadi ﷺ) nkwima (kuswali) mwakunandipila pa ipande iŵili mu ipande itatu yaachilo (⅔), kapena litika lyakwe (½), kapena chimo mu ipande itatu (⅓), pamo ni likuga lya aŵala ŵan'di nao, sano Allah ni Jwaakupimila chenene (ulewu wa) chilo ni muusi, jwaimanyi yanti nganim'ba nkukwanisye kupimila kusyesyene (nikuswali mwannamulile, niligongo lyakwe n'gamba kuswali chilo chosope), basi ankululuchile (pakuusyaausya lilamusili). Kwaligongo lyele; soomagani chachijepepele chakuumila m Qur’an. Jwaimanyi yanti ŵane mwa jenumanja tachiŵa ŵakulwala, soni ŵane tachiŵa ali nkwendajenda pa chilambo kupita nchisosasosa umbone wa Allah, soni ŵane tachiŵa ali nkuputa ngondo petala lya Allah, basi soomagani chachijepepele chakuumila mwele (mu Qur’animo), ni n'jimicheje Swala mwakolosya ni kutolaga Zaka, soni munkongosyeje Allah ngongole jambone. Soni chambone chilichose chankulilongochesya mwachimisyene tinkachisimane kwa Allah chili chambone nnope ni chamalipilo gekulungwa kusyene. Ni mum'bendagani chikuluko Allah, chisimu Allah ni Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope"
  74,1,"E, mmwe ŵan'diunichile nguwo"
  74,2,Jimani ni mwaatetele (ŵandu)
  74,3,Soni Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) mwakusyaani
  74,4,Soni nguwo syenu siswejesyani
  74,5,Soni yakusakala (mpela isanamu) iŵambalani
  74,6,Soni ngasimumpa (jwinejwakwe chindu) ni ligongo lyakuti mpochele yejinji
  74,7,Soni ligongo lya Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) pililani
  74,8,Basi ndema jalichigombedwa lipenga
  74,9,Lyele lisikulyotu lichiŵa lisiku lyakunonopa kusyene
  74,10,Kwa achimakafili ngasiliŵa lyakwepepala
  74,11,Munekaani ni mundu jwanan'gumbile jikajikape
  74,12,Ninampele ipanje yejinji
  74,13,Ni ŵanache ŵakuŵanajo
  74,14,Ni nankolochesye (ndamo jakwe) kunkolochesya kwambone nnope
  74,15,Panyuma pakwe jukolaga tama janti ndili nan'jonjechesye
  74,16,Kwapi! Chisimu jwalakwejo jwaliji nkugakanila maaya Getu
  74,17,Chingankanganichisye ku ilagasyo yakusausya kuikwela
  74,18,Chisimu jwalakwe jwachetelele (yatajile paajigamba Qur’an) ni jwapimiile
  74,19,"Basi julwesedwe, ana jwapimiile chantiuli"
  74,20,"Soni julwesedwe, ana jwapimiile chantiuli"
  74,21,Kaneka ni jwalolite (ŵandu)
  74,22,Kaneko ni jwautile sinya ni kusakasya kungope (kulosya ukali)
  74,23,Kaneko soni jwachitundumalile (chikulupi) ni kulikwesya
  74,24,"Ni jwatite: “Nganijiŵatu jalakwe (Qur’aniji) ikaŵeje usaŵi waukupocheledwa (kuumila kwa asaŵi ŵakala).”"
  74,25,“Nganijiŵatu jalakwe (Qur’aniji) ikaŵeje maloŵe ga mundu.”
  74,26,Sampano tinan'jinjisye ku Saqara
  74,27,Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya Saqara
  74,28,(Weletu ni Moto) wangasigasya (chilichose chachiponyedwemo) soni wangachileka (kuti chikopoche)
  74,29,Wakutinisya ni kuŵiilisya lipende
  74,30,Pa walakweo pana (Achimalika ŵakuugosa) ŵakwana likumi kwisa nsano nancheche
  74,31,"Ni nganitwaaŵiika akuuloleela Moto ikaŵeje Achimalaika, soni nganituchiŵiika chiŵalanjilo chaocho ikaŵeje kuŵa mayeso gakwalinjila achimakafili, kuti asimichisye ŵandu ŵaŵapedwile chitabu (ya chiŵalanjilochi), ni kuti soni ajonjechesye chikulupi chao ŵandu ŵaakulupilile, soni kuti akakaichila ŵandu ŵaŵapedwile chitabu ni ŵakulupilila, ni kuti soni aŵala ŵamuli m’mitima mwao mwana ulwele (wa unakunaku) ni achimakafili ajileje: “Ana Allah akusaka chichi pachilandanyo chalakwechi?” Iyyoyopeyo niyaakutiji Allah pa kunnechelela kusokonechela jwansachile ni kun'jongola jwansachile. Ni pangali ŵaakumanyilila mikutula ja asilikali ŵa Ambuje ŵenu ikaŵeje Jwelepejo. Ni nganiuŵa Walakwe (Motowo) ikaŵeje chikumbusyo kwa ŵandu (cha kwatetela nacho)"
  74,32,Ngwamba! Nguulumbila mwesi
  74,33,Ni chilo ndema jachikutyoka (pakucha)
  74,34,Ni kumasikusiku ndema jakukulanguka
  74,35,Chisimu Walakwe (Motowo) uŵele limpepe (m’makungu) gekulungwa nnope
  74,36,Chitetelo kwa ŵandu
  74,37,Kwa jwalijose mwa jenumanja jwaasachile kuti alongolele (pakutenda yambone) kapena kusigalila (pakupanganya yakusakala)
  74,38,Mundu jwalijose tachiŵa uwombosi wakuliombolela ku (yakusakala) yaŵapanganyisye (pakutaŵidwa ku Moto)
  74,39,Ikaŵeje aŵala ŵakunkono wan'dyo
  74,40,(Chachiŵa) m’Matimbe ga ku Mbepo achiwuusyanaga
  74,41,Ya (ŵandu) ŵakuleŵa
  74,42,“Ana ni chichi chachin'jinjisye ŵanganyammwe ku Saqara?”
  74,43,"(Pakwanga) chachitiji: “Nganituŵa mwa akuswali.”"
  74,44,“Soni nganituŵa nkwaaliisya masikini.”
  74,45,“Ni twaliji nkutiŵila (mu sambi) pamo ni akutiŵila.”
  74,46,“Ni twaliji soni nkukanila ya Lisiku Lyamalipilo.”
  74,47,“Mpaka chatuichilile chiwa.”
  74,48,Basi ngasichija kwakamuchisya ŵanganyao chondechonde cha akuchondelela
  74,49,Ana chipali chichi kukwao chikwatendekasya kuchitundumalila chikumbusyo (Qur’an)
  74,50,(Kakwipuche kakwe kuti akajipikana Qur’an) gamba kuŵa ŵanganyao mpela mbunda (syamwitinji) syasikwipusyidwe
  74,51,Syasikutila lisimba
  74,52,Yeti mundu jwalijose mwa ŵanganyao akusakaga ali apedwile ikalakala yeunukule-unukule (kuumila kwa Allah kutendela umboni yakuŵecheta Muhammadi ﷺ)
  74,53,Ngwamba! Nambo kuti ŵanganyao ngaakujijogopa Akhera
  74,54,Ngwamba! Chisimu jalakwe (Qur’aniji) jiŵele chikumbusyo
  74,55,Basi jwaakusaka taalikumbusye najo
  74,56,Ni nganaŵa alikumbwisye ŵanganyao ikaŵeje naga Allah ali asachile. Jwalakwe ni jwaali Jwakuŵajilwa kogopedwa soni ni Nysene chikululuko
  75,1,Ngulilumbila lisiku lya Kiyama
  75,2,Ni nguulumbila soni ntima wakuliigamba
  75,3,Ana akuganichisya mundu kuti ngaŵa nkusonganganya Uwwe maupa gakwe
  75,4,"Elo (tuchigasonganganya), ngati Uwwe tuli ŵakombola kwalanya chenene (tumisela twa) songa sya yala yakwe, (kuli uli maupa)"
  75,5,Nambo mundu (akukanila ya Kiyama) pakusachilila kwendelechela kusakasya m'bujo mwakwe
  75,6,"Akuusya (mwa chipongwe kuti): “Ana lisiku lya Kiyama lichiŵa chakachi?”"
  75,7,Sano ndema ja lichikolondoka liso (ligongo lya woga)
  75,8,Ni kutyoka kuŵala kwa mwesi
  75,9,Ni kusonganganyisyidwa lyuŵa ni mwesi
  75,10,"Lyele lisikulyo mundu tachiti: “Kwakutilila ni kwapi?”"
  75,11,"Iyayi, pangali kwakutilila"
  75,12,Kwa Ambuje ŵenupe (Allah) lyele lisikulyo nikuchipelela kwakuujila
  75,13,Tachisalilidwa mundu lyele lisikulyo ichindu yajwalongwesye (kupanganya) ni yajwalesile (munyuma)
  75,14,"Nambo mundu tachilichonjela nsyene (ligongo kutandila lipende, makono ni ngongolo syakwe ichijuwula masengo gakusakala ga jwapanganyisye)"
  75,15,Namuno tatole madandawusi gakwe (pakuliŵalanga ngasigankamuchisya)
  75,16,Ngasin'jitenganyila (Qur’aniji mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) lulimi lwenu (ndema jajikutuluka) kuti n'jikulumisye (kujisunga ni kujisooma)
  75,17,Chisimu ili Kukwetu Uwwe kujisonganganya (mu ntima mwenu) ni kumpa ukombosi wakujisooma
  75,18,"Sano pati tuchinsoomelaga, basi kuyichisyani kusoomwa kwakwe"
  75,19,Soni chisimu ili Kukwetu Uwwe kujisalichisya
  75,20,"Ngaŵa (chine chikuntendekasya kaanila Kiyama), nambo kuti ŵanganyammwe nkunonyelwa umi wachitema (wa duniya)"
  75,21,Ni nkujileka Akhera
  75,22,Ngope sine lyele lisikulyo sichiŵa syakuŵala
  75,23,Sili nkwalola Ambuje ŵao (Allah)
  75,24,Sano nambo ngope sine lyele lisikulyo sichiyinda
  75,25,Sichisimichisya yanti chiitendekwe kukwakwe yakuniula n'gongo
  75,26,"Ngaŵa (yanti nikanila), ndema jauchiika ntima paligongwa (papasimanile maupa gammakoyo)"
  75,27,"Nikuŵechetedwa (yanti): “Ŵani ŵampaka aposye (chilwelechi)?”"
  75,28,Nikumala mwakusimichisya (chilwelecho) kuti kwalakweku ni kulekangana (najo duniya)
  75,29,Mwanti lusonjo nikusajikana ni lusonjo (lujakwe ndema jakutyoka ntima)
  75,30,Kwa Ambuje ŵenupe lyele lisikulyo ni kwakuwujila mwakuchinjidwa
  75,31,Mwanti (kafili) nganijukunda (chikulupi) soni (namuno swala) nganijuswali
  75,32,Nambo jwakaaniile ni kunyosya
  75,33,Kaneka jwapite kwiŵasa lyakwe (juli nkwenda) mwakutwanga
  75,34,Chonasiko nichenu! Chonasiko chisyene
  75,35,Soni chonasiko nichenu! Chonasiko chisyene
  75,36,Ana jukuganichisya mundu yanti chijugambe kulechedwa wambape (ngapedwa malamusi soni ngaja kulipidwa)
  75,37,Ana nganijuŵa lindondwa lya ulume wakutajidwa (m’chiŵelechelo)
  75,38,"Kaneka jwaliji chipande cha myasi, niŵan'gumbile ni kunkolosya"
  75,39,Ni ŵagumbile kuumila mwalakwemo mitundu jiŵili (jaŵandu) jwannume ni jwankongwe
  75,40,Ana Jwalakwe (Allah jwaŵapakombwele kutenda yele) nganaŵa jwanti ni kombola kwasyusya (ŵandu) ŵawe
  76,1,Ana nganijipita kwamundu mbinga jelewu ja ndaŵi nkanaŵe kuŵa chindu chanti ni kusalidwa
  76,2,"Chisimu Uwwe tun'gumbile mundu kuumila mwindondwa lyakuwanganyichilana (lya mesi ga ŵalume ni ŵakongwe), kuti tun'dinje (ni malamusi Getu), ni tuntesile kuŵa jwakupikana, jwakulola"
  76,3,"Chisimu Uwwe tunsaalichiisye jwalakwejo litala (lyambone ni lyakusakala, sano ili ni nsyene) kuŵa jwakutogolela (pakusagula lyambonelyo) kapena kuŵa jwakanila (pakusagula lyakusakala)"
  76,4,"Chisimu Uwwe twalinganyichisye achimakafili malundelunde ga unyolo, ni makongwa kwisa soni Moto Wakulapuka"
  76,5,Chisimu atenda ngoto chakamweje chipanda (chankologo) chakuwanganyichisya chakwe (nkologowo) chigakaŵeje (mesi ga) Kaafuura
  76,6,"(Kaafuurajo ni) tutumule jwachakamwejemo achikapolo ŵa Allah, chakam'bumyeje (palipose pachakasacheje) kaumye kangasausya"
  76,7,"(Ŵanganyao ni aŵala) ŵaakukwanilisya nasili (syao), soni ni akulijogopa Lisiku lya ichiŵa yakusakala yakwe yakwenela"
  76,8,"Ni akutolaga yakulya - achiisakaga - kwapa masikini, jwawina ni mateeka"
  76,9,"(Chamuntima akutiji): “Chisimu tukun'diisya pakusachilila chinonyelo cha Allah, ngatukusaka kukwenu malipilo galigose namuno kutogolela.”"
  76,10,“Chisimu uwwe tukogopa kwa M’mbuje gwetu Lisiku lyakuuta sinya (kafili) soni lyakupoteka nnope ni kupwelembwesula (ligongo lya kuleupa kwakwe mu ilagasyo).”
  76,11,Basi Allah tachagosa kuyakusakala ya lyele lisikulyo ni kwapa kumelemenda (kungope kwao) ni kusengwa
  76,12,Soni tachalipila ligongo lya kupilila kwao Litimbe lya ku Mbepo kwisa soni nguwo sya silika
  76,13,"Ali ajegeme kwalakweko nyyindanda yetandiche chenene, ngaaja kuchiona chitukuta cha lyuŵa namuno mbepo ja chikweenya"
  76,14,"Soni miulili jakwe chijikaaŵandichile ŵanganyao, ni mikonga (ja isogosi) chijikagoyeche kwakwalala (yanti konyola chitamile)"
  76,15,Soni chiikaŵeje ili nkwasyungula ikolelo ya silifa kwisa soni migawo jegalasi
  76,16,"Jegalasi (jagumbidwa) kuumila mu silifa, chakajipimileje (pakujigumbasya) kapimile kambone (kakulandana ni njota jao, ngapelembechesya soni ngajonjechesya)"
  76,17,Ni chakamwesyedweje kwalakweko chipanda (chankologo) chakuwanganyichisya chakwe (nkologowo) chichikaŵe (mesi ga) chikasu
  76,18,(Jwalakwejo ni) tutumule jwajuli kwalakweko jwakuŵilanjikwa Salsabila
  76,19,"Soni chaakaasyunguleje ŵanganyao (pakwaatumichila) achachanda ŵakutamilichika (pa uchanda, ŵangachekulupa). N'di mwaweni ŵanganyao mpaka mwaganichisye kuti ngalekale syakumelemenda nnope syemwasyidwe"
  76,20,Soni patinchilola kwalakwe (ku Mbepoko) tinchiuona ntendele wakusengwasya ni uchimwene wekulungwa
  76,21,"Pachanya pao chipakaŵe pana nguwo sya silika jwakuŵeŵela syachisamba kwisa soni nguwo sya silika jwakandapalila. Soni chakawechedwe makosa ga silifa, nombe soni M’mbuje gwao (Allah) chijukaamwesye ŵanganyao yakumwa yakulenjela kusyene"
  76,22,"(Chakasalilidwe kuti): “Chisimu galakwega gaŵele malipilo genu, soni masengo genu gaŵele gakupocheledwa.”"
  76,23,Chisimu Uwwe tujitulwisye kukwenu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) Qur’an kujitulusya kwapanandi panandi (kuti n'jisunje chenene)
  76,24,Basi pililani ni lilamusi lya Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) ni ngasimumpikanila mwa ŵanganyao jwasambi kapena jwakanila (jwalijose)
  76,25,"Soni likumbuchilani lina lya Ambuje ŵenu kundaŵi ni kwigulo (pakuswali swala sya Fajr, Dhuhr ni Asr)"
  76,26,"Soni chilo munsujudilani (pakuswali swala sya Maghrib ni Isha), ni munswejesyeje chilo ndema jelewu"
  76,27,"Chisimu ŵanganyaŵa akunonyelwa umi wachitema (wa duniya), ni akulileka munyuma mwao Lisiku lya usito"
  76,28,"Uwwe ni ŵatwaagumbile ŵanganyao soni twaliyiye kagumbidwe kao, soni tuli tusachile mpaka tuiche nao ŵane ŵanti mpela ŵanganyao kwinjila m’malo mwao (nambo ali ŵakun'jogopa Allah)"
  76,29,"Chisimu galakwe (ma Ȃyaga) gaŵele chikumbusyo, basi jwaakusaka aliikolochesye chilepe litala lyakuujila kwa M'bujegwe (Allah)"
  76,30,"Ni nganim'ba nsachile ŵanganyammwe ikaŵeje akasache kaje Allah, chisimu Allah aŵele Jwakumanyilila nnope, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  76,31,"Taakan'jinjisye jwansachile ku ukoto Wakwe (ku Mbepo), nambo ŵakulitenda lupuso ŵalinganyichisye ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope"
  77,1,Ngujilumbila mbungo jajikupuga mwakuyana
  77,2,Ni mbungo jajikupuga mwa chimbunga
  77,3,Ni mbungo jajikwenesya (mawunde kwisa soni wula) mu kajenesye (kaasachile Allah)
  77,4,Ni ma Ȃya (ga Qur’an) gakulekanganya (chilikati cha yakuona ni yaunami)
  77,5,Ni (Achimalaika) ŵaakupelekaga utenga (kwa Achimitenga)
  77,6,Kuti utyose kuliŵalanga (kwakupeleka madandausi) kapena kuti utetele
  77,7,"Chisimu ichindu yankupedwa chilanga (cha kwisa kwakwe, mpela Kiyama) iŵele yakupatikana (mwangalepeleka)"
  77,8,Pa ndema ja sichisiimaasidwa ndondwa (kuŵala kwakwe)
  77,9,Ni ndema ja lichipesedwa liwunde (nikuŵa mapesa-mapesa)
  77,10,Ni ndema ja gachichuŵidwa matumbi ni kusyajidwa mwachitema ni kuululusyidwa
  77,11,Ni ndema ja chachisonganganyisyidwa Achimitenga pa ndema jetomechedwe
  77,12,Ana lisikuchi lyaiŵichilidwe (yayisalidweyi kuti tiyitendekwe)
  77,13,Pa Lisiku Lyachiilanyo
  77,14,Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya Lisiku Lyachiilanyo
  77,15,Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila
  77,16,Ana Uwwe nganitwajonanga (ŵandu) ŵandanda (ligongo lya ilemwa yao)
  77,17,Kaneka chitukuichisye pajamanjao (kwajonanga ŵandu) ŵambesi
  77,18,Mwele ni mwatukutendelaga ni ŵandu ŵakuleŵa
  77,19,Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila
  77,20,Ana nganitun'gumba jenumanja kuumila mmesi gakunyosyeka
  77,21,Basi ni twagaŵisile pa malo gakutamilichika ni kusunjika (m’chiŵelechelo)
  77,22,Kwikanila ndema jakumanyika
  77,23,"Basi ni twapimiile (ndema jakupagwila mwanache), Uwwetu niŵambone nnope mwa akupimila (ichindu)"
  77,24,Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila
  77,25,Ana nganituliŵika litaka kuŵa chikuti
  77,26,Cha ŵachijumi ni ŵawe
  77,27,"Ni tuŵisile mwalakwemo yakunyichisya yaileu-leu (gagali matumbi), ni tumpele kumwa ŵanganyammwe mesi gakunong’a"
  77,28,Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila
  77,29,"(Chachisalilidwa achimakafili kuti): “Ŵigulani mwanja kwa ayila yamwaliji nkuikanila"
  77,30,Ŵigulani mwanja ku m'bulili (walyosi lya ku Moto) waukwete nyambi sitatu
  77,31,Nganiuŵa mwa m'bulili wachisisimila soni wangakamuchisya kwilamba (lya Moto).”
  77,32,Chisimu Walakwe (Motowo) ukasaponyaga (pakutatasika) ndamba (syekulungwa) mpela nyumba jandalaja
  77,33,Syanti mpela ngamiya syam'bilichila
  77,34,Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila
  77,35,Lyalakweli nilisiku lyatachitenda ngapaŵecheta (ŵanganyao)
  77,36,Soni ngasapedwa luusa lwanti aliŵalanje (pakupeleka madandausi)
  77,37,Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila
  77,38,"Lyalakweli ni Lisiku Lyachiilanyo, tunsonganganyisye ŵanganyammwe ni (ŵandu) ŵandanda"
  77,39,"Sano naga nkwete malindi, basi mundendelani"
  77,40,Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila
  77,41,Chisimu ŵakun'jogopa (Allah) chachiŵa m’miulili (jakusisimila chenene) ni achitutumule
  77,42,Ni isogosi yatachiilaluchilaga
  77,43,"(Tachasalila kuti): “Lyagani soni mwagani mwakusengwa ligongo lya ayila (yambone) yamwaliji nkutenda.”"
  77,44,Chisimu Uwwe iyyoyopeyo ni yatukutiji pakwalipila ŵakolosya
  77,45,Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila
  77,46,"(E, jenumanja achimakafili!) Lyagani ni kusengwa panandi (mukandaŵi kannono kaumi wa duniyau), chisimu ŵanganyammwe ŵaleŵeleŵe"
  77,47,Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila
  77,48,"Soni pati iŵechetedwe kukwao (yanti): “Jinamani (kuswali).” Ngakwinamaga"
  77,49,Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila
  77,50,Ana ni abalichi jatachijikulupilila panyuma pa aji (Qur’an)
  78,1,Ana akuwusyana ya chichi
  78,2,Ya abali jekulungwa (ja Kiyama)
  78,3,Jaakuŵa ŵanganyao pa jalakwejo ali nkutindana
  78,4,Ngwamba! Sampano chaimanye (isyesyene yakwe)
  78,5,Soni ngwamba! Sampano chaimanye (isyesyene yakwe)
  78,6,Ana nganituliŵika litaka kuŵa chakutandika
  78,7,Matumbi ni kuŵa ichili
  78,8,Ni tun'gumbile ŵanganyammwe mitundu jiŵili (achalume ni achakongwe)
  78,9,Soni tuluŵisile lugono lwenu kuŵa kupumula (kwa ilu yenu)
  78,10,Ni tuchiŵisile chilo kuŵa chiwaalo (pakusiŵilila ilu yenu ni chipi chakwe)
  78,11,Ni tuuŵisile muusi kuŵa ndema jakupalila
  78,12,Ni tutaŵile pachanya penu (mawunde) nsano nagaŵili gakulimbangana
  78,13,Soni tuŵisile (kwalakweko) nyali jaakolela kusyene (lyuŵa)
  78,14,Ni tutulwisye kuumila m’mawunde gawula mesi gakugwa mwamachili
  78,15,Kuti tukopochesye mbeju ni mmela
  78,16,Kwisa soni migunda jetotekane (nyambi sya itela)
  78,17,Chisimu Lisiku Lyachiilanyo liŵele lyana ndema jakwe jisyesyene
  78,18,"Lisiku lya chiiligombedwa lipenga, mwanti ŵanganyammwe chinchiikanganaga mikutula-mikutula"
  78,19,"Ni lichiugulidwa liwunde, mwanti lichiŵa milango-milango"
  78,20,"Nombe matumbi gachityosyedwa m’mangwakwe, mwanti gachiŵa lunyisinyisi"
  78,21,Chisimu Jahannama jikuŵa nkwajembecheya (ŵakulemwa)
  78,22,Kwa ŵakusumba mpika gaŵele malo gakuujila
  78,23,Tachiŵa nkutama mwalakwemo yaka-yaka
  78,24,Ngasapasya mwalakwemo kusisimila namuno yakumwa (yakumasya njota)
  78,25,Ikaŵeje mesi gamasemule nnope ni uwowu
  78,26,(Kuŵa) malipilo gakulandanila (ni masengo gao)
  78,27,Chisimu ŵanganyao ŵaliji ali ngaakwembecheya ya chiŵalanjilo
  78,28,Ni ŵaikaaniile imanyilo Yetu naikanilape
  78,29,Soni chindu chilichose tuchisunjile paachilemba m’Chitabu
  78,30,Basi pasyani; mwanti ngatun'jonjechesya (inepe) ikaŵeje ilagasyo (pachanya pa ilagasyo)
  78,31,Chisimu ŵaoga (wakun’jogopa Allah) akwete kupata malo ga kupunda (ku Mbepo)
  78,32,Matimbe gana uŵigo ni itela ya zabibu
  78,33,Ni ŵaali ŵangagwa maŵele ŵakulandana misingu
  78,34,Kwisa soni ipanda yachigumbalile
  78,35,Ngasaja kupikana mwalakwemo yangali mate atamuno unami
  78,36,"(Aga ni) malipilo gakuumila kwa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah), ntuuka wakwana"
  78,37,"M'mbuje jwa kumawunde ni petaka ni yaili chilikati chakwe, Jwaukoto wejinji. Pangali ŵachachikola machili gakuŵecheta Najo"
  78,38,"Lisiku lyatiuchijima Nsimu (Jibulilu) pamo ni Achimalaika m’misela; ngasaŵecheta (jwalijose) ikaŵeje jwatachipedwa lusa ni (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji, ni tachiŵecheta yakulungamika"
  78,39,"Lyele ni Lisiku lyakuonaonape, basi jwaakusaka aliikolochesye chilepe malo gakuujila kwa M'mbujegwe (Allah)"
  78,40,"Chisimu Uwwe tukuntetela chilepe ya ilagasyo yakuŵandika. Lisiku lyataachiiwona mundu yagaalongwesye makono gakwe, nitachiŵecheta kafili kuti: “Nkongwene! Bola ningaliji litaka.”"
  79,1,Ngwaalumbila (Achimalaika) ŵaakuchuŵaga (mitima ja makafili) mwamachili
  79,2,Ngwaalumbila soni (Achimalaika) ŵaakutyosyaga (mitima ja ŵandu ŵakulupilila) mwambolembole
  79,3,"Nguilumbila soni yaying'ambila mwangalechesya (munnengaleenga, mpela Achimalaika ni ndondwa)"
  79,4,Ni ŵaakutendesyana mpikisano (pakwanilisya malamusi ga Allah)
  79,5,Ni (Achimalaika) ŵaakuŵalaganya malamusi (ga Allah pakugaŵika m’mangwakwe)
  79,6,Lisiku lyalichigombedwa lipenga lyandanda (lyaliichitenganya chilichose ni kuwa)
  79,7,Lichilikuichisya lipenga lyaaŵili (yosope yene nikwimuka ni kola umi)
  79,8,Lyele lisikulyo mitima (jine) jichitetemela ni woga
  79,9,Meso ga (achinsyene) mitimajo gachiteteŵala
  79,10,"(Makafili) gakasatiji: “Ana uwwe yakuona chachituuchisya mukaŵe ketu kakala (nikuŵa niumi soni)"
  79,11,Kutendaga uwwe tuli maupa gepukuswe-pukuswe?”
  79,12,"Ŵatite (mwachisyawumi ni mwakuchindimbula): “Nakuŵaga kwele kuujilaako kusyene, basi kuchiŵa kuujila kwachasiko (kwangali ukoto kukwetu).”"
  79,13,Chisimu walakweo ni n'gumiilo umpepe
  79,14,Basi ajile sayi ŵanganyao tachigamba kuona ali pachanya petaka
  79,15,Ana jinyyiche abali ja Musa
  79,16,Pandema jaŵam'bilaasile Ambujegwe (Allah) pachiŵata chakutakata (chakuŵilanjikwa) Tuwaa
  79,17,"(Nikuntenda kuti): Jaawulani kwa Firiauna, chisimu jwalakwejo jusumbile mpika"
  79,18,"Ni nkajile: “Ana nkusaka kuti n'diiswejesye?”"
  79,19,“Ni nan'jongolele kwa Ambuje ŵenu kuti mwaajogopeje?”
  79,20,Basi niŵannosisye chisimosimo chekulungwa
  79,21,Nambo jwaakaaniile nikunyosya
  79,22,Kaneka jwachitundumalile (chikulupi) aku junankulimbichila (kwasiŵilila ŵandu kwa Allah)
  79,23,Basi jwaasonganganyisye (asaŵi) nikwaŵilanga (ŵandu)
  79,24,"Ni jwatite: “Une ni nam'mbuje gwenu jwapenani kusyene!”"
  79,25,Basi Allah ni ŵankwembekenye ni ipotesi ligongo lya maloŵe gakwe gambesi ni gandanda
  79,26,Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chaamuko kwa mundu jwaakun'jogopa (Allah)
  79,27,Ana ŵanganyammwe niŵakusausya nnope kagumbidwe (kenu) kapena liwunde lyaŵalitaŵile
  79,28,Ŵalinyakwile nsingu wakwe nikulikolosya
  79,29,Ni ŵachiunichile chilo chakwe (nichipi) nikulikoposya lilanguka lyakwe (muusi)
  79,30,Nombe litaka panyuma payalakweyo ŵalitandiche
  79,31,Ŵakopwesye mwalakwemo mesi gakwe ni mopo wakwe
  79,32,Nombe matumbi ŵagasimiiche
  79,33,(Kuŵa) yakunsengwasya ŵanganyammwe ni ilango yenu
  79,34,Basi ndema jaliichiika likungu lyekulungwa nnope (Kiyama)
  79,35,Lyele lisikulyo mundu tachikumbuchila yaŵapanganyisye
  79,36,Nombe Moto Waukali wuchiŵichidwa palangulangu kwa nkulola (jwalijose)
  79,37,Sano mundu jwaŵasumbile mpika
  79,38,Ni kulongosya umi wa duniya
  79,39,Chisimu Moto Waukali basi ni liuto lyakwe
  79,40,"Sano jwaakogopa kuti tachija kwima pameso pa Ambujegwe (Allah), nikuwukanyaga ntima ku isako yakusakala"
  79,41,Chisimu Litimbe lya ku Mbepo basi ni liuto lyakwe
  79,42,"Akum'buusya (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) ya ndema (jakwichila Kiyama kuti): “Jichiŵa chakachi?”"
  79,43,Mmwe nganinkola umanyilisi wanti nikujitomeka
  79,44,Kwa Ambuje ŵenupe (Allah) ni kuchipelela kwakwe (kwa umanyilisi wa Kiyama)
  79,45,Mmwe masengo genu ni kwaatetela ŵaakujijogopa (Kiyamajo)
  79,46,Chisimu ŵanganyao lisiku lyatachijiona (Kiyamajo) tachiŵa nti chisawu nganatama (pa duniya) ikaŵeje ligulo limo kapena kundaŵi kwakwe
  80,1,Jwautile sinya (Muhammadi ﷺ) ni kulola kumbali
  80,2,Ligongo lyakum’bichiilila jwangalola
  80,3,Ana chichi chachimmanyisye kuti mwine jwalakwejo kuŵa nkuliswejesya (ku ilemwa)
  80,4,"Mwine chakumbuchile, basi nikunkamuchisya kumbuchilako"
  80,5,Nambo mundu jwaliweni kusichila
  80,6,Basi jwalakwejo mmwe ni nkunkosoŵalila
  80,7,Pangalitu ulemwa kukwenu naga ngaakuliswejesya (ku ukafili)
  80,8,Nambo mundu jwam’bichilile aku juchikangamalaga
  80,9,Soni jwalakwejo ali nkun'jogopa (Allah)
  80,10,Basi ya jwalakwejo mmwe ni nkuikwanjila
  80,11,Ngwamba (ngasintenda iyyo)! Chisimu galakwe (ma Ȃyaga) gaŵele chikumbusyo
  80,12,Basi jwaakusaka talikumbusye najo (Qur’anijo)
  80,13,(Jili) mu ikalakala yakuchimbichikwa
  80,14,"Yapenani, yakuswejesyedwa"
  80,15,Ili m’makono mwa akulemba (Achimalaika)
  80,16,"Ŵakuchimbichika, ŵaakunda (malamusi)"
  80,17,"Pamasile palaniwe mundu (kafili), kanila kwakwe kwalakweku ni kwantiuli"
  80,18,Ana an'gumbile kuumila mu chinduchi
  80,19,"Kuumila m’mesi (gaŵalume ni ŵakongwe) an'gumbile, ni kumpanjila mpango (wakagumbidwe kakwe)"
  80,20,Kaneka naakun'jepepachisyaga litala (lyakopochela ku duniya)
  80,21,Kaneko nakasampaga chiwa ni kunsiika m’malembe
  80,22,Soni patachisakapo tachinsyusya
  80,23,Ngwamba! Chisimu (kafili) nganakwanilisyepe yannamwile (Allah)
  80,24,Basi achetelele mundu ya yakulya yakwe
  80,25,Chisimu Uwwe tukasakusula mesi (gawula) mwamachili
  80,26,Kaneka ni tukasaligangaga litaka kuliganga kusyene
  80,27,Ni tukasakoposya mwalakwemo songolo
  80,28,Kwisa soni isogosi ya zabibu ni maupulu (gakulya ilango)
  80,29,Ni kwisa soni isogosi ya zaituni (yakwenga mauta) ni itela yatende
  80,30,Ni migunda jaitela yejinji
  80,31,Kwisa soni isogosi (yamitundu mitundu) ni mopo
  80,32,(Kuŵa) yakunsengwasya ŵanganyammwe ni ilango yenu
  80,33,Basi ndema jaliichiika lipenga lyakusiŵa m’mawiwi (ligongo lya machili gakwe)
  80,34,Lyele lisikulyo mundu tachatila achimwenegwe
  80,35,Kwisa soni mamagwe ni babagwe
  80,36,Ni kwisa soni ŵankwakwe ni ŵanache ŵakwe
  80,37,Mundu jwalijose mwa ŵanganyao lyele lisikulyo tachikola yakunkwanila (kuntendekasya kuti akakosoŵalila ya jwine)
  80,38,Ngope sine lyele lisikulyo sichiŵa syakumelemenda
  80,39,Syakusechelela ni kusengwa (pakupikana yakuja ku Mbepo)
  80,40,Sano ngope sine lyele lisikulyo sichipakala luwundu
  80,41,Sichiŵa siunichilidwe ni chipi
  80,42,Ŵanganyao ni ŵali achimakafili ŵakusakasya nnope
  81,1,Pandema jalichikulunjidwa lyuŵa (nikutyoka lilanguka lyakwe)
  81,2,Ni ndema jasichipatuka ndondwa
  81,3,Ni ndema jagachijendesyedwa matumbi (paagachuŵa m’mangwakwe)
  81,4,Ni ndema jasichilechedwa ngamiya syana maŵele gepele
  81,5,Ni ndema jaichisonganganyisyidwa inyama yamwitinji
  81,6,Ni ndema jasichikolesyedwa mbwani moto
  81,7,Ni ndema jajichilumbikanyisyidwa mitima (ku ilu yakwe)
  81,8,Ni ndema jachachiwusyidwa mwanache jwankwongwe jwaŵasichidwe ali jwaumi
  81,9,Kuti ŵawulajidwe ni ulemwachi
  81,10,Ni ndema jaichipindikulidwa ikalakala (mugalembedwe masengo gamundu)
  81,11,Ni ndema jalichitandukulidwa liwunde
  81,12,Ni ndema jauchikwisilidwa Moto Waukali
  81,13,Ni ndema jajichiŵandichisyidwa Mbepo
  81,14,Mundu jwalijose tachimanyilila yayiche nayo
  81,15,Basi ngusilumbila ndondwa syasikusisika muusi
  81,16,(Ni) syasikwendaga (chilo kaneka) ni kusisika pakutiŵila
  81,17,Ni nguchilumbila soni chilo ndema jachikwika ni kutyoka
  81,18,Ni ngukulumbila soni kumasikusiku ndema jakukulanguka
  81,19,Chisimu aji (Qur’aniji) gaŵele maloŵe ga (kulungusyidwa ni) Ntenga Jwakuchimbichika (Jibulilu)
  81,20,"Nsyene machili, soni jwana uchimbichimbi wapenani kwa (Allah) Nsyene Arishi (Chindanda Chaulungu)"
  81,21,Jwakundidwa malamusi kwinaniko (ni Achimalaika) soni jwakulupichika
  81,22,Soni Nnongo n'jenuju (Muhammadi ﷺ) nganaŵa jwamasoka
  81,23,Soni chisimu chene (Muhammadi ﷺ) ŵam'bweni jwalakwe (Jibulilu mu kagumbidwe kakwe kasyesyene) kuchipelela chameso chakuonechela (cha ku ngopoko lyuŵa)
  81,24,Soni jwalakwe nganijuŵa jwausuchi pa (umanyilisi wa) yakusisika
  81,25,Soni aji (Qur’an) nganigaŵa maloŵe ga shetani jwakuŵinjidwa
  81,26,Nambi kwapi nkuja
  81,27,Nganijiŵa aji (Qur’an) ikaŵeje chikumbusyo cha iwumbe yosope
  81,28,Kwa mundu jwaakusaka mwa jenumanja kuti ajongoche
  81,29,"Ni nganim'ba nsachile, ikaŵeje akasache kaje Allah M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope"
  82,1,Pandema jalichipasuka liwunde
  82,2,Ni ndema jasichilakatika ndondwa
  82,3,Ni ndema jasichigumuchila mbwani
  82,4,Ni ndema jagachiukulidwa malembe
  82,5,Mundu jwalijose juchimanyilila yajwalongwesye (kupanganya) ni yajwalesile munyuma
  82,6,E mmwe amundu! Ana ni chichi chinnyenjile kwa (kwikanila kunnyosya) M’mbuje gwenu (Allah) Jwantuka wejinji
  82,7,"Ajula jwaŵan'gumbile, ni kunkolosya pa kunnandanya (iŵalo yenu) soni ni kun'golosya (nsingu wenu)"
  82,8,Mukawoneche kalikose kaŵasachile (kuti m'bonecheje) ŵampanganyisye
  82,9,Ngwamba! Nambo kuti ŵanganyammwe nkukanila ya malipilo
  82,10,Soni chisimu kwa jenumanja kwana (Achimalaika) ŵakunnolela (ni kusunga itendo yenu)
  82,11,"Ŵakuchimbichika, ŵakulemba"
  82,12,Akumanyilila yankuntenda
  82,13,Chisimu atenda ngoto chachiŵa nchindimba (mu Mbepo Jakusengwasya)
  82,14,"Sano ŵandu ŵakusakasya nnope, chisimu chene tachiŵa m’Moto Waukali"
  82,15,Chachiujinjila Lisiku Lyamalipilo
  82,16,Soni ŵanganyao ngasaŵa asoŵile mwalakwemo (pakopoka ata panandi)
  82,17,Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya Lisiku Lyamalipilo
  82,18,Soni ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya Lisiku Lyamalipilo
  82,19,Lyele ni lisiku lyangakola mundu chilichose chanti ni kunkamuchisya mundu jwine. Nombe ulamusi (wosope) lyele lisikulyo uchiŵa wa Allah pe
  83,1,Ipotesi ni yao ŵakupuungusya (miliingo)
  83,2,Aŵala ŵaakutiji naga ndema jaakulilinjila ku ŵandu (pakwasuma indu yao) akasaligumbachisyaga
  83,3,Nambo pa ndema jaakwaaliinjila (ŵanduo) kapena kwapimila (pakwasumisya indu) akupungusyaga
  83,4,Ana ngakuganisya ŵanganyao yanti chachiukulidwa (m’malembe)
  83,5,Pa Lisiku Lyekulungwa nnope
  83,6,Lisiku lyatachijima ŵandu pameso pa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope
  83,7,Yakuona! Chisimu yakulembedwa ya (masengo ga) ŵandu ŵakusakasya nnope ili mu Sijjin
  83,8,Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya Sijjin
  83,9,Chele ni chitabu (chekulungwa) chachilembedwe (nkati mwakwe yakusakalape)
  83,10,Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila
  83,11,Aŵala ŵakukanila ya Lisiku Lyamalipilo
  83,12,Ni pangali jwampaka alikanile lyalakwelyo ikaŵeje jwalijose jwakusumba mpika jwasambi syejinji
  83,13,"Pandema jakusoomedwa kukwakwe ma Ȃya Getu akasatiji: “Asi ni adisiadisi sya ŵandu ŵandanda.”"
  83,14,Ngwamba! Nambo kuti m’mitima mwao mwana nkuwo wa (ilemwa) yaaŵele ali nkupanganya
  83,15,Yakuona! Chisimu ŵanganyao lyele lisikulyo kwa M’mbuje gwao (Allah) tachisiŵilidwa (mwanti ngaaja kum’bona)
  83,16,Kaneka chisimu ŵanganyao tachiujinjila Moto Waukali
  83,17,"Kaneko ni kuchiŵechetedwa kuti: “Ayi ni ayilayila yamwaliji nkuikanila.”"
  83,18,Yakuona! Chisimu yakulembedwa ya (masengo ga) atenda ngoto ili mu Illiyyun
  83,19,Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya Illiyyun
  83,20,Chalakwecho ni chitabu (chekulungwa) chachilembedwe (nkati mwakwe yambonepe)
  83,21,Akuchiŵichilaga umboni (Achimalaika) ŵaŵandichisyidwe (kwa Allah)
  83,22,Chisimu atenda ngoto tachiŵa m’chindimba (mu Mbepo Jakusengwasya)
  83,23,Ali pachanya pa indanda yetandiche chenene aku achilolaga (ku chindimba chaŵapele ni kum'bona soni Allah)
  83,24,Tinchikumanyilila pangope syao kumelemenda kwa chindimba
  83,25,Takamwesyedweje nkologo wambone nnope wesiŵe (ni isiŵilo yakulimbangana)
  83,26,Kumbesi kwa kumwako (chikukanunjileje luwumba lwa) miski. Sano kuti akaipate yele basi apikisane akupikisana (pakutenda yambone)
  83,27,Soni chakuwanganyichisya chakwe (nkologowo chigakaŵe) mesi gakuumila mu Tasnim
  83,28,Jwalakwejo ni tutumule jwachakamweje (ŵandu) ŵakuŵandichisyidwa (kwa Allah)
  83,29,Chisimu (ku duniya) ŵandu ŵaŵanneŵele (Allah) ŵaliji nkwaseka ŵandu ŵakulupilila
  83,30,Mwanti ndema jaŵaliji nkupita (ŵakulupililao) paali ŵanganyao ŵaliji nkukupililana meso (mwakuchembulusya)
  83,31,Sano naga atite agalauche kuja kwaachin'jao ŵagalaukaga ali nkusengwa (ligongo lya kuchembulusya kwao)
  83,32,"Soni naga ali ŵawenimo ŵatiji: “Chisimu ŵanganyaŵa ni ŵali ŵakupotela nnope.”"
  83,33,Nambotu (achimakafilio) nganatumisyidwa kuŵa ŵakwalolela (Asilamu nikusunga itendo yao)
  83,34,Nambo lelojino (lisiku lya Kiyama) ŵandu ŵaŵakulupilile chaŵe ali nkugaseka makafili
  83,35,Ali pachanya pa indanda yetandiche chenene aku achigalolaga (makafiligo galinkulagasika)
  83,36,Ana alipiidwe achimakafili pa yaŵaliji nkutenda
  84,1,Pandema jalichipapuka liwunde
  84,2,"Ni kwisa kunda lilamusi lya M’mbujeegwe, soni liichiŵajilwa (kuti likunde)"
  84,3,Ni ndema jalichijasyisyidwa litaka (pakusyaga matumbi ni ikwesya)
  84,4,Ni kwisa kuponya kusa (litakalyo) yayaliji nkati mwakwe nikuŵa mwangali chachipali
  84,5,"Ni kwisa kunda lilamusi lya M’mbujeegwe, soni liichiŵajilwa (kuti likunde)"
  84,6,"E mmwe amundu! Chisimutu mmwe nkukangamala wa kwa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) nchilimbichilaga (kutenda itendo yambone kapena yakusakala), basi ni tinchisimangana nayo (pa lisiku lya Kiyamalyo)"
  84,7,Sano mundu jwatachipedwa chitabu chakwe ku nkono wakwe wan'dyo
  84,8,Basi jwalakwe tachiŵalanjidwa kuŵalanjidwa kwakwepepala
  84,9,Soni ni tachiujila kwa achalongo achin'jakwe ali jwakusengwa
  84,10,Nambo mundu jwatachipedwa chitabu chakwe cha kunyuma kwa n'gongo wakwe
  84,11,"Basi jwalakwe, tachichiŵilanga chonasiko (kuti bola agambe kuwa, nambo ngasiyikomboleka)"
  84,12,Ni tachijinjila ku Moto Wakulapuka
  84,13,Chisimu jwalakwe jwaliji jwakusengwa (pajwaliji) ni achalongo achin'jakwe (ku duniya)
  84,14,Chisimu jwalakwe jwasimichisyaga kuti ngasaujila (kwa Allah)
  84,15,Elo! Chisimu Ambujegwe ŵaliji ali nkunnolechesya
  84,16,Basi ngukulumbila kuchejela kwegulo
  84,17,Kwisa soni chilo ni yachikusonganganyaga
  84,18,Ni mwesi ndema jaukwanila lilanguka (lyakwe)
  84,19,Chisimu ŵanganyammwe chinsimanganeje nako kaŵe kane kutyochela pa kaŵe kane (paumi wa duniya uno mpaka kwa Akhera)
  84,20,Ana akwete chichi ŵanganyao chikwatendekasya kuti akakulupilila
  84,21,Soni pati jichisoomedwaga kukwao Qur’an ŵangasujudu
  84,22,Nambo kuti achimakafili agamba kanila basi
  84,23,Sano Allah ni jwaakuyimanya chenene yaakusonganganya ŵanganyao
  84,24,Basi mwatagulilani ya ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope
  84,25,"Ikaŵeje aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, akwete kupata ŵanganyao malipilo gangamala"
  85,1,Ngulilumbila liwunde lyalikwete ndondwa syekulungwa-kulungwa ni mwakwenda mwakwe
  85,2,Ni Lisiku Lyeŵichidwe chilanga
  85,3,Kwisa soni nkuŵichila ni nkuŵichilidwa umboni
  85,4,Pamasile paŵalaniwe achinsyene masimbo
  85,5,(Ga) moto wawakwete sasu (syejinji syakuukolechesya ni kwachomela ŵandu ŵakulupilila)
  85,6,Pandema janti ŵanganyao ŵaliji ali chitamile mungulugulu mwakwe
  85,7,Soni ŵanganyao ŵaliji aku ali nkulolela yaŵaliji nkwatenda ŵakulupilila (yakwachoma motoyo)
  85,8,"Ni nganauwona ulemwa uliose kwa jamanjao ikaŵeje ligongo lyanti ŵaliji nkunkulupilila Allah Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwakulapilildwa kusyesyene"
  85,9,"Ajula Jwauli wakwe uchimwene wa kumawunde ni petaka, sanotu Allah pa chindu chilichose aŵele Mboni"
  85,10,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaŵalagasisye ŵakulupilila ŵachilume ni ŵakulupilila ŵachikongwe (pakwachoma moto) kaneka ni ngatenda toba, basi akwete kupata ilagasyo ya Jahannama, soni akwete kupata ilagasyo yakutinisya"
  85,11,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, akwete kupata Matimbe ga ku Mbepo gasikujilima cha pasi pakwe sulo. Kwalakweko nikupunda kwekulungwa"
  85,12,Chisimu kapeleche ka ilagasyo ka Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) kaŵele kaukali nnope
  85,13,Chisimu Jwelepejo ni juŵatandisye (gumba iwumbe) soni ni jutachiyiusya-usya (kuigumba panyuma pakonasika)
  85,14,Soni Jwalakwe ni Jwakululuka kusyene Jwachinonyelo chejinji
  85,15,"Nsyene Arish (Chindanda Chaulungu), Jwakuchimbichika kusyene"
  85,16,Jwakutenda yajukusaka mwangalepeleka
  85,17,Ana jinyyiche abali ja mikutula ja asilikali
  85,18,Achina Firiauna ni achina Samuda
  85,19,Nambo kuti achimakafili ali mu kukanila basi
  85,20,Sano Allah ni ŵasyungulile chakunyuma kwao
  85,21,Nambo jalakweji ni Qur’an Jakuchimbichika
  85,22,(Jilembedwe) mu Ubawo Wagosedwa
  86,1,Ngulilumbila liwunde ni chakwisa chilo
  86,2,Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya chakwisa chilo
  86,3,(Jalakwejo ni) ndondwa jakupowola (chipi ligongo lya kuŵala nnope)
  86,4,Pangali mundu jwalijose ikaŵeje kwa jwalakwejo kwana nkunnolela (jwaakusunga itendo yakwe)
  86,5,"Basi achetelele mundu, ana agumbidwe kuumila ku chichi"
  86,6,Agumbidwe kuumila ku mesi gakusumbika
  86,7,Gakopokaga kutyochela chilikati cha maupa ga n'gongo (wa ŵalume) ni maupa ga chidali (cha ŵakongwe)
  86,8,Chisimu Jwalakwe (Allah) pakum'buchisya (kuwumi mundujo) aŵele Jwakombola kusyene
  86,9,Lisiku lyasichionechela papaswela asili (syosope)
  86,10,Ni ngasakola (mundujo) machili galigose namuno nkulupusyo
  86,11,Ngukulumbila kwinani kwagwisyagwisya wula
  86,12,Ni ngulilumbila soni litaka lyaliganjikaga (pakoposya mmela)
  86,13,Chisimu jalakwe (Qur’aniji) gaŵele maloŵe gakulekanganya (chilikati cha yakuona ni yaunami)
  86,14,Soni jalakweji nganijiŵa chindu chambenje
  86,15,Chisimu ŵanganyao akuŵa ali nkutenda malindi (kwa Asilamu)
  86,16,None ni ngwauchisya malindi (gaogo pangaapa ilagasyo chitema kuti alilechelele)
  86,17,"Basi, mwalechelesyani achimakafili, mwalechelelani panandipe (chaiwone)"
  87,1,Liswejesyani lina lya Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) Ŵapenani kusyene
  87,2,Aŵala ŵaŵagumbile (chilichose) ni kuchikolosya
  87,3,Soni Aŵala ŵaŵapimiile (chilichose mwachiichiŵeela) ni kuchijongolela (ku yaŵachipimileyo)
  87,4,Soni Aŵala ŵaakumesya mopo
  87,5,Ni kuwusyusya kuŵa wejumu ŵakupiililila
  87,6,Chitunsoomesye ni ngan'diŵalila
  87,7,"Ikaŵeje yasachile Allah, chisimu Jwalakwe jukumanyililaga yakuonechela ni yayikasasisika"
  87,8,Ni chitun'jepepachisye litala lyakwalukangana (lyakutendela yambone)
  87,9,Basi kumbusyani naga kumbusyako tikuŵe kwakamuchisya
  87,10,Talikumbusye mundu jwaakun'jogopa (Allah)
  87,11,Ni takuŵambale (mundu) jwakusakala nnope
  87,12,Ajula jwatakajinjile ku Moto Wekulungwa
  87,13,"Soni ngachija kumpata chiwa mwalakwemo, nambo soni ngaaja kuŵa ni umi (wambone)"
  87,14,Pamasile paapundile mundu jwaliswejesye (ntima wakwe)
  87,15,Ni akuŵa ali nkulikumbuchila Lina lya Ambujegwe (pakulikolanga) aku achiswaliji
  87,16,Nambo ŵanganyammwe nkulongosya umi wa duniya
  87,17,Kutendaga Akhera ni jambone nnope soni jandamo
  87,18,Chisimu yalakweyi yili mu ikalakala yandanda
  87,19,Ikalakala ya Ibrahima ni Musa
  88,1,"Ana jinyyiche abali ja chakuunichila (ŵandu ni yogoyo yakwe, jajili Kiyama)"
  88,2,Ngope sine lyele lisikulyo sichiŵa syakunyosyeka
  88,3,"Syasyapanganyisye masengo (gasambi ku duniya), syakupela (nikwaluka ku Akhera)"
  88,4,Sichijinjila ku Moto Wakupoteka nnope
  88,5,Sichimwesyedwa mu tutumule jwansemule kusyene
  88,6,Ngasakola ŵanganyao yakulya ikaŵeje miŵa janchongwe
  88,7,Jangajimbasya soni jangakamuchisya ku sala
  88,8,Ngope sine lyele lisikulyo sichiŵa m’chindimba
  88,9,Ligongo lya masengo gakwe (gambone) sichiŵa syakusengwa
  88,10,Ku Mbepo Japenani
  88,11,Ngasisija kupikana kwalakweko yangali mate
  88,12,Kweleko kwana tutumule jwakujilimaga
  88,13,Kweleko kwana itengu yauchimbichimbi yenyakulidwe
  88,14,Ni migawo jeŵichidwe (chilepe)
  88,15,Ni misago jejalidwe mu ntungo wambone
  88,16,Ni yakutandika yaofuofu yetandichidwe posepose
  88,17,Ana ngakujiona ngamiya yajatite kagumbidwe
  88,18,Ni liwunde yalyatite kanyakulidwe
  88,19,Ni matumbi yagatite kasimichidwe
  88,20,Ni litaka yalyatite katandichidwe
  88,21,"Basi kumbusyani, chisimu mmwejo ni nkukumbusya"
  88,22,Nganim'batu mmwe ŵakwakanganichisya ŵanganyao (chikulupi)
  88,23,Ikaŵeje jwatagalauche (kuleka masengo gambone) ni kufulu (kuleka Usilamu)
  88,24,Basi Allah tachinnagasya ni ilagasyo yekulungwa nnope
  88,25,Chisimu Kukwetu pe ni kwakuujila kwao
  88,26,Soni chisimu kuŵalanjidwa kwao kuli Nowe
  89,1,Ngukulumbila kumasikusiku
  89,2,Ni ilo likumi (yandanda yamwesi wa Mfungotatu)
  89,3,Ni (indu yayili) yiŵiliyiŵili kwisa soni (yayili) chimochimo
  89,4,Ni chilo ndema jachikuŵigula
  89,5,"Ana mu yalakweyi ngaŵa mwana kulumbila kwakwanila, kwa jwakwete lunda"
  89,6,Ana nganinyyiona yaŵatite Ambuje ŵenu kaape ipotesi ŵanya Adi
  89,7,Ŵa ku Irama; achalewulewu mpela misaati
  89,8,Ŵanganagumbidweje ŵane ŵanti chisawu ŵanganyao mu ilambo (ine)
  89,9,Ni ŵanya Asamuda ŵaŵaliji nkusokola maganga pachiŵata (chakuŵilanjikwa Wadi Qura kuŵa majumba gao)
  89,10,Kwisa soni Firiauna nsyene ichili (yakulimbanganyichisya uchimwene wakwe)
  89,11,Aŵala ŵana kusumbaga mpika mu ilambo (pakusakasya)
  89,12,Ni ŵatupiye mwalakwemo kuwatanganya
  89,13,Basi Ambuje ŵenu ŵapungulile ŵanganyao mitundu ja ilagasyo (yakupoteka nnope)
  89,14,"Chisimu Ambuje ŵenu aŵele Ŵang'unulila (masengo ga ŵandu, mwanti chachalipila mwaakupanganyichisya)"
  89,15,"Sano mundu ndema jaakun'dinga Ambujegwe pakunchimbichisya ni kumpa chindimba, basi akasatiji: “Ambuje ŵangu anjimbichisye (ligongo une nijwakuŵajilwa kupata yeleyi).”"
  89,16,"Nambo ndema jaakun'dinga pakunnandiyichisya lisiki lyakwe, akasatiji: “Ambuje ŵangu anjalwisye.”"
  89,17,Ngwamba! Nambo kuti ngankwatendelaga yaukoto ŵanache ŵawina
  89,18,Soni ngankuchisyanaga yaagaliisya masikini
  89,19,Ni nkulyaga chipanje chamalekwa kalye kakutunduka
  89,20,Ni nkuchinonyelaga soni chipanje kachinonyele kakupelenganya nnope
  89,21,Ngaŵa (mŵankutendelamo)! Ndema jalichisyajidwa litaka syajidwe-syajidwe
  89,22,"Ni kwika Ambuje ŵenu (Allah kukwiilanya magambo), Achimalaika ali ndandanda"
  89,23,"Ni kwikanajo lyele lisikulyo Jahannama! Lyele lisikulyo mundu tachikumbuchila (yaŵapanganyisye), nambo ana kuchinkamuchisya chichi kwele kumbuchilako"
  89,24,"Tachiti (pakuligamba): “Nkongwene! Bola ngalongosye (yambone yakungamuchisya) pa umi wangu (walelo uno).”"
  89,25,"Mwanti palyele lisikuli, pangali jwampaka apeleche ilagasyo mwatachipelechela (Allah)"
  89,26,Soni pangali jwampaka ataŵe mwatachitaŵila (Jwalakwe)
  89,27,E mmwe antima ŵakutulala
  89,28,Wujilani kwa Ambuje ŵenu n'di ŵakusengwa ni kunonyeledwa
  89,29,Jinjilani mwikuga lya achikapolo Ŵangu
  89,30,Soni jinjilani ku Mbepo Jangu
  90,1,Nguulumbila awu musi (wa Maaka)
  90,2,Soni mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) tinchiŵa ŵakundisyidwa (kuputa ngondo) mu wele musiwu
  90,3,Ni ngullumbila soni nangolo ni uŵelesi wajuŵeleche
  90,4,Chisimu pamasile patun'gumbile mundu m’matabu
  90,5,Ana juganichisya yanti pangali ŵampaka ankombole (kumpa ilagasyo)
  90,6,"Jukuŵecheta (mwakutwanga kuti): “Njonasile yipanje yejinji (kuti Usilamu usilale).”"
  90,7,Ana juganichisya kuti pangali ŵaakun'bona
  90,8,Ana nganitun'gumbila meso gaŵili (gajukulolela)
  90,9,Ni lulimi kwisa soni ngomo siŵili (syajukuŵechetela)
  90,10,"Ni tun’jongolele matala gaŵili (lyambone ni lyakusakala, kuti jusagule lyajukusaka)"
  90,11,Ana pakwete pajujesile litala lyamwitumbi (lyalikam’bikasye ku Mbepo)
  90,12,Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya litala lyamwitumbi
  90,13,"(Litala lyamwitumbi nimasengo gambone nambo gakunonopa, mpela): gopola kapolo"
  90,14,Kapena kupeleka yakulya palisiku lyasala
  90,15,(Kumpa) jwawina jwapaulongo
  90,16,Kapena masikini jwaluwunduwundupe (ligongo lyakulaga nnope)
  90,17,"Soni nikuŵa (nkutola yakulyajo) jumpepe mwa aŵala ŵaakulupilile, ni kulimbikasyanaga ya kupilila soni ni kulimbikasyanaga ya kutendelana chanasa"
  90,18,Ŵanganyao niŵandu ŵakun'dyo (ŵali ŵambone)
  90,19,Nambo ŵandu ŵaagakaaniile ma Ȃya Getu ŵanganyao niŵandu ŵakunchiji (ŵali ŵakusakala)
  90,20,Kwaŵanganyao kuchiŵa kwana Moto Wakuunichila ni kutika (wangali pakopochela)
  91,1,Ngulilumbila lyuŵa ni lilanguka lyakwe
  91,2,Ni mwesi ndema jaukulikuya (lyuŵalyo)
  91,3,Ni muusi ndema jaukulilosya palangulangu
  91,4,Ni chilo ndema jachikuliunichila (kuti likaoneka)
  91,5,Kwisa soni liwunde ni Juŵalitaŵile (mwakulitalichisya)
  91,6,Ni litaka ni Juŵalitandiche (mwakulijaasasya)
  91,7,Kwisa soni ntima ni Juŵaukolosisye
  91,8,Basi ni jwaumanyisye yakusakala yakwe ni yambone yakwe
  91,9,Pamasile paapundile jwauswejesye (ntima wakwe)
  91,10,Soni pamasile papelelwe jwautwinyichisye (ntima wakwe mu sambi)
  91,11,Ŵaakaaniile ŵanya Asamudu ligongo lyakusumba mpika kwao
  91,12,Ndema jajwalipeleche jwakusakalilwa jwao (kuulaga ngamiya)
  91,13,"Basi Ntenga jwa Allah (Swaleh) ŵasalile kuti: “(Aji ni) ngamiya ja Allah, sano ngasin'jikanyaga kumwa mesi (palisiku lyakwe)"
  91,14,Nambo ŵankaaniile nikujiulaga; basi Ambuje ŵao ŵajonasile ligongo lya chileŵi chao; niŵalandenye pachonasikocho
  91,15,Soni jwangajogopa yakuichisya yakwe
  92,1,Nguchilumbila chilo ndema jachikuunichila (chilichose ni chipi chakwe)
  92,2,Ni muusi ndema jakukulanguka
  92,3,Ni Ajula (Allah) Jwagumbile chachilume ni chachikongwe
  92,4,Chisimu itendo yenu iŵele yakulekangana-lekangana
  92,5,Sano mundu jwaakutola (petala lya Allah) ni kuŵa niwoga (wakun'jogopa Jwalakwe)
  92,6,Ni kulupilila yambone nnope (yatakalipidwe ligongo lyakutola)
  92,7,Basi chitun'jepepachisye litala lyakwalukangana (lyakutendela yambone)
  92,8,Nambo mundu jwachatende ubayili ni kuliona kusichila
  92,9,Ni kanila yambone nnope (yaakajiile kuipata akatole)
  92,10,Basi chitun'jepepachisye litala lyausito (lyakutendela yakusakala)
  92,11,Soni ngasichija kunkamuchisya chipanje chakwe ndema jagwila (ku Moto)
  92,12,Chisimu Kukwetu nikwachili chongolo
  92,13,Soni chisimu Uwwe ni twachinsyene Akhera ni Duniya
  92,14,Basi nguntetela ya Moto waukolela (mwamachili)
  92,15,Ngaaja kuwujinjila ikaŵeje jwakusakalilwa nnope
  92,16,Ajula jwaakuŵa nkukanila ni kusyulula
  92,17,Ni takaŵambasyidwe nao mundu jwawoga kusyene (wakun'jogopa Allah)
  92,18,Ajula jwaakutola chipanje chakwe pakuliswejesya
  92,19,Soni pangali kwa jwalakwe jwalijose jwaŵantendele yaukoto yaikuŵa ili nkuusyidwa
  92,20,Ikaŵeje (jukutola) pakusachilila Ngope ja M’mbujeegwe (Allah) Jwapenani kusyene (kuti jukajione ku Akhera)
  92,21,Ni juchija kusengwa
  93,1,Nguulumbila nsana
  93,2,Ni chilo ndema jachikutulala
  93,3,Ngananneka Ambuje ŵenu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) soni nganam'benga
  93,4,Soni chisimu umi wambesi uŵele wambone nnope kukwenu kupunda wandanda
  93,5,Soni tachija kumpa Ambuje ŵenu (yambone) ni tinchisengwa
  93,6,Ana nganansimana n'di ŵawina nikumpa liwuto lyambone
  93,7,Soni ni ŵansimene n'di ŵangachimanya chongoko (jajili Qur'an ni malamusi ga Dini) nikun'jongola
  93,8,Ni ŵansimene soni n'di ŵakulaga nikunsichilisya
  93,9,Sano mwanache jwawina basi ngasimunchima
  93,10,Nombe soni jwakuŵenda basi ngasimunkalipila
  93,11,Soni chindimba cha Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) basi chisimbani (pakutogolela ni kutenda yambone)
  94,1,Ana nganitunsapangulila (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) chidali chenu (pakumpa utume)
  94,2,"Ni tuntuusile nsigo wenu (wausito wa kalungusye ka utenga, pakun’jepepachisya kalungusye kakwe)"
  94,3,Awula (nsigo wakwe) wawalumbisye n'gongo wenu
  94,4,Ni tunnyakuliile kusaalidwa kwenu
  94,5,Basi chisimu pakuli kunonopa pana kwepepala
  94,6,Chisimu pakuli kunonopa pana kwepepala
  94,7,"Sano pati mmalisyisye (masengo genu), basi limbichilani (kutenda ibada)"
  94,8,Soni kwa Ambuje ŵenu pe (Allah) basi sachililani (ukoto Wakwe)
  95,1,Nguulumbila nkuju ni nzaituni
  95,2,Ni litumbi lya Sinai
  95,3,Kwisa soni awu nsinda (wa Maaka) wantunjelele
  95,4,Chisimu pamasile patun'gumbile mundu mu kagumbidwe kambone nnope
  95,5,Kaneka nitukum'busyaaga kuŵa jwapasi kwapunda ŵapasi wosope (pa uchekulu wakulepela nao kutenda yambone)
  95,6,"Ikaŵeje ŵandu ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone (ali ŵachilimbanganile), basi akwete kupata ŵanganyao malipilo gangamala"
  95,7,Ana panyuma (pa kuimanya yele) nichichi chikuntendekasya kanila ya malipilo (ga pa Kiyama)
  95,8,Ana Allah nganaŵa Nkwiilanya chenene (magambo) kwapunda akwiilanya wosope
  96,1,Soomani mu lina lya Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) ŵaagumbile
  96,2,Agumbile mundu kuumila mu chipande chamyasi jekamatane
  96,3,Soomani! Soni Ambuje ŵenu ni Ŵantuka kusyene
  96,4,Aŵala ŵaajiganyisye (kulemba) ni chakulembela
  96,5,An'jiganyisye mundu yaŵalekaga ngaimanya
  96,6,Yakuona! Chisimu mundu akuŵaga jwakusumba mpika (pa kulikwesya)
  96,7,Ligongo lyakuliona kusichila
  96,8,Chisimu kwa Ambuje ŵenu pe (Allah) ni kwakuujila
  96,9,Ana mum'bweni ajula jwaakuŵa nkunkaanya
  96,10,Kapolo (jwa Allah) ndema jajukusaka kuswali
  96,11,Ana nkuyiona uli najuŵaga (Muhammadi ﷺ) juli pachongoko
  96,12,Kapena jukulamula ya woga (wakun'jogopa Allah)
  96,13,Nambi nkuyiona uli naŵaga (Abujahalio) akukanila ni kusyulula
  96,14,Ana ngaakumanyilila yanti Allah akwaona (yaakutenda)
  96,15,"Ngwamba! Chisimu naga ngaakuleka, chiitwawuta umbo syapewuwo (pakwaponya ku Moto)"
  96,16,Liwuwo lyakwe lyaunami soni lyakulemwa
  96,17,Basi ŵaaŵilanje ŵandu ŵakwe (kuti ankamuchisye)
  96,18,Nowe chitwaŵilanje Azabaniya (asilikali ŵa ku Moto)
  96,19,"Ngwamba! Mmwe ngasimunkunda jwalakwejo, nambo nsujuduji (kuswali) ni n’diŵandichisyeje (kwa Allah)"
  97,1,Chisimu Uwwe tujitulwisye jalakwe (Qur'aniji) m’Chilo Chakuchimbichika
  97,2,Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya Chilo Chakuchimbichika
  97,3,Chilo Chakuchimbichikachi chiŵele chambone nnope kupunda myesi jakwana sausande
  97,4,"Achimalaika akasatulukaga pamo ni Nsimu (Jibulilu) mu Chele (Chilochi) kwa lisosa lya M’mbuje gwao, kwisa kulondesya chindu chilichose (pakuchiŵika mu mpango wakwe)"
  97,5,"Ntunjelele-tunjelelepe! Chele Chilocho, mpaka kumasikusiku"
  98,1,"Ŵandu achimakafili kutandila achinsyene chitabu (Ayuda ni Akilisito) kwisa soni ŵakuwanganya (Allah ni isanamu), nganaŵa alekangene (ni ukafili wao) kwikanila ndema ja chayichilile chilosyo chakuonechela palangulangu"
  98,2,(Jwali) Ntenga (Muhammadi ﷺ) jwakuumila kwa Allah jwaakusooma (Qur’an jajili mu) ikalakala yakuswejesyedwa
  98,3,Mwalakwemo mwana malamusi gagoloka
  98,4,"Chisimu Allah akupeleka chanasa kwa Ntume (Muhammadi ﷺ), nombe nao soni Achimalaika (akum’bombelaga chanasa Ntumejo ﷺ). E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Mum’bombelani chanasa jwalakwe ni kum’bombela soni ntendele"
  98,5,"Ni nganalamulidwa ikaŵeje yanti an'galagatileje Allah mwakunswejechesya dini Jakwe pakupendechela ku Uujika Wakwe (nikutalikangana nayo isanamu), nikuti ajimicheje Swala mwakolosya ni kutolaga Zaka, soni jalakwejo ni dini jagoloka"
  98,6,"Chisimu ŵandu ŵaakanile (dini ja Usilamu); kutandila achinsyene chitabu (Ayuda ni Akilisito) kwisa soni ŵakuwanganya (Allah ni isanamu), chakaŵe m’moto wa Jahannama, chakaŵe ŵandamo mwalakwemo. Ŵanganyao ni iŵumbe yakusakala nnope"
  98,7,"Chisimu ŵandu ŵaakulupilile nikutendaga yambone, ŵanganyao ni iwumbe yambone nnope"
  98,8,"Malipilo gao kwa Ambuje ŵao chigakaŵe Matimbe Gandamo gasikujilima cha pasi pakwe sulo. Chakaŵe ŵandamo mwalakwemo kwa yaka ni yaka. Allah tachanonyela (pakwapochela masengo gao gambone), nombe nao tachinonyelwa Najo (pamalipilo gataachaapa). Yalakweyo ni yamundu jwatan'jogope M'mbujeegwe (Allah)"
  99,1,Pandema jalichitenganyika litaka nichisikinya chakwe chamachili
  99,2,"Ni kwisa koposya litaka misigo jakwe jausito (ichindu yayaliji nkati mwakwe, mpela malilo ni mitapo jambiya)"
  99,3,"Ni kwisa kuŵecheta mundu (mwawoga soni mwakusimonga kuti): “Litite uli (litaka, ana Kiyama jiyiche?)”"
  99,4,Lyele lisikulyo (litaka) lichiŵecheta abali syakwe syosope (sya indu yayatendekwele pachanya pakwe yambone kapena yakusakala)
  99,5,Ligongo lyanti Ambuje ŵenu tachililamula lyalakwelyo (kuti liŵechete)
  99,6,Lyele lisikulyo ŵandu tachipwilingana ali m'mikutula jakulekangana-lekangana kuti akaalosye masengo gao
  99,7,"Basi jwatapanganye chambone chausito wanti chisawu lunyilili, tachija kuchiona"
  99,8,"Nombe soni jwatapanganye chakusakala chausito wanti chisawu lunyilili, tachija kuchiona"
  100,1,Ngusilumbila hachi syasikuwutuka sili nkupumasika
  100,2,Ni syasikoposya moto mu ikotwa mwakwe (pakuwutuka m’maganga)
  100,3,Ni syasikwagungumuchila amagongo kumasikusiku
  100,4,Nikututumya palakwepo luwundu lwejinji
  100,5,Nikulijinjilila palakwepo likuga (lya amagongo)
  100,6,Chisimu mundu kwa Ambujegwe (Allah) juŵele jwakanila (ukoto waakumpa)
  100,7,Soni chisimu jwalakwe jukuŵichila umboni pa yalakweyo (kupitila mu itendo yakwe)
  100,8,Soni chisimu jwalakwe pakuchinonyela chipanje juŵele jwakupelenganya nnope
  100,9,Ana ngajukumanyilila pandema jaichikoposyedwa yaili m’malembe
  100,10,Nikwisa kwilochesya papaswela yaili m’mitima
  100,11,Chisimu lyele lisikulyo M’mbuje gwao (Allah) tachamanya abali syosope (syakwamba yaŵapanganyaga ŵanganyao)
  101,1,Chagunda ntima (Kiyama)
  101,2,Ana chagunda ntima nichichi
  101,3,Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya chagunda ntima
  101,4,Lyele ni lisiku (lya Kiyama) lyachachiŵa ŵandu (sakalaalii!) mpela mapuluputwa gakusapalala
  101,5,Nombe matumbi gachiŵa (nkuwululuka) mpela litonji lyetyosye mbele
  101,6,"Sano mundu jwachiukasitope n'diingo wakwe (wa yambone, nikwepepala yakusakala)"
  101,7,Basi jwalakwejo takaŵe mu ndamo jakusengwasya
  101,8,"Nambo mundu jwachiukajepepale n'dingo wakwe (wa yambone, ni kusitopa yakusakala)"
  101,9,Basi liuto lyakwe ni ku Hawiya
  101,10,Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya jele (Hawiya)
  101,11,Wele ni Moto Wakoocha nnope
  102,1,Kumpele chipaka kusonganganya (ya duniya mwampikisano kuleka ganisya ya Akhera)
  102,2,Mpaka nkwikanila kwaula ku malembe (n'di m'bwile)
  102,3,Ngwamba! Chinchiika kumanyilila
  102,4,Soni ngwamba! Chinchiika kumanyilila
  102,5,Ngwamba! Ingaŵe mwamanyililaga umanyilisi usyesyene (nga nganin'jijilikaga ni ya duniya)
  102,6,Chisimu chene chinkauone Moto Waukali
  102,7,Soni chinkauone kusyene ni liso lyakusimichisya
  102,8,Soni lyele lisikulyo tinkawusyidwe kusyene ya chindimba (chaŵampele pa duniya)
  103,1,Ngujilumbila ndaŵi
  103,2,Chisimu chene mundu ali nchasiko (ni kupelelwa)
  103,3,"Ikaŵeje aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, ni kulimbisyanaga ya (kuya ichindu) yakuona, ni kulimbisyanaga soni yakupilila"
  104,1,Ipotesi ni yakwe jwalijose jwakwasogoda ni kwachembulusya ŵandu mwakwamumunya
  104,2,Ajula jwaachisonganganyisye chipanje nikuchiŵalanjilaga (ndema ni katema)
  104,3,Akuganichisya kuti chipanje chakwecho chichintendekasye kuŵa jwandamo
  104,4,Ngwamba! Chisimu chene takaponyedwe ku Hutwama
  104,5,Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya Hutwama
  104,6,Wele ni Moto wa Allah wachikolelele (wakuteketulanya chilichose chakuponyedwamo)
  104,7,Awula wachiuŵa nkukwelela ku mitima
  104,8,Chisimu walakweo uchaunichila ni kwaakutika ŵanganyao (kwakusoŵa pakopochela)
  104,9,(Chachiŵa) m’makongwa getandaliche chanchilewu (mwanti ngasakombola kupuluputa)
  105,1,Ana nganinyyiona yaŵatite Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) pakwajonanga achinsyene ndembo (ŵaŵayikaga kugumula Likaaba)
  105,2,Ana nganagatenda malindi gao kuŵa gakusokonechela
  105,3,Ni ŵatumichisye ŵanganyao ijuni mikutula-mikutula
  105,4,Yaliji nkwaasoma ni maganga gelongo lyejoche (ni moto wa ku Jahannama)
  105,5,Niŵatesile kuŵa mpela masapi gagalilidwe (ni inyama ni kulukulidwa)
  106,1,(Ŵajonasile achinsyene ndembo) kuti ajendelechele Makuraishi
  106,2,Panyendele jao jamaulendo ga chuku (kuja ku Yemeni) ni chawu (kuja ku Shami kumalonda mwantunjelele)
  106,3,Basi an'galagatileje M'mbuje jwa aji Nyumba (ja Likaaba)
  106,4,"Ajula jwaŵapele yakulya ligongo lyasala, ni kwaŵambasya ku woga"
  107,1,Ana mum'bweni ajula jwaakukanila ya malipilo (ga pa Kiyama)
  107,2,Basi jwele ni ajula jwaakuntutanga mwanache jwawina
  107,3,Soni jwangachisya yagaliisya masikini
  107,4,Basi ipotesi niyao ŵandu ŵakuswaliji
  107,5,Aŵala ŵanya ŵaakuŵa ali nkusikwanjila swala syao
  107,6,Aŵala ŵanya ŵaakuŵa ali nkutenda ndola
  107,7,"Ni akuŵa soni ali nkukanya yaakamuchisya (pannango, mpela liŵago, chipula, lituli ni yine)"
  108,1,Chisimu Uwwe tumpele (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) Kauthara (lusulo lwa ku Mbepo)
  108,2,Basi mwaswalilani Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) nikusikita (inyama yakur’bani yakupelechela mbepesi Kukwakwe ngaŵaga kwa akumasoka)
  108,3,Chisimu jwaakum'benga mmwejo ni jwali jwakatika (upile wakwe ni kusalidwa kwakwe)
  109,1,"Jilani: “E jenumanja achimakafili!”"
  109,2,“Ngangalagatila chinkuchigalagatila (kunneka Allah).”
  109,3,“Nombe ŵanganyammwe nganim'ba mun'galagatile (Allah) jwangun'galagatila (kutendaga n'di mu ukafili pemo).”
  109,4,“Nombe une soni nganimba nachigalagatile cham'bele n'di nkuchigalagatila ŵanganyammwe.”
  109,5,“Nombe ŵanganyammwe nganim'ba mun'galagatile (Allah) jwangun'galagatila (kutendaga n'di mu ukafili pemo).”
  109,6,“Jenumanja nkwete dini jenu (jagalagatila isanamu) une none ngwete dini jangu (jakun’galagatila Allah).”
  110,1,Ndema jachiyiche chikulupusyo cha Allah ni kuwugula (Maaka kuŵa m’makono mwa Asilamu)
  110,2,Ni kwaona mmwejo ŵandu ali nkwinjila mu dini ja Allah mikutula-mikutula
  110,3,"Basi (jele ndemajo) luswejesyani lumbili lwa Ambuje ŵenu, ni kwaŵenda chikululuko. Chisimu Ŵalakweo aŵele Ŵakupochela nnope toba"
  111,1,"Gajonasiche makono ganagaŵili ga Abu Lahabi, nombe nao ajonasiche"
  111,2,Ngaija kwakamuchisya ipanje yao atamuno yaŵapanganyisye (mpela ŵanache ŵaŵaŵeleche)
  111,3,Takajinjile ku Moto waukwete malamba (gakulapuka)
  111,4,Niŵankwao ŵakwe ŵaŵaliji nkutwichila sasu (syamiŵa nikuntejelaga Muhammadi ﷺ mwakupita)
  111,5,Nnukosi mwao (ŵele ŵakongweo) chimukaŵe mwana litondolo lyamiŵamiŵa (lyakwalagachisya nalyo)
  112,1,"Jilani: “Jwalakwe ni Allah Jumpepe.”"
  112,2,“Allah pe ni jwakun'jegama.”
  112,3,“Nganaŵeleka soni nganaŵelechedwa.”
  112,4,“Soni nganakola jwakulanda najo ata jumo.”
  113,1,"Jilani: “Ngulijuya mwa M’mbuje jwa kumasikusiku.”"
  113,2,“Ku yakusakala yaŵaigumbile.”
  113,3,“Ni ku yakusakala yachilo ndema jachikwinjila chipi.”
  113,4,“Ni ku yakusakala ya (asaŵi) ŵaakupepela mu iwundo (pakuloga).”
  113,5,“Ni ku yakusakala ya jwalitima ndema jajukutenda litima.”
  114,1,"Jilani: “Ngulijuya mwa M'mbuje jwa ŵandu.”"
  114,2,“Nchimwene jwa ŵandu.”
  114,3,“Nnungu jwa ŵandu.”
  114,4,"“Ku yakusakala ya nkusongona (pakuunyenjelela ntima yakusakala), jwakuujiilila ni kuliisisa (naga nsyene ntimao juli junkolasile Allah).”"
  114,5,“Ajula jwaakusongonaga m’mitima mwa ŵandu.”
  114,6,“Jwakuumila m’majini ni mu ŵandu.”